{"term": "1964", "caseName": "American Committee for Protection of Foreign Born v. Subversive Activities Control Board", "caseLink": "https://www.oyez.org/cases/1964/44", "caseTranscripts": [{"transcriptTitle": "Oral Argument - December 09, 1964", "transcriptLink": "https://apps.oyez.org/player/#/warren11/oral_argument_audio/14642", "transcript": [{"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Number 44, American Committee for Protection of Foreign Born, Petitioner, versus Subversive Activities Control Board.", "start": 0, "stop": 10.969, "duration": 10.97, "cleanText": [["number", "american", "committee", "for", "protection", "of", "foreign", "bear", "petitioner", "versus", "subversive", "activity", "control", "board"]]}, {"text": "Mr. Terris, you may continue your argument.", "start": 10.969, "stop": 13.622, "duration": 2.65, "cleanText": [["mr", "terris", "you", "may", "continue", "your", "argument"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Chief Justice, may it please the Court.", "start": 13.622, "stop": 16.439, "duration": 2.82, "cleanText": [["mr", "chief", "justice", "may", "it", "please", "the", "court"]]}, {"text": "The outset I'd like to point out an error in the Government's brief.", "start": 16.439, "stop": 20.606, "duration": 4.17, "cleanText": [["the", "outset", "I", "would", "like", "to", "point", "out", "an", "error", "in", "the", "government", "s", "brief"]]}, {"text": "The Government does not now claim that the Board found the petitioner actually arose on the international legal defense in 1932 or 1933, this -- an organization which had its headquarters in Moscow.", "start": 20.606, "stop": 35.794, "duration": 15.19, "cleanText": [["the", "government", "do", "not", "now", "claim", "that", "the", "board", "find", "the", "petitioner", "actually", "arise", "on", "the", "international", "legal", "defense", "in", "or", "this", "an", "organization", "which", "have", "its", "headquarters", "in", "moscow"]]}, {"text": "While there was considerable evidence indicating this fact, we have overlooked contrary evidence and we think, as the petitioner thinks, that the Board deliberately did not resolve this conflict in the evidence.", "start": 35.794, "stop": 47.168, "duration": 11.37, "cleanText": [["while", "there", "be", "considerable", "evidence", "indicate", "this", "fact", "we", "have", "overlook", "contrary", "evidence", "and", "we", "think", "as", "the", "petitioner", "think", "that", "the", "board", "deliberately", "do", "not", "resolve", "this", "conflict", "in", "the", "evidence"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Where is that in your brief, Mr. Terris?", "start": 47.168, "stop": 49.745, "duration": 2.58, "cleanText": [["where", "be", "that", "in", "your", "brief", "mr", "terris"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, it appears in the statement we put -- but it also appears at various points during the discussion of the evidentiary questions in several places.", "start": 49.745, "stop": 58.675, "duration": 8.93, "cleanText": [["well", "it", "appear", "in", "the", "statement", "we", "put", "but", "it", "also", "appear", "at", "various", "point", "during", "the", "discussion", "of", "the", "evidentiary", "question", "in", "several", "place"]]}, {"text": "But it's -- I think it's first on page 4 and the footnote on page 4 is where our reasoning, yes in our brief, it's where our reasoning was.", "start": 58.675, "stop": 71.083, "duration": 12.41, "cleanText": [["but", "it", "be", "i", "think", "it", "be", "first", "on", "page", "and", "the", "footnote", "on", "page", "be", "where", "our", "reasoning", "yes", "in", "our", "brief", "it", "be", "where", "our", "reasoning", "be"]]}, {"text": "The Board clearly didn't explicitly find it and we thought that it had implicitly found it and we agree with the petitioner that probably even that is not so.", "start": 71.083, "stop": 81.341, "duration": 10.26, "cleanText": [["the", "board", "clearly", "do", "not", "explicitly", "find", "it", "and", "we", "think", "that", "it", "have", "implicitly", "find", "it", "and", "we", "agree", "with", "the", "petitioner", "that", "probably", "even", "that", "be", "not", "so"]]}, {"text": "Now, I'd like you to turn to Mr. Justice Goldberg's question yesterday as to the meaning of the aid component of the statute more explicitly whether it requires directly aimed at forcible overthrow of the Government or advocating forcible overthrow of the Government.", "start": 81.341, "stop": 99.826, "duration": 18.49, "cleanText": [["now", "I", "would", "like", "you", "to", "turn", "to", "mr", "justice", "goldberg", "s", "question", "yesterday", "as", "to", "the", "meaning", "of", "the", "aid", "component", "of", "the", "statute", "more", "explicitly", "whether", "it", "require", "directly", "aim", "at", "forcible", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government", "or", "advocate", "forcible", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "I think I mentioned yesterday that we started from the proposition that Section 3 (4) on its face strongly looks the Government's way because it says that all the Government need to show, to show that an organization is a Communist-front is that it operates primarily for the purpose of giving aid and support to a Communist-action organization, a Communist Party.", "start": 99.826, "stop": 124.764, "duration": 24.94, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "i", "mention", "yesterday", "that", "we", "start", "from", "the", "proposition", "that", "section", "on", "its", "face", "strongly", "look", "the", "government", "s", "way", "because", "it", "say", "that", "all", "the", "government", "need", "to", "show", "to", "show", "that", "an", "organization", "be", "a", "communist", "front", "be", "that", "it", "operate", "primarily", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "give", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "a", "communist", "action", "organization", "a", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "On its face, all that it requires is aid and support and not aid and support of any particular kind of or for any particular purpose of the Communist-action organization.", "start": 124.764, "stop": 134.725, "duration": 9.96, "cleanText": [["on", "its", "face", "all", "that", "it", "require", "be", "aid", "and", "support", "and", "not", "aid", "and", "support", "of", "any", "particular", "kind", "of", "or", "for", "any", "particular", "purpose", "of", "the", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}, {"text": "And this is supported by Section 2 (7) which describes Communist-fronts as organizations which conceal the facts as to their true character and their purpose in order to obtain support from persons who would not otherwise give it.", "start": 134.725, "stop": 149.184, "duration": 14.46, "cleanText": [["and", "this", "be", "support", "by", "section", "which", "describe", "communist", "front", "as", "organization", "which", "conceal", "the", "fact", "as", "to", "their", "true", "character", "and", "their", "purpose", "in", "order", "to", "obtain", "support", "from", "person", "who", "would", "not", "otherwise", "give", "it"]]}, {"text": "We think it's quite clear that if it was directly aiding overthrow of the Government or advocating overthrow of the Government, not many non-Communists would be in any doubt as to the control of the organization or to its purpose and therefore it would not fulfill this description.", "start": 149.184, "stop": 167.592, "duration": 18.41, "cleanText": [["we", "think", "it", "be", "quite", "clear", "that", "if", "it", "be", "directly", "aid", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government", "or", "advocate", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government", "not", "many", "non", "communist", "would", "be", "in", "any", "doubt", "as", "to", "the", "control", "of", "the", "organization", "or", "to", "its", "purpose", "and", "therefore", "it", "would", "not", "fulfill", "this", "description"]]}, {"text": "Now, petitioner points to the beginning, the first phrase of 2 (7) that says, well the reason that the Communist-action organization is doing this, setting up Communist-fronts as to aid its objectives under Section 2 (6) and these are forcible overthrow of the Government.", "start": 167.592, "stop": 186.102, "duration": 18.51, "cleanText": [["now", "petitioner", "point", "to", "the", "beginning", "the", "first", "phrase", "of", "that", "say", "well", "the", "reason", "that", "the", "communist", "action", "organization", "be", "do", "this", "set", "up", "communist", "front", "as", "to", "aid", "its", "objective", "under", "section", "and", "these", "be", "forcible", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "Well, that's of course exactly the point that I was making yesterday.", "start": 186.102, "stop": 189.685, "duration": 3.58, "cleanText": [["well", "that", "be", "of", "course", "exactly", "the", "point", "that", "i", "be", "make", "yesterday"]]}, {"text": "But this is exactly why they setup Communist-fronts but it doesn't mean that Communist-fronts themselves advocate overthrow of the Government or directly aid overthrow of the Government.", "start": 189.685, "stop": 199.555, "duration": 9.87, "cleanText": [["but", "this", "be", "exactly", "why", "they", "setup", "communist", "front", "but", "it", "do", "not", "mean", "that", "communist", "front", "themselves", "advocate", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government", "or", "directly", "aid", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "They do other more immediate things.", "start": 199.555, "stop": 203.005, "duration": 3.45, "cleanText": [["they", "do", "other", "more", "immediate", "thing"]]}, {"text": "And I think this is if -- the legislative history of this statute is extremely lengthy, but I think out of the reading of the -- the both -- both the testimony of the congressional hearings and the debate on the floor of Congress on the prompt provisions is quite clear that what they were aiming at is organizations which are seemingly harmless that seem like the organizations defending the Bill of Rights or civil liberties or the rights of farmers or labor but in fact are controlled by the Communist Party and are in fact are aiding it.", "start": 203.005, "stop": 236.13, "duration": 33.13, "cleanText": [["and", "i", "think", "this", "be", "if", "the", "legislative", "history", "of", "this", "statute", "be", "extremely", "lengthy", "but", "i", "think", "out", "of", "the", "reading", "of", "the", "the", "both", "both", "the", "testimony", "of", "the", "congressional", "hearing", "and", "the", "debate", "on", "the", "floor", "of", "congress", "on", "the", "prompt", "provision", "be", "quite", "clear", "that", "what", "they", "we", "be", "aim", "at", "be", "organization", "which", "be", "seemingly", "harmless", "that", "seem", "like", "the", "organization", "defend", "the", "bill", "of", "right", "or", "civil", "liberty", "or", "the", "right", "of", "farmer", "or", "labor", "but", "in", "fact", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "be", "in", "fact", "be", "aid", "it"]]}, {"text": "There's no indication whatsoever that as to Communist-fronts, they are -- that the -- that Congress believed that they directly advocated overthrow of the Government.", "start": 236.13, "stop": 247.21, "duration": 11.08, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "no", "indication", "whatsoever", "that", "as", "to", "communist", "front", "they", "be", "that", "the", "that", "congress", "believe", "that", "they", "directly", "advocate", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "And I may say that that distinction is also clear in the committee report which petitioner's counsel cited to you yesterday.", "start": 247.21, "stop": 255.746, "duration": 8.54, "cleanText": [["and", "i", "may", "say", "that", "that", "distinction", "be", "also", "clear", "in", "the", "committee", "report", "which", "petitioner", "s", "counsel", "cite", "to", "you", "yesterday"]]}, {"text": "All that says is that the Congress was not aiming a mere theoretical problem.", "start": 255.746, "stop": 261.302, "duration": 5.56, "cleanText": [["all", "that", "say", "be", "that", "the", "congress", "be", "not", "aim", "a", "mere", "theoretical", "problem"]]}, {"text": "It was aiming at a problem that was a serious danger to this country.", "start": 261.302, "stop": 266.262, "duration": 4.96, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "aim", "at", "a", "problem", "that", "be", "a", "serious", "danger", "to", "this", "country"]]}, {"text": "Of course that -- and that again is exactly what I was trying to say yesterday that if the Communist Party was just interested in abstract Marxism, the statute would not have been passed.", "start": 266.262, "stop": 278.759, "duration": 12.5, "cleanText": [["of", "course", "that", "and", "that", "again", "be", "exactly", "what", "i", "be", "try", "to", "say", "yesterday", "that", "if", "the", "communist", "party", "be", "just", "interested", "in", "abstract", "marxism", "the", "statute", "would", "not", "have", "be", "pass"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Do you think that the part of saying is to involve or to have itself engaged, as part of the record, is that the original Communist-action definition?", "start": 278.759, "stop": 304.938, "duration": 26.18, "cleanText": [["do", "you", "think", "that", "the", "part", "of", "say", "be", "to", "involve", "or", "to", "have", "itself", "engage", "as", "part", "of", "the", "record", "be", "that", "the", "original", "communist", "action", "definition"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor, I don't -- I don't think you would.", "start": 304.938, "stop": 309.313, "duration": 4.38, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "i", "do", "not", "i", "do", "not", "think", "you", "would"]]}, {"text": "I think, an argue could have been made if the Communist-fronts provisions weren't in the statute at all.", "start": 309.313, "stop": 315.638, "duration": 6.32, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "an", "argue", "could", "have", "be", "make", "if", "the", "communist", "front", "provision", "be", "not", "in", "the", "statute", "at", "all"]]}, {"text": "That the definition of organization in the statute is so broad that it could have covered Communist-fronts.", "start": 315.638, "stop": 322.478, "duration": 6.84, "cleanText": [["that", "the", "definition", "of", "organization", "in", "the", "statute", "be", "so", "broad", "that", "it", "could", "have", "cover", "communist", "front"]]}, {"text": "The difficulty is that I think it's quite clear by putting in Communist-fronts that the Congress wanted to deal with this type of organization under the Communist-front provisions.", "start": 322.478, "stop": 332.549, "duration": 10.07, "cleanText": [["the", "difficulty", "be", "that", "i", "think", "it", "be", "quite", "clear", "by", "put", "in", "communist", "front", "that", "the", "congress", "want", "to", "deal", "with", "this", "type", "of", "organization", "under", "the", "communist", "front", "provision"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Communist-front, a popular definition by (Inaudible) or by the statute that it is an organization (Inaudible).", "start": 332.549, "stop": 345.011, "duration": 12.46, "cleanText": [["well", "communist", "front", "a", "popular", "definition", "by", "inaudible", "or", "by", "the", "statute", "that", "it", "be", "an", "organization", "inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Even the name itself, that's right, that's the name itself.", "start": 345.011, "stop": 347.499, "duration": 2.49, "cleanText": [["even", "the", "name", "itself", "that", "be", "right", "that", "be", "the", "name", "itself"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "The purpose of the front is to --", "start": 347.499, "stop": 348.557, "duration": 1.06, "cleanText": [["the", "purpose", "of", "the", "front", "be", "to"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 348.557, "stop": 350.374, "duration": 1.82, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- (Inaudible) that you in fact require.", "start": 350.374, "stop": 352.607, "duration": 2.23, "cleanText": [["inaudible", "that", "you", "in", "fact", "require"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right, Your Honor.", "start": 352.607, "stop": 354.267, "duration": 1.66, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "And that of course is what 2 (7) describes the front as -- now I may say that -- and this is what I was coming to -- if, if the petitioner's argument is accepted, the front provisions will be completely wiped out of the statute.", "start": 354.267, "stop": 367.325, "duration": 13.06, "cleanText": [["and", "that", "of", "course", "be", "what", "describe", "the", "front", "as", "now", "i", "may", "say", "that", "and", "this", "be", "what", "i", "be", "come", "to", "if", "if", "the", "petitioner", "s", "argument", "be", "accept", "the", "front", "provision", "will", "be", "completely", "wipe", "out", "of", "the", "statute"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "So far as your argument is concerned, the aid provision --", "start": 367.325, "stop": 371.069, "duration": 3.74, "cleanText": [["so", "far", "as", "your", "argument", "be", "concern", "the", "aid", "provision"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, I don't think so, Your Honor.", "start": 371.069, "stop": 373.088, "duration": 2.02, "cleanText": [["no", "i", "do", "not", "think", "so", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "What I -- I believe what you required is that it should involve itself with (Inaudible) show that Communist (Inaudible).", "start": 373.088, "stop": 391.451, "duration": 18.36, "cleanText": [["what", "i", "i", "believe", "what", "you", "require", "be", "that", "it", "should", "involve", "itself", "with", "inaudible", "show", "that", "communist", "inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 391.451, "stop": 392.914, "duration": 1.46, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 392.914, "stop": 393.962, "duration": 1.05, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 393.962, "stop": 394.419, "duration": 0.46, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible) by the Communist Party.", "start": 394.419, "stop": 399.126, "duration": 4.71, "cleanText": [["inaudible", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, by definition?", "start": 399.126, "stop": 400.215, "duration": 1.09, "cleanText": [["well", "by", "definition"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 400.215, "stop": 400.849, "duration": 0.63, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}, {"text": "Now, Congress stopped there and then regarded this as (Inaudible).", "start": 400.849, "stop": 411.133, "duration": 10.28, "cleanText": [["now", "congress", "stop", "there", "and", "then", "regard", "this", "as", "inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "But that isn't --", "start": 411.133, "stop": 411.598, "duration": 0.47, "cleanText": [["but", "that", "be", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "They are the ones who can get out of control.", "start": 411.598, "stop": 413.839, "duration": 2.24, "cleanText": [["they", "be", "the", "one", "who", "can", "get", "out", "of", "control"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, but it didn't add anything beyond serving the purposes of the Communist Party, that's exactly what the A provision says.", "start": 413.839, "stop": 419.94, "duration": 6.1, "cleanText": [["yes", "but", "it", "do", "not", "add", "anything", "beyond", "serve", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "that", "be", "exactly", "what", "the", "a", "provision", "say"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Then you ought to -- (Inaudible) and also the -- the (Inaudible).", "start": 419.94, "stop": 431.162, "duration": 11.22, "cleanText": [["then", "you", "ought", "to", "inaudible", "and", "also", "the", "the", "inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor I think I did say that it would be covered if its purpose was to -- was to aid the Soviet Union.", "start": 431.162, "stop": 440.089, "duration": 8.93, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "i", "think", "i", "do", "say", "that", "it", "would", "be", "cover", "if", "its", "purpose", "be", "to", "be", "to", "aid", "the", "soviet", "union"]]}, {"text": "It's controlled by the Communist Party and aiding the Soviet Union, my answer was that it is covered.", "start": 440.089, "stop": 448.617, "duration": 8.53, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "aid", "the", "soviet", "union", "my", "answer", "be", "that", "it", "be", "cover"]]}, {"text": "If it -- if he has an interest that's ballet, it asked the Soviet Ballet Company in the United States and the Danish one and the English --", "start": 448.617, "stop": 453.557, "duration": 4.94, "cleanText": [["if", "it", "if", "he", "have", "an", "interest", "that", "be", "ballet", "it", "ask", "the", "soviet", "ballet", "company", "in", "the", "united", "state", "and", "the", "danish", "one", "and", "the", "english"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Voice Overlap) by the Communist Party.", "start": 453.557, "stop": 455.65, "duration": 2.09, "cleanText": [["voice", "overlap", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right and just as it is interest is ballet, it does not have to register, right.", "start": 455.65, "stop": 460.104, "duration": 4.45, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "and", "just", "as", "it", "be", "interest", "be", "ballet", "it", "do", "not", "have", "to", "register", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, what -- what about this organization, who are just interested -- an immigrant.", "start": 460.104, "stop": 464.217, "duration": 4.11, "cleanText": [["well", "what", "what", "about", "this", "organization", "who", "be", "just", "interested", "an", "immigrant"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, that was what they said they were interested in the Board found in the basis of, we believe, ample evidence and I like to get to that evidence on just how we did deliberately served the Communist Party in a moment but I -- before I get to it, I like to point out that if the petitioner's argument is accepted, there will be no more Communist-front provisions in the statute.", "start": 464.217, "stop": 485.62, "duration": 21.4, "cleanText": [["well", "that", "be", "what", "they", "say", "they", "we", "be", "interested", "in", "the", "board", "find", "in", "the", "basis", "of", "we", "believe", "ample", "evidence", "and", "i", "like", "to", "get", "to", "that", "evidence", "on", "just", "how", "we", "do", "deliberately", "serve", "the", "communist", "party", "in", "a", "moment", "but", "i", "before", "i", "get", "to", "it", "i", "like", "to", "point", "out", "that", "if", "the", "petitioner", "s", "argument", "be", "accept", "there", "will", "be", "no", "more", "communist", "front", "provision", "in", "the", "statute"]]}, {"text": "Not only -- there isn't a bit of evidence in this record, not a bit and we wouldn't ever expect them that they were advocating overthrow of the government, or that they were directly attempting to have overthrow of the government.", "start": 485.62, "stop": 498.508, "duration": 12.89, "cleanText": [["not", "only", "there", "be", "not", "a", "bit", "of", "evidence", "in", "this", "record", "not", "a", "bit", "and", "we", "would", "not", "ever", "expect", "them", "that", "they", "we", "be", "advocate", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government", "or", "that", "they", "we", "be", "directly", "attempt", "to", "have", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "Nor, as far as I know and description of the other Communist-front cases is in the Appendix to the Government's brief has any one of the other organizations ever done any of these things (Voice Overlap) --", "start": 498.508, "stop": 510.644, "duration": 12.14, "cleanText": [["nor", "as", "far", "as", "i", "know", "and", "description", "of", "the", "other", "communist", "front", "case", "be", "in", "the", "appendix", "to", "the", "government", "s", "brief", "have", "any", "one", "of", "the", "other", "organization", "ever", "do", "any", "of", "these", "thing", "voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Why did they say there would never be any evidence to that effect if in fact they were doing that.", "start": 510.644, "stop": 515.615, "duration": 4.97, "cleanText": [["why", "do", "they", "say", "there", "would", "never", "be", "any", "evidence", "to", "that", "effect", "if", "in", "fact", "they", "we", "be", "do", "that"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, no, no.", "start": 515.615, "stop": 516.029, "duration": 0.41, "cleanText": [["no", "no", "no"]]}, {"text": "They in fact are not doing it.", "start": 516.029, "stop": 517.722, "duration": 1.69, "cleanText": [["they", "in", "fact", "be", "not", "do", "it"]]}, {"text": "In fact, they do not advocate overthrow of the government in these organizations or directly aid overthrow of the government.", "start": 517.722, "stop": 526.017, "duration": 8.3, "cleanText": [["in", "fact", "they", "do", "not", "advocate", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government", "in", "these", "organization", "or", "directly", "aid", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "They do not, Your Honor.", "start": 526.017, "stop": 528.458, "duration": 2.44, "cleanText": [["they", "do", "not", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "That -- to the extent that the Communist Party does those things, it does it itself.", "start": 528.458, "stop": 534.227, "duration": 5.77, "cleanText": [["that", "to", "the", "extent", "that", "the", "communist", "party", "do", "those", "thing", "it", "do", "it", "itself"]]}, {"text": "There's no need to have separate organizations to directly do those things.", "start": 534.227, "stop": 538.81, "duration": 4.58, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "no", "need", "to", "have", "separate", "organization", "to", "directly", "do", "those", "thing"]]}, {"text": "When it wants to conceal these purposes then it sets up the subsidiaries.", "start": 538.81, "stop": 543.627, "duration": 4.82, "cleanText": [["when", "it", "want", "to", "conceal", "these", "purpose", "then", "it", "set", "up", "the", "subsidiary"]]}, {"text": "In order to deceive non-Communists to support various Communist positions which on their face do not directly relate to overthrow of the government.", "start": 543.627, "stop": 553.367, "duration": 9.74, "cleanText": [["in", "order", "to", "deceive", "non", "communist", "to", "support", "various", "communist", "position", "which", "on", "their", "face", "do", "not", "directly", "relate", "to", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "What you're saying is that Communist org -- named organizations in the next case as an organization called the gentleman --", "start": 553.367, "stop": 565.504, "duration": 12.14, "cleanText": [["what", "you", "be", "say", "be", "that", "communist", "org", "name", "organization", "in", "the", "next", "case", "as", "an", "organization", "call", "the", "gentleman"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 565.504, "stop": 568.001, "duration": 2.5, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- that it's expounding the principle related to -- the other purposes followed to the principle of -- the principle established, as discussed in A, is that it?", "start": 568.001, "stop": 578.087, "duration": 10.09, "cleanText": [["that", "it", "be", "expound", "the", "principle", "relate", "to", "the", "other", "purpose", "follow", "to", "the", "principle", "of", "the", "principle", "establish", "as", "discuss", "in", "a", "be", "that", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right Your Honor because, and again --", "start": 578.087, "stop": 581.487, "duration": 3.4, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "your", "honor", "because", "and", "again"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Then the question is whether that is permissible.", "start": 581.487, "stop": 583.575, "duration": 2.09, "cleanText": [["then", "the", "question", "be", "whether", "that", "be", "permissible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, then we have the constitutional question of whether --", "start": 583.575, "stop": 586.927, "duration": 3.35, "cleanText": [["well", "then", "we", "have", "the", "constitutional", "question", "of", "whether"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 586.927, "stop": 587.523, "duration": 0.6, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- that's right Your Honor and if I don't --", "start": 587.523, "stop": 590.659, "duration": 3.14, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "your", "honor", "and", "if", "i", "do", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's the test you're talking about.", "start": 590.659, "stop": 592.14, "duration": 1.48, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "the", "test", "you", "be", "talk", "about"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 592.14, "stop": 593.055, "duration": 0.91, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}, {"text": "The Congress said that -- and I think this is quite clear as to what the Congress was doing -- the Congress said if you're controlled by the Communist Party and you're deliberately aiding the Communist Party, you are the Communist Party despite any fictional lines that are drawn between the two.", "start": 593.055, "stop": 610.13, "duration": 17.08, "cleanText": [["the", "congress", "say", "that", "and", "i", "think", "this", "be", "quite", "clear", "as", "to", "what", "the", "congress", "be", "do", "the", "congress", "say", "if", "you", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "you", "be", "deliberately", "aid", "the", "communist", "party", "you", "be", "the", "communist", "party", "despite", "any", "fictional", "line", "that", "be", "draw", "between", "the", "two"]]}, {"text": "In the corporate field nobody would have any difficulty seeing that you treat the two organizations the same.", "start": 610.13, "stop": 616.217, "duration": 6.09, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "corporate", "field", "nobody", "would", "have", "any", "difficulty", "see", "that", "you", "treat", "the", "two", "organization", "the", "same"]]}, {"text": "That's -- we're saying that Congress did exactly that.", "start": 616.217, "stop": 618.886, "duration": 2.67, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "we", "be", "say", "that", "congress", "do", "exactly", "that"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Byron R. White", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well Mr. Terris, then I quote that a -- the Communist Party setup a contacting firm or partnership, it's no question that's controlled by the Communist Party and it's sole purpose was to build houses and sell them to make money with the purposes of financing the Communist Party movements, all the profits of the organization that was profitable, but right back into the -- into the Communist Party treasury is by definition would be (Voice Overlap) --", "start": 618.886, "stop": 648.403, "duration": 29.52, "cleanText": [["well", "mr", "terris", "then", "i", "quote", "that", "a", "the", "communist", "party", "setup", "a", "contacting", "firm", "or", "partnership", "it", "be", "no", "question", "that", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "it", "be", "sole", "purpose", "be", "to", "build", "house", "and", "sell", "them", "to", "make", "money", "with", "the", "purpose", "of", "finance", "the", "communist", "party", "movement", "all", "the", "profit", "of", "the", "organization", "that", "be", "profitable", "but", "right", "back", "into", "the", "into", "the", "communist", "party", "treasury", "be", "by", "definition", "would", "be", "voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I think they would be covered.", "start": 648.403, "stop": 649.429, "duration": 1.03, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "they", "would", "be", "cover"]]}, {"text": "Yes sir.", "start": 649.429, "stop": 650.195, "duration": 0.77, "cleanText": [["yes", "sir"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Byron R. White", "textObjs": [{"text": "Although the activity is wholly legal.", "start": 650.195, "stop": 652.875, "duration": 2.68, "cleanText": [["although", "the", "activity", "be", "wholly", "legal"]]}, {"text": "I mean the building operation is --", "start": 652.875, "stop": 653.412, "duration": 0.54, "cleanText": [["i", "mean", "the", "building", "operation", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right --", "start": 653.412, "stop": 653.982, "duration": 0.57, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Byron R. White", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- is wholly legal and then best American division.", "start": 653.982, "stop": 656.937, "duration": 2.96, "cleanText": [["be", "wholly", "legal", "and", "then", "best", "american", "division"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's quite -- that's quite right, Your Honor.", "start": 656.937, "stop": 658.769, "duration": 1.83, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "quite", "that", "be", "quite", "right", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "I mean and it is a -- I'd like to return, however, that that's also true in the Foreign Agents Registration Act and Federal Regulation of Lobbying Act and other statutes in which the matter is perfectly legal and protected, in the area protected by the First Amendment.", "start": 658.769, "stop": 673.223, "duration": 14.45, "cleanText": [["i", "mean", "and", "it", "be", "a", "I", "would", "like", "to", "return", "however", "that", "that", "be", "also", "true", "in", "the", "foreign", "agent", "registration", "act", "and", "federal", "regulation", "of", "lobby", "act", "and", "other", "statute", "in", "which", "the", "matter", "be", "perfectly", "legal", "and", "protect", "in", "the", "area", "protect", "by", "the", "first", "amendment"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, suppose the (Inaudible).", "start": 673.223, "stop": 680.219, "duration": 7, "cleanText": [["well", "suppose", "the", "inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "What was their purpose, Your Honor?", "start": 680.219, "stop": 682.141, "duration": 1.92, "cleanText": [["what", "be", "their", "purpose", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 682.141, "stop": 693.13, "duration": 10.99, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "They would have to register, Your Honor.", "start": 693.13, "stop": 695.212, "duration": 2.08, "cleanText": [["they", "would", "have", "to", "register", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 695.212, "stop": 712.82, "duration": 17.61, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I return to the purpose of what it was.", "start": 712.82, "stop": 716.323, "duration": 3.5, "cleanText": [["i", "return", "to", "the", "purpose", "of", "what", "it", "be"]]}, {"text": "If it insists those -- those facts, you'd still have to look for the purpose.", "start": 716.323, "stop": 720.105, "duration": 3.78, "cleanText": [["if", "it", "insist", "those", "those", "fact", "you", "would", "still", "have", "to", "look", "for", "the", "purpose"]]}, {"text": "It isn't enough just to happen to aid the Communist Party, that's why Cramp and Baggett cases are not important.", "start": 720.105, "stop": 727.255, "duration": 7.15, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "enough", "just", "to", "happen", "to", "aid", "the", "communist", "party", "that", "be", "why", "cramp", "and", "baggett", "case", "be", "not", "important"]]}, {"text": "It's not enough just to perform an act that somebody can say is a vague.", "start": 727.255, "stop": 732.204, "duration": 4.95, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "enough", "just", "to", "perform", "an", "act", "that", "somebody", "can", "say", "be", "a", "vague"]]}, {"text": "You have to have that purpose.", "start": 732.204, "stop": 733.75, "duration": 1.55, "cleanText": [["you", "have", "to", "have", "that", "purpose"]]}, {"text": "You have to be doing it deliberately.", "start": 733.75, "stop": 735.086, "duration": 1.34, "cleanText": [["you", "have", "to", "be", "do", "it", "deliberately"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 735.086, "stop": 737.041, "duration": 1.96, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well --", "start": 737.041, "stop": 737.565, "duration": 0.52, "cleanText": [["well"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 737.565, "stop": 738.836, "duration": 1.27, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I think that it's very possible that you also have the -- have to have the objective fact.", "start": 738.836, "stop": 743.762, "duration": 4.93, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "that", "it", "be", "very", "possible", "that", "you", "also", "have", "the", "have", "to", "have", "the", "objective", "fact"]]}, {"text": "We don't think that has to be reached here because both the Board and the Court of Appeals found that they were actually aiding the Communist Party.", "start": 743.762, "stop": 750.804, "duration": 7.04, "cleanText": [["we", "do", "not", "think", "that", "have", "to", "be", "reach", "here", "because", "both", "the", "board", "and", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "find", "that", "they", "we", "be", "actually", "aid", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "But you at least have to have the subjective fact.", "start": 750.804, "stop": 753.202, "duration": 2.4, "cleanText": [["but", "you", "at", "least", "have", "to", "have", "the", "subjective", "fact"]]}, {"text": "That's right, Your Honor.", "start": 753.202, "stop": 755.275, "duration": 2.07, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "There's a concept of -- this has to be a cover as I -- the Ian Fleming used to call it --", "start": 755.275, "stop": 762.188, "duration": 6.91, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "a", "concept", "of", "this", "have", "to", "be", "a", "cover", "as", "i", "the", "ian", "fleming", "use", "to", "call", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 762.188, "stop": 762.412, "duration": 0.22, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "Or a front, it has to -- it purport -- purportedly to be per as Justice Harlan says for Abraham Lincoln but really to be --", "start": 762.412, "stop": 770.248, "duration": 7.84, "cleanText": [["or", "a", "front", "it", "have", "to", "it", "purport", "purportedly", "to", "be", "per", "as", "justice", "harlan", "say", "for", "abraham", "lincoln", "but", "really", "to", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right (Voice Overlap).", "start": 770.248, "stop": 772.289, "duration": 2.04, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "voice", "overlap"]]}, {"text": "And insofar as we talked --", "start": 772.289, "stop": 773.514, "duration": 1.23, "cleanText": [["and", "insofar", "as", "we", "talk"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "Now, purportedly to be for the ballet but really for something else.", "start": 773.514, "stop": 777.306, "duration": 3.79, "cleanText": [["now", "purportedly", "to", "be", "for", "the", "ballet", "but", "really", "for", "something", "else"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 777.306, "stop": 777.365, "duration": 0.06, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "That it's was really for the ballet, then it wouldn't be covered.", "start": 777.365, "stop": 779.924, "duration": 2.56, "cleanText": [["that", "it", "have", "be", "really", "for", "the", "ballet", "then", "it", "would", "not", "be", "cover"]]}, {"text": "The Russian ballet, that wouldn't be covered.", "start": 779.924, "stop": 780.768, "duration": 0.84, "cleanText": [["the", "russian", "ballet", "that", "would", "not", "be", "cover"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, no, it would not be covered.", "start": 780.768, "stop": 782.785, "duration": 2.02, "cleanText": [["no", "no", "it", "would", "not", "be", "cover"]]}, {"text": "And the purpose of this, in your terms Your Honor, is to disclose what are the facts insofar as we're talking here.", "start": 782.785, "stop": 790.322, "duration": 7.54, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "purpose", "of", "this", "in", "your", "term", "your", "honor", "be", "to", "disclose", "what", "be", "the", "fact", "insofar", "as", "we", "be", "talk", "here"]]}, {"text": "We're not talking about the disabilities.", "start": 790.322, "stop": 791.838, "duration": 1.52, "cleanText": [["we", "be", "not", "talk", "about", "the", "disability"]]}, {"text": "The purpose is to disclose the facts.", "start": 791.838, "stop": 794.372, "duration": 2.53, "cleanText": [["the", "purpose", "be", "to", "disclose", "the", "fact"]]}, {"text": "Now, let me point to what -- what are the facts that the Board found the evidence shows concerning petitioner's aims.", "start": 794.372, "stop": 801.625, "duration": 7.25, "cleanText": [["now", "let", "me", "point", "to", "what", "what", "be", "the", "fact", "that", "the", "board", "find", "the", "evidence", "show", "concern", "petitioner", "s", "aim"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Terris, may I ask you this question, suppose a law firm was headed by a man who was a Communist.", "start": 801.625, "stop": 810.837, "duration": 9.21, "cleanText": [["mr", "terris", "may", "i", "ask", "you", "this", "question", "suppose", "a", "law", "firm", "be", "head", "by", "a", "man", "who", "be", "a", "communist"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, Your Honor.", "start": 810.837, "stop": 811.691, "duration": 0.85, "cleanText": [["yes", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "And he was employed, let's say by the Communist Party to do nothing but defend persons who were charged with a -- who were subject to deportation.", "start": 811.691, "stop": 823.1, "duration": 11.41, "cleanText": [["and", "he", "be", "employ", "let", "us", "say", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "to", "do", "nothing", "but", "defend", "person", "who", "we", "be", "charge", "with", "a", "who", "we", "be", "subject", "to", "deportation"]]}, {"text": "They're claiming to be subject to deportation, would that law firm have to register?", "start": 823.1, "stop": 830.423, "duration": 7.32, "cleanText": [["they", "be", "claim", "to", "be", "subject", "to", "deportation", "would", "that", "law", "firm", "have", "to", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, there would be a number of -- there would be the number of questions, Your Honor.", "start": 830.423, "stop": 833.417, "duration": 2.99, "cleanText": [["well", "there", "would", "be", "a", "number", "of", "there", "would", "be", "the", "number", "of", "question", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "The first one that occurs to me is does this man control the law firm?", "start": 833.417, "stop": 837.941, "duration": 4.52, "cleanText": [["the", "first", "one", "that", "occur", "to", "me", "be", "do", "this", "man", "control", "the", "law", "firm"]]}, {"text": "His word decides everything that occurs --", "start": 837.941, "stop": 840.284, "duration": 2.34, "cleanText": [["his", "word", "decide", "everything", "that", "occur"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Unless --", "start": 840.284, "stop": 840.458, "duration": 0.17, "cleanText": [["unless"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- in it or is it, you know --", "start": 840.458, "stop": 841.089, "duration": 0.63, "cleanText": [["in", "it", "or", "be", "it", "you", "know"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Let's start --", "start": 841.089, "stop": 841.55, "duration": 0.46, "cleanText": [["let", "us", "start"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- a partnership in which they discuss --", "start": 841.55, "stop": 842.677, "duration": 1.13, "cleanText": [["a", "partnership", "in", "which", "they", "discuss"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Let's start with that premise that he's a dominating factor and a --", "start": 842.677, "stop": 846.852, "duration": 4.17, "cleanText": [["let", "us", "start", "with", "that", "premise", "that", "he", "be", "a", "dominating", "factor", "and", "a"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "He controls it and the purpose is to defend Communists.", "start": 846.852, "stop": 849.471, "duration": 2.62, "cleanText": [["he", "control", "it", "and", "the", "purpose", "be", "to", "defend", "communist"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, no.", "start": 849.471, "stop": 851.071, "duration": 1.6, "cleanText": [["no", "no"]]}, {"text": "He defends anyone who comes along.", "start": 851.071, "stop": 853.239, "duration": 2.17, "cleanText": [["he", "defend", "anyone", "who", "come", "along"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Right.", "start": 853.239, "stop": 853.41, "duration": 0.17, "cleanText": [["right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "What the Communist Party employs him to -- to represent those members of the party who were subject to deportation.", "start": 853.41, "stop": 863.166, "duration": 9.76, "cleanText": [["what", "the", "communist", "party", "employ", "him", "to", "to", "represent", "those", "member", "of", "the", "party", "who", "we", "be", "subject", "to", "deportation"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor, the Act doesn't apply to individuals.", "start": 863.166, "stop": 865.846, "duration": 2.68, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "the", "act", "do", "not", "apply", "to", "individual"]]}, {"text": "You'd have to make a finding --", "start": 865.846, "stop": 866.865, "duration": 1.02, "cleanText": [["you", "would", "have", "to", "make", "a", "finding"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, no, no --", "start": 866.865, "stop": 866.97, "duration": 0.11, "cleanText": [["no", "no", "no"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- to see that the purpose of the law firm --", "start": 866.97, "stop": 867.363, "duration": 0.39, "cleanText": [["to", "see", "that", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "law", "firm"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- (Voice Overlap) organization because these people are not -- are not corporations.", "start": 867.363, "stop": 873.202, "duration": 5.84, "cleanText": [["voice", "overlap", "organization", "because", "these", "people", "be", "not", "be", "not", "corporation"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No they can be unincorporated association.", "start": 873.202, "stop": 874.359, "duration": 1.16, "cleanText": [["no", "they", "can", "be", "unincorporated", "association"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 874.359, "stop": 874.727, "duration": 0.37, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}, {"text": "Now unless, one is loosely organize as this but a law firm.", "start": 874.727, "stop": 880.181, "duration": 5.45, "cleanText": [["now", "unless", "one", "be", "loosely", "organize", "as", "this", "but", "a", "law", "firm"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "If the purpose of the law firm, not the purpose of the dominating partner, but the purpose of the law firm, of course you can look to his purpose.", "start": 880.181, "stop": 889.155, "duration": 8.97, "cleanText": [["if", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "law", "firm", "not", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "dominating", "partner", "but", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "law", "firm", "of", "course", "you", "can", "look", "to", "his", "purpose"]]}, {"text": "The purpose of the law firm is to aid the Communist Party and that is its purpose, yes it has to register.", "start": 889.155, "stop": 894.868, "duration": 5.71, "cleanText": [["the", "purpose", "of", "the", "law", "firm", "be", "to", "aid", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "that", "be", "its", "purpose", "yes", "it", "have", "to", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "He's paid to do that.", "start": 894.868, "stop": 896.344, "duration": 1.48, "cleanText": [["he", "be", "pay", "to", "do", "that"]]}, {"text": "He's paid to do that but they also do other things.", "start": 896.344, "stop": 899.473, "duration": 3.13, "cleanText": [["he", "be", "pay", "to", "do", "that", "but", "they", "also", "do", "other", "thing"]]}, {"text": "They also represent other clients and represent other persons in deportation cases who were not Communist such as these people.", "start": 899.473, "stop": 907.614, "duration": 8.14, "cleanText": [["they", "also", "represent", "other", "client", "and", "represent", "other", "person", "in", "deportation", "case", "who", "we", "be", "not", "communist", "such", "as", "these", "people"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "It's not enough Your Honor to be paid to represent Communists.", "start": 907.614, "stop": 911.35, "duration": 3.74, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "enough", "your", "honor", "to", "be", "pay", "to", "represent", "communist"]]}, {"text": "If you had -- the purpose of the law firm has to be to aid the Communist Party.", "start": 911.35, "stop": 915.955, "duration": 4.61, "cleanText": [["if", "you", "have", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "law", "firm", "have", "to", "be", "to", "aid", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "In other words, Wendell -- as I said yesterday, Wendell Willkie was paid, I suppose, or maybe he did it for nothing but he could very well have been paid by Mr. Schneiderman to represent him.", "start": 915.955, "stop": 927.055, "duration": 11.1, "cleanText": [["in", "other", "word", "wendell", "as", "i", "say", "yesterday", "wendell", "willkie", "be", "pay", "i", "suppose", "or", "maybe", "he", "do", "it", "for", "nothing", "but", "he", "could", "very", "well", "have", "be", "pay", "by", "mr", "schneiderman", "to", "represent", "him"]]}, {"text": "Now, his law firm didn't have to register even though somebody could say that he -- that he was aiding the Communist Party.", "start": 927.055, "stop": 935.362, "duration": 8.31, "cleanText": [["now", "his", "law", "firm", "do", "not", "have", "to", "register", "even", "though", "somebody", "could", "say", "that", "he", "that", "he", "be", "aid", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "He has the purpose that's his purpose.", "start": 935.362, "stop": 938.131, "duration": 2.77, "cleanText": [["he", "have", "the", "purpose", "that", "have", "his", "purpose"]]}, {"text": "It is subjective as well as objective.", "start": 938.131, "stop": 940.395, "duration": 2.26, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "subjective", "as", "well", "as", "objective"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 940.395, "stop": 947.725, "duration": 7.33, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's true.", "start": 947.725, "stop": 948.084, "duration": 0.36, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "true"]]}, {"text": "Well, Your Honor --", "start": 948.084, "stop": 948.742, "duration": 0.66, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "The law firm is not going to work itself.", "start": 948.742, "stop": 952.103, "duration": 3.36, "cleanText": [["the", "law", "firm", "be", "not", "go", "to", "work", "itself"]]}, {"text": "It's has to be (Inaudible) to the law.", "start": 952.103, "stop": 957.31, "duration": 5.21, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "have", "to", "be", "inaudible", "to", "the", "law"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right, Your Honor.", "start": 957.31, "stop": 957.86, "duration": 0.55, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "The Chief Justice and I -- I think we're -- we're taking it as a hypothetical, that this law firm was controlled through employing this man.", "start": 957.86, "stop": 966.1, "duration": 8.24, "cleanText": [["the", "chief", "justice", "and", "i", "i", "think", "we", "be", "we", "be", "take", "it", "as", "a", "hypothetical", "that", "this", "law", "firm", "be", "control", "through", "employ", "this", "man"]]}, {"text": "He was employed by the Communist Party to do this job.", "start": 966.1, "stop": 970.554, "duration": 4.45, "cleanText": [["he", "be", "employ", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "to", "do", "this", "job"]]}, {"text": "Let me turn to what the evidence is of -- the purpose of what the petitioner was doing and its purpose.", "start": 970.554, "stop": 976.529, "duration": 5.98, "cleanText": [["let", "me", "turn", "to", "what", "the", "evidence", "be", "of", "the", "purpose", "of", "what", "the", "petitioner", "be", "do", "and", "its", "purpose"]]}, {"text": "It was not to defend civil rights.", "start": 976.529, "stop": 979.706, "duration": 3.18, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "to", "defend", "civil", "right"]]}, {"text": "First of all, there's the objective factor.", "start": 979.706, "stop": 981.173, "duration": 1.47, "cleanText": [["first", "of", "all", "there", "be", "the", "objective", "factor"]]}, {"text": "A very large proportion of its -- of its -- the people suit, cases it handled involved Communism or some other type of subversion or some dispute whether it's 10% or 50%, it's a very large proportion far more than the proportion of subversion cases and the deportation cases generally.", "start": 981.173, "stop": 1003.214, "duration": 22.04, "cleanText": [["a", "very", "large", "proportion", "of", "its", "of", "its", "the", "people", "suit", "case", "it", "handle", "involved", "communism", "or", "some", "other", "type", "of", "subversion", "or", "some", "dispute", "whether", "it", "be", "or", "it", "be", "a", "very", "large", "proportion", "far", "more", "than", "the", "proportion", "of", "subversion", "case", "and", "the", "deportation", "case", "generally"]]}, {"text": "In addition, the petitioner -- again, this is the objective fact, it advocated repeal of many of these statutes.", "start": 1003.214, "stop": 1010.909, "duration": 7.69, "cleanText": [["in", "addition", "the", "petitioner", "again", "this", "be", "the", "objective", "fact", "it", "advocate", "repeal", "of", "many", "of", "these", "statute"]]}, {"text": "Nothing I said is anything wrong with doing this.", "start": 1010.909, "stop": 1017.78, "duration": 6.87, "cleanText": [["nothing", "i", "say", "be", "anything", "wrong", "with", "do", "this"]]}, {"text": "Now, the Communist Party used these facts in order to show that it's purportedly non-Communist organization was defending Communist Party members and protesting harassment by the Government of the Communist Party.", "start": 1017.78, "stop": 1033.938, "duration": 16.16, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "communist", "party", "use", "these", "fact", "in", "order", "to", "show", "that", "it", "be", "purportedly", "non", "communist", "organization", "be", "defend", "communist", "party", "member", "and", "protest", "harassment", "by", "the", "government", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Now, why did the petitioner do this?", "start": 1033.938, "stop": 1037.261, "duration": 3.32, "cleanText": [["now", "why", "do", "the", "petitioner", "do", "this"]]}, {"text": "Did he do it -- I suppose everything that I have said, the American Civil Liberties Union also has done.", "start": 1037.261, "stop": 1046.034, "duration": 8.77, "cleanText": [["do", "he", "do", "it", "i", "suppose", "everything", "that", "i", "have", "say", "the", "american", "civil", "liberty", "union", "also", "have", "do"]]}, {"text": "A witness testified who was a party to the choosing of the chief officer of petitioner.", "start": 1046.034, "stop": 1053.509, "duration": 7.47, "cleanText": [["a", "witness", "testify", "who", "be", "a", "party", "to", "the", "choosing", "of", "the", "chief", "officer", "of", "petitioner"]]}, {"text": "The petitioner -- two leading officers deliberately carried out the policies of the Communist Party and running petitioner.", "start": 1053.509, "stop": 1062.266, "duration": 8.76, "cleanText": [["the", "petitioner", "two", "lead", "officer", "deliberately", "carry", "out", "the", "policy", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "run", "petitioner"]]}, {"text": "Another witness testified that the third leading officer of the petitioner was acting for the Communist Party when she was an officer of petitioner.", "start": 1062.266, "stop": 1072.125, "duration": 9.86, "cleanText": [["another", "witness", "testify", "that", "the", "third", "leading", "officer", "of", "the", "petitioner", "be", "act", "for", "the", "communist", "party", "when", "she", "be", "an", "officer", "of", "petitioner"]]}, {"text": "A local branch of petitioner was setup because of the discussions by the Communist Party that it had to have an organization to defend party members against deportation.", "start": 1072.125, "stop": 1084.82, "duration": 12.69, "cleanText": [["a", "local", "branch", "of", "petitioner", "be", "setup", "because", "of", "the", "discussion", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "that", "it", "have", "to", "have", "an", "organization", "to", "defend", "party", "member", "against", "deportation"]]}, {"text": "It was setup by -- this branch was setup by a party member under instructions from the Communist Party to do this and then later on this person became the chief officer of the branch.", "start": 1084.82, "stop": 1096.342, "duration": 11.52, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "setup", "by", "this", "branch", "be", "setup", "by", "a", "party", "member", "under", "instruction", "from", "the", "communist", "party", "to", "do", "this", "and", "then", "later", "on", "this", "person", "become", "the", "chief", "officer", "of", "the", "branch"]]}, {"text": "Two other branches were setup, in order for the purpose of defending party members.", "start": 1096.342, "stop": 1103.393, "duration": 7.05, "cleanText": [["two", "other", "branch", "we", "be", "setup", "in", "order", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "defend", "party", "member"]]}, {"text": "Now, it seems to us this evidence takenas a whole establishes not the petitioner happened to defend Communists because he was interested in Civil Liberties but because he was deliberately interested --", "start": 1103.393, "stop": 1115.486, "duration": 12.09, "cleanText": [["now", "it", "seem", "to", "us", "this", "evidence", "takenas", "a", "whole", "establishes", "not", "the", "petitioner", "happen", "to", "defend", "communist", "because", "he", "be", "interested", "in", "civil", "liberty", "but", "because", "he", "be", "deliberately", "interested"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Does the record shows these local organizations are controlled by the one here in litigation.", "start": 1115.486, "stop": 1124.267, "duration": 8.78, "cleanText": [["do", "the", "record", "show", "these", "local", "organization", "be", "control", "by", "the", "one", "here", "in", "litigation"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Your Honor, I think the record is not showing -- there are no findings of the Board to that effect.", "start": 1124.267, "stop": 1131.439, "duration": 7.17, "cleanText": [["your", "honor", "i", "think", "the", "record", "be", "not", "show", "there", "be", "no", "finding", "of", "the", "board", "to", "that", "effect"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "I beg your pardon?", "start": 1131.439, "stop": 1132.318, "duration": 0.88, "cleanText": [["i", "beg", "your", "pardon"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "The record does not show control -- that kind of control over the national organization or the local organization and the Board made no findings that there was control and the reason it did not do so, was that the statute Section 3 (2) of the statute which defines the organization for the purpose of the Act is considerably broader than that.", "start": 1132.318, "stop": 1151.521, "duration": 19.2, "cleanText": [["the", "record", "do", "not", "show", "control", "that", "kind", "of", "control", "over", "the", "national", "organization", "or", "the", "local", "organization", "and", "the", "board", "make", "no", "finding", "that", "there", "be", "control", "and", "the", "reason", "it", "do", "not", "do", "so", "be", "that", "the", "statute", "section", "of", "the", "statute", "which", "define", "the", "organization", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "act", "be", "considerably", "broad", "than", "that"]]}, {"text": "It says any group of persons whether or not incorporated permanently or temporarily associated together for joint action.", "start": 1151.521, "stop": 1158.577, "duration": 7.06, "cleanText": [["it", "say", "any", "group", "of", "person", "whether", "or", "not", "incorporate", "permanently", "or", "temporarily", "associate", "together", "for", "joint", "action"]]}, {"text": "And the Court of Appeals said the national organization or local organizations were tightly woven together as it says intermeshed.", "start": 1158.577, "stop": 1166.674, "duration": 8.1, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "say", "the", "national", "organization", "or", "local", "organization", "we", "be", "tightly", "woven", "together", "as", "it", "say", "intermeshed"]]}, {"text": "I could point you all kinds of evidence to this fact.", "start": 1166.674, "stop": 1169.518, "duration": 2.84, "cleanText": [["i", "could", "point", "you", "all", "kind", "of", "evidence", "to", "this", "fact"]]}, {"text": "I suppose the most damming evidence on this point is the fact that the petitioner and the local committee said in their own publications that the local committees were a part of, that's their own phraseology a part of the national committee, affiliated with the national committee.", "start": 1169.518, "stop": 1187.486, "duration": 17.97, "cleanText": [["i", "suppose", "the", "most", "damming", "evidence", "on", "this", "point", "be", "the", "fact", "that", "the", "petitioner", "and", "the", "local", "committee", "say", "in", "their", "own", "publication", "that", "the", "local", "committee", "we", "be", "a", "part", "of", "that", "be", "their", "own", "phraseology", "a", "part", "of", "the", "national", "committee", "affiliate", "with", "the", "national", "committee"]]}, {"text": "Whenever petitioner was setting fort in its own documents, statistics concerning what it was doing, it always included the statistics of all the local committees.", "start": 1187.486, "stop": 1197.62, "duration": 10.13, "cleanText": [["whenever", "petitioner", "be", "set", "fort", "in", "its", "own", "document", "statistic", "concern", "what", "it", "be", "do", "it", "always", "include", "the", "statistic", "of", "all", "the", "local", "committee"]]}, {"text": "It never indicated that these local committees were separate.", "start": 1197.62, "stop": 1200.769, "duration": 3.15, "cleanText": [["it", "never", "indicate", "that", "these", "local", "committee", "we", "be", "separate"]]}, {"text": "I don't think -- Your Honor, I think the evidence is overwhelming that these were the same organization.", "start": 1200.769, "stop": 1206.233, "duration": 5.46, "cleanText": [["i", "do", "not", "think", "your", "honor", "i", "think", "the", "evidence", "be", "overwhelm", "that", "these", "we", "be", "the", "same", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, as I say and we have a National Legal Aid Society for instance and there are a lot of independent legal agents by these --", "start": 1206.233, "stop": 1213.963, "duration": 7.73, "cleanText": [["well", "as", "i", "say", "and", "we", "have", "a", "national", "legal", "aid", "society", "for", "instance", "and", "there", "be", "a", "lot", "of", "independent", "legal", "agent", "by", "these"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, Your Honor.", "start": 1213.963, "stop": 1214.906, "duration": 0.94, "cleanText": [["yes", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- all over the country that are more or less affiliated --", "start": 1214.906, "stop": 1218.582, "duration": 3.68, "cleanText": [["all", "over", "the", "country", "that", "be", "more", "or", "less", "affiliated"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 1218.582, "stop": 1218.651, "duration": 0.07, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- with the national organization, but at most, it's controlled, controlled by it.", "start": 1218.651, "stop": 1225, "duration": 6.35, "cleanText": [["with", "the", "national", "organization", "but", "at", "most", "it", "be", "control", "control", "by", "it"]]}, {"text": "Suppose a national organization was paid for this, you say this one was -- would all those locals have to be -- have to register?", "start": 1225, "stop": 1234.018, "duration": 9.02, "cleanText": [["suppose", "a", "national", "organization", "be", "pay", "for", "this", "you", "say", "this", "one", "be", "would", "all", "those", "local", "have", "to", "be", "have", "to", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Your Honor, I must -- the reason I'm a little hesitant to answer your question is I'm not sure of all the tie-in between the locals and the national --", "start": 1234.018, "stop": 1242.167, "duration": 8.15, "cleanText": [["your", "honor", "i", "must", "the", "reason", "I", "be", "a", "little", "hesitant", "to", "answer", "your", "question", "be", "I", "be", "not", "sure", "of", "all", "the", "tie", "in", "between", "the", "local", "and", "the", "national"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "I beg your pardon?", "start": 1242.167, "stop": 1242.178, "duration": 0.01, "cleanText": [["i", "beg", "your", "pardon"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- as far as -- the reason I'm hesitant to answer your question straight out is that I'm not -- I'm not sufficiently aware of all the interrelationship of the local groups within the national legal aid, within the legal aid framework --", "start": 1242.178, "stop": 1255.131, "duration": 12.95, "cleanText": [["as", "far", "as", "the", "reason", "I", "be", "hesitant", "to", "answer", "your", "question", "straight", "out", "be", "that", "I", "be", "not", "I", "be", "not", "sufficiently", "aware", "of", "all", "the", "interrelationship", "of", "the", "local", "group", "within", "the", "national", "legal", "aid", "within", "the", "legal", "aid", "framework"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "But you're not --", "start": 1255.131, "stop": 1255.141, "duration": 0.01, "cleanText": [["but", "you", "be", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- with the national.", "start": 1255.141, "stop": 1255.805, "duration": 0.66, "cleanText": [["with", "the", "national"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "You're not sure about the relationship here either --", "start": 1255.805, "stop": 1259.091, "duration": 3.29, "cleanText": [["you", "be", "not", "sure", "about", "the", "relationship", "here", "either"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I think the evidence is quite --", "start": 1259.091, "stop": 1259.946, "duration": 0.86, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "the", "evidence", "be", "quite"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- the record didn't show it (Voice Overlap) --", "start": 1259.946, "stop": 1261.354, "duration": 1.41, "cleanText": [["the", "record", "do", "not", "show", "it", "voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Oh no!", "start": 1261.354, "stop": 1261.877, "duration": 0.52, "cleanText": [["oh", "no"]]}, {"text": "It does not show control if control is necessary, control was not shown and the findings of the Board are not supported.", "start": 1261.877, "stop": 1269.458, "duration": 7.58, "cleanText": [["it", "do", "not", "show", "control", "if", "control", "be", "necessary", "control", "be", "not", "show", "and", "the", "finding", "of", "the", "board", "be", "not", "support"]]}, {"text": "If that is what is required, Your Honor, there's no doubt that this record does not show that kind of control.", "start": 1269.458, "stop": 1275.133, "duration": 5.67, "cleanText": [["if", "that", "be", "what", "be", "require", "your", "honor", "there", "be", "no", "doubt", "that", "this", "record", "do", "not", "show", "that", "kind", "of", "control"]]}, {"text": "As I said, the statute does not require that kind of control.", "start": 1275.133, "stop": 1280.202, "duration": 5.07, "cleanText": [["as", "i", "say", "the", "statute", "do", "not", "require", "that", "kind", "of", "control"]]}, {"text": "In order to treat an organization as a single organization for the purposes of the Act and this isn't --", "start": 1280.202, "stop": 1285.116, "duration": 4.91, "cleanText": [["in", "order", "to", "treat", "an", "organization", "as", "a", "single", "organization", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "act", "and", "this", "be", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Then why would you be more hesitant about answering the question concerning the -- concerning the legal aid bureaus?", "start": 1285.116, "stop": 1292.38, "duration": 7.26, "cleanText": [["then", "why", "would", "you", "be", "more", "hesitant", "about", "answer", "the", "question", "concern", "the", "concern", "the", "legal", "aid", "bureau"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, the reason that their evidence -- there is overwhelming evidence that these organizations were very tightly interwoven.", "start": 1292.38, "stop": 1299.823, "duration": 7.44, "cleanText": [["well", "the", "reason", "that", "their", "evidence", "there", "be", "overwhelming", "evidence", "that", "these", "organization", "we", "be", "very", "tightly", "interweave"]]}, {"text": "Now, if that's the case of the legal aid bureaus, then the answer is if the national -- let me point out, Your Honor that our evidence isn't just that the national group is controlled by the Communists.", "start": 1299.823, "stop": 1314.947, "duration": 15.12, "cleanText": [["now", "if", "that", "be", "the", "case", "of", "the", "legal", "aid", "bureau", "then", "the", "answer", "be", "if", "the", "national", "let", "me", "point", "out", "your", "honor", "that", "our", "evidence", "be", "not", "just", "that", "the", "national", "group", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist"]]}, {"text": "Our evidence is that the locals are controlled by Communists.", "start": 1314.947, "stop": 1318.075, "duration": 3.13, "cleanText": [["our", "evidence", "be", "that", "the", "local", "be", "control", "by", "communist"]]}, {"text": "In other words, the pattern is identical that -- that's why we rely on the locals.", "start": 1318.075, "stop": 1323.925, "duration": 5.85, "cleanText": [["in", "other", "word", "the", "pattern", "be", "identical", "that", "that", "be", "why", "we", "rely", "on", "the", "local"]]}, {"text": "If we only had evidence I suppose of the national, then what we would have found is that probably Mr. Forer would be here saying what's all when an organization and there are no Communist in the locals and that must show that the Communists really aren't in control.", "start": 1323.925, "stop": 1337.281, "duration": 13.36, "cleanText": [["if", "we", "only", "have", "evidence", "i", "suppose", "of", "the", "national", "then", "what", "we", "would", "have", "find", "be", "that", "probably", "mr", "forer", "would", "be", "here", "say", "what", "be", "all", "when", "an", "organization", "and", "there", "be", "no", "communist", "in", "the", "local", "and", "that", "must", "show", "that", "the", "communist", "really", "be", "not", "in", "control"]]}, {"text": "We are the converse, there are Communists both places and it's the Government that's relying on the fact that this is a single organization and the common pattern shows control by the Communist Party.", "start": 1337.281, "stop": 1348.245, "duration": 10.96, "cleanText": [["we", "be", "the", "converse", "there", "be", "communist", "both", "place", "and", "it", "be", "the", "government", "that", "be", "rely", "on", "the", "fact", "that", "this", "be", "a", "single", "organization", "and", "the", "common", "pattern", "show", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "Do you think that it will be consistent with the constitutional provision and stands to the right of counsel for the Government to make it against the law for some man that it says it's engaged in the bad undertaking, to pay -- to pay money to get him represented by a counsel.", "start": 1348.245, "stop": 1366.333, "duration": 18.09, "cleanText": [["do", "you", "think", "that", "it", "will", "be", "consistent", "with", "the", "constitutional", "provision", "and", "stand", "to", "the", "right", "of", "counsel", "for", "the", "government", "to", "make", "it", "against", "the", "law", "for", "some", "man", "that", "it", "say", "it", "be", "engage", "in", "the", "bad", "undertaking", "to", "pay", "to", "pay", "money", "to", "get", "him", "represent", "by", "a", "counsel"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, I would have a lot of trouble making an argument, Your Honor this is --", "start": 1366.333, "stop": 1371.555, "duration": 5.22, "cleanText": [["well", "i", "would", "have", "a", "lot", "of", "trouble", "make", "an", "argument", "your", "honor", "this", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "Why --", "start": 1371.555, "stop": 1371.575, "duration": 0.02, "cleanText": [["why"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- seemingly a kind of (Voice Overlap) --", "start": 1371.575, "stop": 1372.102, "duration": 0.53, "cleanText": [["seemingly", "a", "kind", "of", "voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- why is that important to the argument you're making?", "start": 1372.102, "stop": 1376.813, "duration": 4.71, "cleanText": [["why", "be", "that", "important", "to", "the", "argument", "you", "be", "make"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "The statute that -- what we are arguing here, Your Honor, has no prohibitions whatsoever.", "start": 1376.813, "stop": 1382.206, "duration": 5.39, "cleanText": [["the", "statute", "that", "what", "we", "be", "argue", "here", "your", "honor", "have", "no", "prohibition", "whatsoever"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "But it's admitted -- it's registered.", "start": 1382.206, "stop": 1385.007, "duration": 2.8, "cleanText": [["but", "it", "be", "admit", "it", "be", "register"]]}, {"text": "Everybody knows the purpose of the registry.", "start": 1385.007, "stop": 1388.466, "duration": 3.46, "cleanText": [["everybody", "know", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "registry"]]}, {"text": "Suppose you made every man who's going to help an injured to get a lawyer register, do you think if you could make him register because -- take him out because he was -- believed in something or had some purpose, would you have to make them all register alike?", "start": 1388.466, "stop": 1405.193, "duration": 16.73, "cleanText": [["suppose", "you", "make", "every", "man", "who", "be", "go", "to", "help", "an", "injure", "to", "get", "a", "lawyer", "register", "do", "you", "think", "if", "you", "could", "make", "him", "register", "because", "take", "him", "out", "because", "he", "be", "believe", "in", "something", "or", "have", "some", "purpose", "would", "you", "have", "to", "make", "them", "all", "register", "alike"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Your Honor, I -- I would suspect that we couldn't do that as to an indigent.", "start": 1405.193, "stop": 1408.663, "duration": 3.47, "cleanText": [["your", "honor", "i", "i", "would", "suspect", "that", "we", "could", "not", "do", "that", "as", "to", "an", "indigent"]]}, {"text": "The trouble was in the Communist Party case, we think the Court correctly found that this was a very serious danger to the country.", "start": 1408.663, "stop": 1415.617, "duration": 6.95, "cleanText": [["the", "trouble", "be", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "we", "think", "the", "court", "correctly", "find", "that", "this", "be", "a", "very", "serious", "danger", "to", "the", "country"]]}, {"text": "The total problem was a serious danger --", "start": 1415.617, "stop": 1417.044, "duration": 1.43, "cleanText": [["the", "total", "problem", "be", "a", "serious", "danger"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- (Voice Overlap) all he's doing is to get a lawyer for a man, when the Constitution from the first day it was written, the first day of the Bill of Rights was written, it has provided a man -- is entitled to a lawyer.", "start": 1417.044, "stop": 1428.336, "duration": 11.29, "cleanText": [["voice", "overlap", "all", "he", "be", "do", "be", "to", "get", "a", "lawyer", "for", "a", "man", "when", "the", "constitution", "from", "the", "first", "day", "it", "be", "write", "the", "first", "day", "of", "the", "bill", "of", "right", "be", "write", "it", "have", "provide", "a", "man", "be", "entitle", "to", "a", "lawyer"]]}, {"text": "How can you put any kind of penalty or punishment or burden on a man who tries to give him help to get him a lawyer?", "start": 1428.336, "stop": 1436.216, "duration": 7.88, "cleanText": [["how", "can", "you", "put", "any", "kind", "of", "penalty", "or", "punishment", "or", "burden", "on", "a", "man", "who", "try", "to", "give", "him", "help", "to", "get", "him", "a", "lawyer"]]}, {"text": "The Constitution is --", "start": 1436.216, "stop": 1437.23, "duration": 1.01, "cleanText": [["the", "constitution", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor, I really -- I must emphasize -- the burden of the petitioner is that its character will be known to non-Communists and the petitioner will no longer be able to benefit from its deception.", "start": 1437.23, "stop": 1455.683, "duration": 18.45, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "i", "really", "i", "must", "emphasize", "the", "burden", "of", "the", "petitioner", "be", "that", "its", "character", "will", "be", "know", "to", "non", "communist", "and", "the", "petitioner", "will", "no", "longer", "be", "able", "to", "benefit", "from", "its", "deception"]]}, {"text": "That is the detriment, that's the harm that I'd like to point, Your Honor to I'm sure, a passage from the opinion that you remember in your dissenting opinion on other grounds from the majority in the Viereck case, and there you pointed out that disclosure under the Foreign Agents Registration Act was not inconsistent with the First Amendment rights.", "start": 1455.683, "stop": 1475.059, "duration": 19.38, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "the", "detriment", "that", "be", "the", "harm", "that", "I", "would", "like", "to", "point", "your", "honor", "to", "I", "be", "sure", "a", "passage", "from", "the", "opinion", "that", "you", "remember", "in", "your", "dissent", "opinion", "on", "other", "ground", "from", "the", "majority", "in", "the", "viereck", "case", "and", "there", "you", "point", "out", "that", "disclosure", "under", "the", "foreign", "agent", "registration", "act", "be", "not", "inconsistent", "with", "the", "first", "amendment", "right"]]}, {"text": "It was a positive implementation of the First Amendment rights.", "start": 1475.059, "stop": 1478.687, "duration": 3.63, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "a", "positive", "implementation", "of", "the", "first", "amendment", "right"]]}, {"text": "After all, the man who gives money under deception, deceit to one of these Communist-fronts thinking that it is merely just like the American Civil Liberties Union.", "start": 1478.687, "stop": 1492.464, "duration": 13.78, "cleanText": [["after", "all", "the", "man", "who", "give", "money", "under", "deception", "deceit", "to", "one", "of", "these", "communist", "front", "think", "that", "it", "be", "merely", "just", "like", "the", "american", "civil", "liberty", "union"]]}, {"text": "He has received information that allows him to more effectively implement his rights if he gets the kind of information that this statute provides.", "start": 1492.464, "stop": 1501.893, "duration": 9.43, "cleanText": [["he", "have", "receive", "information", "that", "allow", "him", "to", "more", "effectively", "implement", "his", "right", "if", "he", "get", "the", "kind", "of", "information", "that", "this", "statute", "provide"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "Do you mean that a law was passed to protect defendants who were charged in this trial from being deceived by somebody as to what they believe in who wants to supply them a lawyer?", "start": 1501.893, "stop": 1514.312, "duration": 12.42, "cleanText": [["do", "you", "mean", "that", "a", "law", "be", "pass", "to", "protect", "defendant", "who", "we", "be", "charge", "in", "this", "trial", "from", "be", "deceive", "by", "somebody", "as", "to", "what", "they", "believe", "in", "who", "want", "to", "supply", "them", "a", "lawyer"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I'm talking about a very large number of non-Communists who support this organization financially or in other ways.", "start": 1514.312, "stop": 1524.135, "duration": 9.82, "cleanText": [["I", "be", "talk", "about", "a", "very", "large", "number", "of", "non", "communist", "who", "support", "this", "organization", "financially", "or", "in", "other", "way"]]}, {"text": "I'm also talking -- I think Your Honor, actually you're --", "start": 1524.135, "stop": 1527.093, "duration": 2.96, "cleanText": [["I", "be", "also", "talk", "i", "think", "your", "honor", "actually", "you", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "You would agree I'm sure that the Communist is entitled to have a lawyer now?", "start": 1527.093, "stop": 1530.296, "duration": 3.2, "cleanText": [["you", "would", "agree", "I", "be", "sure", "that", "the", "communist", "be", "entitle", "to", "have", "a", "lawyer", "now"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, Your Honor, of course.", "start": 1530.296, "stop": 1532.144, "duration": 1.85, "cleanText": [["yes", "your", "honor", "of", "course"]]}, {"text": "I may say also, you suggested well -- how about, how about a particular alien who was going to be deported.", "start": 1532.144, "stop": 1538.884, "duration": 6.74, "cleanText": [["i", "may", "say", "also", "you", "suggest", "well", "how", "about", "how", "about", "a", "particular", "alien", "who", "be", "go", "to", "be", "deport"]]}, {"text": "One of the petitioner's witnesses indicated that if anybody ever said anything to him, I guess it was to his relative who was going to be deported.", "start": 1538.884, "stop": 1549.466, "duration": 10.58, "cleanText": [["one", "of", "the", "petitioner", "s", "witness", "indicate", "that", "if", "anybody", "ever", "say", "anything", "to", "him", "i", "guess", "it", "be", "to", "his", "relative", "who", "be", "go", "to", "be", "deport"]]}, {"text": "If there's anything to them that about Communist aims, they would have just -- that would have -- they would have -- wouldn't want them -- the petitioner to represent them.", "start": 1549.466, "stop": 1559.882, "duration": 10.42, "cleanText": [["if", "there", "be", "anything", "to", "them", "that", "about", "communist", "aim", "they", "would", "have", "just", "that", "would", "have", "they", "would", "have", "would", "not", "want", "them", "the", "petitioner", "to", "represent", "them"]]}, {"text": "It's very possible that some of these people wouldn't have want the petitioner to represent them either if they know petitioner's true purposes, that it wasn't really to defend their rights but to be helping the Communist Party.", "start": 1559.882, "stop": 1570.981, "duration": 11.1, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "very", "possible", "that", "some", "of", "these", "people", "would", "not", "have", "want", "the", "petitioner", "to", "represent", "them", "either", "if", "they", "know", "petitioner", "s", "true", "purpose", "that", "it", "be", "not", "really", "to", "defend", "their", "right", "but", "to", "be", "help", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "To make someone represent the man.", "start": 1570.981, "stop": 1573.349, "duration": 2.37, "cleanText": [["to", "make", "someone", "represent", "the", "man"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Oh yes, oh yes.", "start": 1573.349, "stop": 1574.52, "duration": 1.17, "cleanText": [["oh", "yes", "oh", "yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "Who's at the registers?", "start": 1574.52, "stop": 1576.235, "duration": 1.71, "cleanText": [["who", "be", "at", "the", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Who was at the registers?", "start": 1576.235, "stop": 1577.407, "duration": 1.17, "cleanText": [["who", "be", "at", "the", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "Than some talk about indigent, do you have any indigent at the registry under the statute?", "start": 1577.407, "stop": 1584.08, "duration": 6.67, "cleanText": [["than", "some", "talk", "about", "indigent", "do", "you", "have", "any", "indigent", "at", "the", "registry", "under", "the", "statute"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, Your Honor.", "start": 1584.08, "stop": 1585.174, "duration": 1.09, "cleanText": [["yes", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "That issue is not here either.", "start": 1585.174, "stop": 1587.8, "duration": 2.63, "cleanText": [["that", "issue", "be", "not", "here", "either"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Do you mean that an officer of the Communist Party?", "start": 1587.8, "stop": 1591.572, "duration": 3.77, "cleanText": [["do", "you", "mean", "that", "an", "officer", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well no, let me separate --", "start": 1591.572, "stop": 1592.517, "duration": 0.95, "cleanText": [["well", "no", "let", "me", "separate"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- (Voice Overlap) whoever it is that has to register would they by registering risks the Smith Act prosecution?", "start": 1592.517, "stop": 1598.958, "duration": 6.44, "cleanText": [["voice", "overlap", "whoever", "it", "be", "that", "have", "to", "register", "would", "they", "by", "register", "risk", "the", "smith", "act", "prosecution"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, oh no.", "start": 1598.958, "stop": 1599.849, "duration": 0.89, "cleanText": [["no", "oh", "no"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Why not?", "start": 1599.849, "stop": 1601.033, "duration": 1.18, "cleanText": [["why", "not"]]}, {"text": "Why wouldn't just be at least a need to --", "start": 1601.033, "stop": 1604.134, "duration": 3.1, "cleanText": [["why", "would", "not", "just", "be", "at", "least", "a", "need", "to"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Your Honor -- as Your Honor probably is aware that under the standards of Scales and Yates, the Government is now bringing prosecutions against Communist Party members because of the difficulties of proof of incitement to --", "start": 1604.134, "stop": 1619.726, "duration": 15.59, "cleanText": [["your", "honor", "as", "your", "honor", "probably", "be", "aware", "that", "under", "the", "standard", "of", "scale", "and", "yates", "the", "government", "be", "now", "bring", "prosecution", "against", "communist", "party", "member", "because", "of", "the", "difficulty", "of", "proof", "of", "incitement", "to"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, I -- I repeat that that answers my questions --", "start": 1619.726, "stop": 1622.545, "duration": 2.82, "cleanText": [["well", "i", "i", "repeat", "that", "that", "answer", "my", "question"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well --", "start": 1622.545, "stop": 1622.591, "duration": 0.05, "cleanText": [["well"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- in fact, that you're not possibly --", "start": 1622.591, "stop": 1623.996, "duration": 1.41, "cleanText": [["in", "fact", "that", "you", "be", "not", "possibly"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, what --", "start": 1623.996, "stop": 1624.596, "duration": 0.6, "cleanText": [["no", "what"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "What I'm getting to is the -- what concerned me as you recall is the Communist Party case and that was that an officer the Communist Party would have to record by the mere self revelation that he was an officer risked possibilities of prosecutions under the Smith Act.", "start": 1624.596, "stop": 1640.764, "duration": 16.17, "cleanText": [["what", "I", "be", "get", "to", "be", "the", "what", "concern", "me", "as", "you", "recall", "be", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "and", "that", "be", "that", "an", "officer", "the", "communist", "party", "would", "have", "to", "record", "by", "the", "mere", "self", "revelation", "that", "he", "be", "an", "officer", "risk", "possibility", "of", "prosecution", "under", "the", "smith", "act"]]}, {"text": "And that's the view I took from the Communist Party case.", "start": 1640.764, "stop": 1643.059, "duration": 2.3, "cleanText": [["and", "that", "be", "the", "view", "i", "take", "from", "the", "communist", "party", "case"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 1643.059, "stop": 1643.195, "duration": 0.14, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Is this any different?", "start": 1643.195, "stop": 1644.747, "duration": 1.55, "cleanText": [["be", "this", "any", "different"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, the Communist -- the Smith Act prosecutions are connected with belonging to an organization which itself advocates overthrow of the government.", "start": 1644.747, "stop": 1653.842, "duration": 9.1, "cleanText": [["well", "the", "communist", "the", "smith", "act", "prosecution", "be", "connect", "with", "belong", "to", "an", "organization", "which", "itself", "advocate", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "As I said --", "start": 1653.842, "stop": 1654.621, "duration": 0.78, "cleanText": [["as", "i", "say"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, my question --", "start": 1654.621, "stop": 1654.711, "duration": 0.09, "cleanText": [["well", "my", "question"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- the petitioner doesn't itself advocate overthrow of the government.", "start": 1654.711, "stop": 1656.838, "duration": 2.13, "cleanText": [["the", "petitioner", "do", "not", "itself", "advocate", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "It may not.", "start": 1656.838, "stop": 1657.464, "duration": 0.63, "cleanText": [["it", "may", "not"]]}, {"text": "But I'm asking you whether an officer or one of these Communist-front organizations could comply to the registration provision and register to the Communist-front organization reveal that he was the President, would he by that revelation risk the possibility of the Smith Act prosecution?", "start": 1657.464, "stop": 1676.624, "duration": 19.16, "cleanText": [["but", "I", "be", "ask", "you", "whether", "an", "officer", "or", "one", "of", "these", "communist", "front", "organization", "could", "comply", "to", "the", "registration", "provision", "and", "register", "to", "the", "communist", "front", "organization", "reveal", "that", "he", "be", "the", "president", "would", "he", "by", "that", "revelation", "risk", "the", "possibility", "of", "the", "smith", "act", "prosecution"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Not by that alone --", "start": 1676.624, "stop": 1678.159, "duration": 1.54, "cleanText": [["not", "by", "that", "alone"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Voice Overlap) not by that --", "start": 1678.159, "stop": 1679.133, "duration": 0.97, "cleanText": [["voice", "overlap", "not", "by", "that"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, I want to -- no, I am not trying to evade Your Honor's question.", "start": 1679.133, "stop": 1682.698, "duration": 3.57, "cleanText": [["no", "i", "want", "to", "no", "i", "be", "not", "try", "to", "evade", "your", "honor", "s", "question"]]}, {"text": "I think there's no doubt that there's the possibility of incrimination by admitting that you're an officer of this group.", "start": 1682.698, "stop": 1690.787, "duration": 8.09, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "there", "be", "no", "doubt", "that", "there", "be", "the", "possibility", "of", "incrimination", "by", "admit", "that", "you", "be", "an", "officer", "of", "this", "group"]]}, {"text": "In the time that I'm going to have in the next case, I'm going to address to turn directly to the Fifth Amendment question.", "start": 1690.787, "stop": 1696.349, "duration": 5.56, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "time", "that", "I", "be", "go", "to", "have", "in", "the", "next", "case", "I", "be", "go", "to", "address", "to", "turn", "directly", "to", "the", "fifth", "amendment", "question"]]}, {"text": "I think there's -- there are many reasons why the issue was premature now, reasons that were not at least pointed out in the Communist Party case about prematurity, but I don't want to indicate that it's impossible to believe that a person could incriminate himself by admitting that he was the leader of a Communist-front organization.", "start": 1696.349, "stop": 1716.859, "duration": 20.51, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "there", "be", "there", "be", "many", "reason", "why", "the", "issue", "be", "premature", "now", "reason", "that", "we", "be", "not", "at", "least", "point", "out", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "about", "prematurity", "but", "i", "do", "not", "want", "to", "indicate", "that", "it", "be", "impossible", "to", "believe", "that", "a", "person", "could", "incriminate", "himself", "by", "admit", "that", "he", "be", "the", "leader", "of", "a", "communist", "front", "organization"]]}, {"text": "I think there is the possibility.", "start": 1716.859, "stop": 1719.039, "duration": 2.18, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "there", "be", "the", "possibility"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "Did the counsel register the Communist-front?", "start": 1719.039, "stop": 1722.656, "duration": 3.62, "cleanText": [["do", "the", "counsel", "register", "the", "communist", "front"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, that was -- that is going to be one of the things that I was going to point.", "start": 1722.656, "stop": 1725.401, "duration": 2.75, "cleanText": [["well", "that", "be", "that", "be", "go", "to", "be", "one", "of", "the", "thing", "that", "i", "be", "go", "to", "point"]]}, {"text": "Yes, Your Honor.", "start": 1725.401, "stop": 1726.551, "duration": 1.15, "cleanText": [["yes", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "The regulations are explicit, an attorney or any agent can register a front as well as a Communist-action organization, and of course such a person could -- under no circumstances, incriminate themselves.", "start": 1726.551, "stop": 1741.759, "duration": 15.21, "cleanText": [["the", "regulation", "be", "explicit", "an", "attorney", "or", "any", "agent", "can", "register", "a", "front", "as", "well", "as", "a", "communist", "action", "organization", "and", "of", "course", "such", "a", "person", "could", "under", "no", "circumstance", "incriminate", "themselves"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "Does the individual member of the Communist-front organization is the one that have to register?", "start": 1741.759, "stop": 1746.926, "duration": 5.17, "cleanText": [["do", "the", "individual", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "front", "organization", "be", "the", "one", "that", "have", "to", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, Your Honor, in addition he doesn't have to be -- let me separate all two things, one is whether the organization has to disclose the name.", "start": 1746.926, "stop": 1757.72, "duration": 10.79, "cleanText": [["no", "your", "honor", "in", "addition", "he", "do", "not", "have", "to", "be", "let", "me", "separate", "all", "two", "thing", "one", "be", "whether", "the", "organization", "have", "to", "disclose", "the", "name"]]}, {"text": "And then the second thing is if the organization doesn't disclose person's -- a person's name, that person has to register.", "start": 1757.72, "stop": 1763.824, "duration": 6.1, "cleanText": [["and", "then", "the", "second", "thing", "be", "if", "the", "organization", "do", "not", "disclose", "person", "s", "a", "person", "s", "name", "that", "person", "have", "to", "register"]]}, {"text": "Now, the organization does not have to disclose the names of its members when it is a Communist-front organization, in contrast to a Communist-action organization.", "start": 1763.824, "stop": 1774.329, "duration": 10.5, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "organization", "do", "not", "have", "to", "disclose", "the", "name", "of", "its", "member", "when", "it", "be", "a", "communist", "front", "organization", "in", "contrast", "to", "a", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}, {"text": "There is however the problem that Mr. Forer pointed out.", "start": 1774.329, "stop": 1778.531, "duration": 4.2, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "however", "the", "problem", "that", "mr", "forer", "point", "out"]]}, {"text": "The forms promulgated by the Department of Justice required a detailed financial accounting.", "start": 1778.531, "stop": 1784.73, "duration": 6.2, "cleanText": [["the", "form", "promulgate", "by", "the", "department", "of", "justice", "require", "a", "detailed", "financial", "accounting"]]}, {"text": "They provide for all contributors.", "start": 1784.73, "stop": 1787.388, "duration": 2.66, "cleanText": [["they", "provide", "for", "all", "contributor"]]}, {"text": "The question would arise whether an ordinary dues-paying member would be considered a contributor.", "start": 1787.388, "stop": 1794.253, "duration": 6.87, "cleanText": [["the", "question", "would", "arise", "whether", "an", "ordinary", "due", "pay", "member", "would", "be", "consider", "a", "contributor"]]}, {"text": "I think there is an argument, I'm sure Mr. Forer would make it if we had that case here, there is an argument that when the Congress said you didn't have to disclose members that you didn't have to disclose people who were doing just the ordinary things that a member does paying ordinary dues.", "start": 1794.253, "stop": 1812.265, "duration": 18.01, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "there", "be", "an", "argument", "I", "be", "sure", "mr", "forer", "would", "make", "it", "if", "we", "have", "that", "case", "here", "there", "be", "an", "argument", "that", "when", "the", "congress", "say", "you", "do", "not", "have", "to", "disclose", "member", "that", "you", "do", "not", "have", "to", "disclose", "people", "who", "we", "be", "do", "just", "the", "ordinary", "thing", "that", "a", "member", "do", "pay", "ordinary", "due"]]}, {"text": "Now, whether that will ultimate -- and only have -- and then what people would have to be disclosed are those who made contributions above the dues or who are not members.", "start": 1812.265, "stop": 1820.476, "duration": 8.21, "cleanText": [["now", "whether", "that", "will", "ultimate", "and", "only", "have", "and", "then", "what", "people", "would", "have", "to", "be", "disclose", "be", "those", "who", "make", "contribution", "above", "the", "due", "or", "who", "be", "not", "member"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Terris, am I correct from my recollection that under the action organization, if the officers don't register it, the statute imposes a duty upon the members to register the action organization?", "start": 1820.476, "stop": 1832.365, "duration": 11.89, "cleanText": [["mr", "terris", "be", "i", "correct", "from", "my", "recollection", "that", "under", "the", "action", "organization", "if", "the", "officer", "do", "not", "register", "it", "the", "statute", "impose", "a", "duty", "upon", "the", "member", "to", "register", "the", "action", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, no, not to register --", "start": 1832.365, "stop": 1833.216, "duration": 0.85, "cleanText": [["no", "no", "not", "to", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "It does not?", "start": 1833.216, "stop": 1834.521, "duration": 1.31, "cleanText": [["it", "do", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- the organization to register themselves.", "start": 1834.521, "stop": 1837.388, "duration": 2.87, "cleanText": [["the", "organization", "to", "register", "themselves"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "But that's not true whether the Communist-front org --", "start": 1837.388, "stop": 1838.887, "duration": 1.5, "cleanText": [["but", "that", "be", "not", "true", "whether", "the", "communist", "front", "org"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, because members themselves don't have to be disclosed.", "start": 1838.887, "stop": 1842.143, "duration": 3.26, "cleanText": [["no", "because", "member", "themselves", "do", "not", "have", "to", "be", "disclose"]]}, {"text": "In other words, anybody that has to be disclosed and is not disclosed by the organization either because it doesn't register or it leaves their name off the list has to register himself since the Communist-front organization, a member doesn't have to register doesn't have to register himself.", "start": 1842.143, "stop": 1857.772, "duration": 15.63, "cleanText": [["in", "other", "word", "anybody", "that", "have", "to", "be", "disclose", "and", "be", "not", "disclose", "by", "the", "organization", "either", "because", "it", "do", "not", "register", "or", "it", "leave", "their", "name", "off", "the", "list", "have", "to", "register", "himself", "since", "the", "communist", "front", "organization", "a", "member", "do", "not", "have", "to", "register", "do", "not", "have", "to", "register", "himself"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 1857.772, "stop": 1867.179, "duration": 9.41, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I don't know Your Honor, to be frank about it.", "start": 1867.179, "stop": 1870.525, "duration": 3.35, "cleanText": [["i", "do", "not", "know", "your", "honor", "to", "be", "frank", "about", "it"]]}, {"text": "The forms I think are not -- are not clear of on who's going to be included in that list.", "start": 1870.525, "stop": 1878.94, "duration": 8.41, "cleanText": [["the", "form", "i", "think", "be", "not", "be", "not", "clear", "of", "on", "who", "be", "go", "to", "be", "include", "in", "that", "list"]]}, {"text": "It's possible that we would be on the other side of Mr. Forer's position.", "start": 1878.94, "stop": 1882.847, "duration": 3.91, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "possible", "that", "we", "would", "be", "on", "the", "other", "side", "of", "mr", "forer", "s", "position"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "You might have then a point.", "start": 1882.847, "stop": 1884.475, "duration": 1.63, "cleanText": [["you", "might", "have", "then", "a", "point"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Pardon me?", "start": 1884.475, "stop": 1885.042, "duration": 0.57, "cleanText": [["pardon", "me"]]}, {"text": "Yes, that's quite -- that wouldn't go -- the forms certainly don't go to the constitution argument.", "start": 1885.042, "stop": 1889.934, "duration": 4.89, "cleanText": [["yes", "that", "be", "quite", "that", "would", "not", "go", "the", "form", "certainly", "do", "not", "go", "to", "the", "constitution", "argument"]]}, {"text": "If that's invalid, certainly it'll be preferable for the Government could pointed out the forms are unconstitutional and not -- and not the statute.", "start": 1889.934, "stop": 1900.03, "duration": 10.1, "cleanText": [["if", "that", "be", "invalid", "certainly", "it", "will", "be", "preferable", "for", "the", "government", "could", "point", "out", "the", "form", "be", "unconstitutional", "and", "not", "and", "not", "the", "statute"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "Oh, that's not here though now.", "start": 1900.03, "stop": 1902.631, "duration": 2.6, "cleanText": [["oh", "that", "be", "not", "here", "though", "now"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's not here now except for to the extent that petitioner argues that they -- that the registration in and of itself not to its abilities, registration in and of itself is such an interference with First Amendment rights.", "start": 1902.631, "stop": 1920.004, "duration": 17.37, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "not", "here", "now", "except", "for", "to", "the", "extent", "that", "petitioner", "argues", "that", "they", "that", "the", "registration", "in", "and", "of", "itself", "not", "to", "its", "ability", "registration", "in", "and", "of", "itself", "be", "such", "an", "interference", "with", "first", "amendment", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "I suppose that all of the money supporting this organization came from dues members and all the sources of the Government would insist that those -- they included this contribution, would they not?", "start": 1920.004, "stop": 1934.13, "duration": 14.13, "cleanText": [["i", "suppose", "that", "all", "of", "the", "money", "support", "this", "organization", "come", "from", "due", "member", "and", "all", "the", "source", "of", "the", "government", "would", "insist", "that", "those", "they", "include", "this", "contribution", "would", "they", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, you have to make a financial accounting.", "start": 1934.13, "stop": 1935.867, "duration": 1.74, "cleanText": [["well", "you", "have", "to", "make", "a", "financial", "accounting"]]}, {"text": "The question would be whether you have to disclose the names of all those people who paid dues.", "start": 1935.867, "stop": 1939.711, "duration": 3.84, "cleanText": [["the", "question", "would", "be", "whether", "you", "have", "to", "disclose", "the", "name", "of", "all", "those", "people", "who", "pay", "due"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 1939.711, "stop": 1941.232, "duration": 1.52, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "One problem here is in this particular case, I might point out, the petitioner is not a membership organization at all.", "start": 1941.232, "stop": 1947.956, "duration": 6.72, "cleanText": [["one", "problem", "here", "be", "in", "this", "particular", "case", "i", "might", "point", "out", "the", "petitioner", "be", "not", "a", "membership", "organization", "at", "all"]]}, {"text": "It's an organization in which anybody who wants to come to the annual meeting comes, and then they have a meeting and they elect some officers and that's the way the organization runs.", "start": 1947.956, "stop": 1958.692, "duration": 10.74, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "an", "organization", "in", "which", "anybody", "who", "want", "to", "come", "to", "the", "annual", "meeting", "come", "and", "then", "they", "have", "a", "meeting", "and", "they", "elect", "some", "officer", "and", "that", "be", "the", "way", "the", "organization", "run"]]}, {"text": "Apparently, that's also true with the local committees although I'm not sure of that.", "start": 1958.692, "stop": 1961.745, "duration": 3.05, "cleanText": [["apparently", "that", "be", "also", "true", "with", "the", "local", "committee", "although", "I", "be", "not", "sure", "of", "that"]]}, {"text": "Mr. Forer might know that.", "start": 1961.745, "stop": 1963.401, "duration": 1.66, "cleanText": [["mr", "forer", "might", "know", "that"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "They have to have dues?", "start": 1963.401, "stop": 1965.43, "duration": 2.03, "cleanText": [["they", "have", "to", "have", "due"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I don't think so.", "start": 1965.43, "stop": 1965.982, "duration": 0.55, "cleanText": [["i", "do", "not", "think", "so"]]}, {"text": "They don't have members.", "start": 1965.982, "stop": 1967.762, "duration": 1.78, "cleanText": [["they", "do", "not", "have", "member"]]}, {"text": "So --", "start": 1967.762, "stop": 1968.12, "duration": 0.36, "cleanText": [["so"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Forer -- is that a standard or pattern that's in the statute or is that a discretionary, not --", "start": 1968.12, "stop": 1974.191, "duration": 6.07, "cleanText": [["mr", "forer", "be", "that", "a", "standard", "or", "pattern", "that", "be", "in", "the", "statute", "or", "be", "that", "a", "discretionary", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, that's propagated by the Attorney General.", "start": 1974.191, "stop": 1979.302, "duration": 5.11, "cleanText": [["no", "that", "be", "propagate", "by", "the", "attorney", "general"]]}, {"text": "Thank you, Your Honor.", "start": 1979.302, "stop": 1980.537, "duration": 1.24, "cleanText": [["thank", "you", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Forer?", "start": 1980.537, "stop": 1982.929, "duration": 2.39, "cleanText": [["mr", "forer"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Chief Justice and may it please the Court.", "start": 1982.929, "stop": 1986.458, "duration": 3.53, "cleanText": [["mr", "chief", "justice", "and", "may", "it", "please", "the", "court"]]}, {"text": "It's just very difficult for me to believe, in fact I just find it repugnant to believe that the Government is entitled to impose this kind of destructive control of an organization which concededly does nothing but constitutionally protected laudable activities on the finding by the administrative agency that the hidden motivation, which he calls purpose, that the hidden motivation for these agencies is to help the Communist Party.", "start": 1986.458, "stop": 2017.409, "duration": 30.95, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "just", "very", "difficult", "for", "me", "to", "believe", "in", "fact", "i", "just", "find", "it", "repugnant", "to", "believe", "that", "the", "government", "be", "entitle", "to", "impose", "this", "kind", "of", "destructive", "control", "of", "an", "organization", "which", "concededly", "do", "nothing", "but", "constitutionally", "protect", "laudable", "activity", "on", "the", "finding", "by", "the", "administrative", "agency", "that", "the", "hidden", "motivation", "which", "he", "call", "purpose", "that", "the", "hidden", "motivation", "for", "these", "agency", "be", "to", "help", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well in a sense, it has to be proved.", "start": 2017.409, "stop": 2020.821, "duration": 3.41, "cleanText": [["well", "in", "a", "sense", "it", "have", "to", "be", "prove"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well --", "start": 2020.821, "stop": 2021.918, "duration": 1.1, "cleanText": [["well"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "In the sense, (Voice Overlap), there would be an equal test to be proved.", "start": 2021.918, "stop": 2029.182, "duration": 7.26, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "sense", "voice", "overlap", "there", "would", "be", "an", "equal", "test", "to", "be", "prove"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, he says hidden.", "start": 2029.182, "stop": 2030.5, "duration": 1.32, "cleanText": [["well", "he", "say", "hidden"]]}, {"text": "He says they're exposing the real nature whether it's hidden or not on the -- an ulterior motive that's what it amounts to.", "start": 2030.5, "stop": 2039.077, "duration": 8.58, "cleanText": [["he", "say", "they", "be", "expose", "the", "real", "nature", "whether", "it", "be", "hide", "or", "not", "on", "the", "an", "ulterior", "motive", "that", "be", "what", "it", "amount", "to"]]}, {"text": "He says the American committee here does nothing else let it say, leaving aside some of the activities that they don't even question, does nothing else but defend aliens in deportation cases oversimplified a bit.", "start": 2039.077, "stop": 2053.268, "duration": 14.19, "cleanText": [["he", "say", "the", "american", "committee", "here", "do", "nothing", "else", "let", "it", "say", "leave", "aside", "some", "of", "the", "activity", "that", "they", "do", "not", "even", "question", "do", "nothing", "else", "but", "defend", "alien", "in", "deportation", "case", "oversimplify", "a", "bit"]]}, {"text": "That's all it does.", "start": 2053.268, "stop": 2055.062, "duration": 1.79, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "all", "it", "do"]]}, {"text": "He says that's okay provided its motivation is to defend the particular alien.", "start": 2055.062, "stop": 2059.317, "duration": 4.26, "cleanText": [["he", "say", "that", "be", "okay", "provide", "its", "motivation", "be", "to", "defend", "the", "particular", "alien"]]}, {"text": "But if it has an ulterior motive, it not only wants to win the case for the alien who may be a Communist or a non-Communist or just accused of being a Communist, but it's an additional one to win the case for the alien that has an ulterior motive.", "start": 2059.317, "stop": 2073.627, "duration": 14.31, "cleanText": [["but", "if", "it", "have", "an", "ulterior", "motive", "it", "not", "only", "want", "to", "win", "the", "case", "for", "the", "alien", "who", "may", "be", "a", "communist", "or", "a", "non", "communist", "or", "just", "accuse", "of", "be", "a", "communist", "but", "it", "be", "an", "additional", "one", "to", "win", "the", "case", "for", "the", "alien", "that", "have", "an", "ulterior", "motive"]]}, {"text": "It isn't even a motive that the reason we want to help this alien is that it will somehow benefit the Communist Party.", "start": 2073.627, "stop": 2080.643, "duration": 7.02, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "even", "a", "motive", "that", "the", "reason", "we", "want", "to", "help", "this", "alien", "be", "that", "it", "will", "somehow", "benefit", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "He says that satisfies the aid component.", "start": 2080.643, "stop": 2082.693, "duration": 2.05, "cleanText": [["he", "say", "that", "satisfy", "the", "aid", "component"]]}, {"text": "That just sounds to me to be thoroughly outlandish and thoroughly unconstitutional.", "start": 2082.693, "stop": 2086.501, "duration": 3.81, "cleanText": [["that", "just", "sound", "to", "me", "to", "be", "thoroughly", "outlandish", "and", "thoroughly", "unconstitutional"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Are you saying that -- are you saying that the organization would not have been defending acceptable purpose of the -- its own interest for this act where he thought --", "start": 2086.501, "stop": 2100.724, "duration": 14.22, "cleanText": [["be", "you", "say", "that", "be", "you", "say", "that", "the", "organization", "would", "not", "have", "be", "defend", "acceptable", "purpose", "of", "the", "its", "own", "interest", "for", "this", "act", "where", "he", "think"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well --", "start": 2100.724, "stop": 2101.287, "duration": 0.56, "cleanText": [["well"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- or be done, it should be done and must be done the only reason for its seeming business is to help the Communist Party detriment an organization --", "start": 2101.287, "stop": 2111.923, "duration": 10.64, "cleanText": [["or", "be", "do", "it", "should", "be", "do", "and", "must", "be", "do", "the", "only", "reason", "for", "its", "seeming", "business", "be", "to", "help", "the", "communist", "party", "detriment", "an", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Justice Harlan, I must say that it seems to me that you're saying the same thing that I said he'd said.", "start": 2111.923, "stop": 2119.337, "duration": 7.41, "cleanText": [["mr", "justice", "harlan", "i", "must", "say", "that", "it", "seem", "to", "me", "that", "you", "be", "say", "the", "same", "thing", "that", "i", "say", "he", "have", "say"]]}, {"text": "The reason for doing this laudable activity the real reason, the real reason is to help the Communist Party.", "start": 2119.337, "stop": 2129.636, "duration": 10.3, "cleanText": [["the", "reason", "for", "do", "this", "laudable", "activity", "the", "real", "reason", "the", "real", "reason", "be", "to", "help", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "That's what he's saying if all --", "start": 2129.636, "stop": 2131.318, "duration": 1.68, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "what", "he", "be", "say", "if", "all"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Now, I hear you said in order to --", "start": 2131.318, "stop": 2135.647, "duration": 4.33, "cleanText": [["now", "i", "hear", "you", "say", "in", "order", "to"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well --", "start": 2135.647, "stop": 2136.032, "duration": 0.39, "cleanText": [["well"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "You're saying it now in a way that I understand the Ggovernment's position.", "start": 2136.032, "stop": 2139.382, "duration": 3.35, "cleanText": [["you", "be", "say", "it", "now", "in", "a", "way", "that", "i", "understand", "the", "ggovernment", "s", "position"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, I -- if I misled Your Honor by the use of the word ulterior, I'm sorry.", "start": 2139.382, "stop": 2143.878, "duration": 4.5, "cleanText": [["well", "i", "if", "i", "mislead", "your", "honor", "by", "the", "use", "of", "the", "word", "ulterior", "I", "be", "sorry"]]}, {"text": "But to me, when you talk about real reasons as distinguished from the actual objective fact of what you're doing, that relates an ulterior motive.", "start": 2143.878, "stop": 2154.288, "duration": 10.41, "cleanText": [["but", "to", "me", "when", "you", "talk", "about", "real", "reason", "as", "distinguish", "from", "the", "actual", "objective", "fact", "of", "what", "you", "be", "do", "that", "relate", "an", "ulterior", "motive"]]}, {"text": "Now, I don't want to quibble on the use of that word ulterior.", "start": 2154.288, "stop": 2158.775, "duration": 4.49, "cleanText": [["now", "i", "do", "not", "want", "to", "quibble", "on", "the", "use", "of", "that", "word", "ulterior"]]}, {"text": "Now, I think it is instructed to look at the kind of evidence that the Government relied on to prove for this real reason of what I call this ulterior motive.", "start": 2158.775, "stop": 2170.901, "duration": 12.13, "cleanText": [["now", "i", "think", "it", "be", "instruct", "to", "look", "at", "the", "kind", "of", "evidence", "that", "the", "government", "rely", "on", "to", "prove", "for", "this", "real", "reason", "of", "what", "i", "call", "this", "ulterior", "motive"]]}, {"text": "And I have spent although I said in my brief the whole thing is so thoroughly thought farfetched and so repugnant to me that I don't think we even have to examine the evidence.", "start": 2170.901, "stop": 2181.208, "duration": 10.31, "cleanText": [["and", "i", "have", "spend", "although", "i", "say", "in", "my", "brief", "the", "whole", "thing", "be", "so", "thoroughly", "think", "farfetched", "and", "so", "repugnant", "to", "me", "that", "i", "do", "not", "think", "we", "even", "have", "to", "examine", "the", "evidence"]]}, {"text": "I attempted in my brief to examine every evidentiary finding that the Board cited and supported that.", "start": 2181.208, "stop": 2187.469, "duration": 6.26, "cleanText": [["i", "attempt", "in", "my", "brief", "to", "examine", "every", "evidentiary", "finding", "that", "the", "board", "cite", "and", "support", "that"]]}, {"text": "And I must say that it is simply enough -- it aroused my indignation and I really think that the whole thing is an outrage to put it bluntly.", "start": 2187.469, "stop": 2199.101, "duration": 11.63, "cleanText": [["and", "i", "must", "say", "that", "it", "be", "simply", "enough", "it", "arouse", "my", "indignation", "and", "i", "really", "think", "that", "the", "whole", "thing", "be", "an", "outrage", "to", "put", "it", "bluntly"]]}, {"text": "It consist of doing things like putting on a man like John Lautner who -- a Communist who turned an informer and professional witness in the pay of the Department of Justice who knew nothing about the work of the American Committee for the Protection of Foreign Born and he gives it as his opinion, and the Board seriously relies on this.", "start": 2199.101, "stop": 2221.381, "duration": 22.28, "cleanText": [["it", "consist", "of", "do", "thing", "like", "put", "on", "a", "man", "like", "john", "lautner", "who", "a", "communist", "who", "turn", "an", "informer", "and", "professional", "witness", "in", "the", "pay", "of", "the", "department", "of", "justice", "who", "know", "nothing", "about", "the", "work", "of", "the", "american", "committee", "for", "the", "protection", "of", "foreign", "born", "and", "he", "give", "it", "as", "his", "opinion", "and", "the", "board", "seriously", "rely", "on", "this"]]}, {"text": "He gives it as his opinion that the purpose of the American Committee for the Protection of Foreign Born is to defend Communists.", "start": 2221.381, "stop": 2228.966, "duration": 7.59, "cleanText": [["he", "give", "it", "as", "his", "opinion", "that", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "american", "committee", "for", "the", "protection", "of", "foreign", "bear", "be", "to", "defend", "communist"]]}, {"text": "Now, as a matter of fact that doesn't even satisfy his definition because of -- it should be, it should have been -- Mr. Wendell Willkie's purpose when he defended Mr. Schneiderman -- to defend Mr. Schneider.", "start": 2228.966, "stop": 2242.292, "duration": 13.33, "cleanText": [["now", "as", "a", "matter", "of", "fact", "that", "do", "not", "even", "satisfy", "his", "definition", "because", "of", "it", "should", "be", "it", "should", "have", "be", "mr", "wendell", "willkie", "s", "purpose", "when", "he", "defend", "mr", "schneiderman", "to", "defend", "mr", "schneider"]]}, {"text": "And I may say also that either standards of the Board used in this case for determining this ulterior motive, I don't think Mr. Willkie would have been so well off, because there's evidence in this record that Mr. Willkie not only defended Mr. Schneider, and in the course of that as a lawyer, it was his obligation within the area of his professional responsibility to accept directions from his client to be was going to represent him at all.", "start": 2242.292, "stop": 2269.139, "duration": 26.85, "cleanText": [["and", "i", "may", "say", "also", "that", "either", "standard", "of", "the", "board", "use", "in", "this", "case", "for", "determine", "this", "ulterior", "motive", "i", "do", "not", "think", "mr", "willkie", "would", "have", "be", "so", "well", "off", "because", "there", "be", "evidence", "in", "this", "record", "that", "mr", "willkie", "not", "only", "defend", "mr", "schneider", "and", "in", "the", "course", "of", "that", "as", "a", "lawyer", "it", "be", "his", "obligation", "within", "the", "area", "of", "his", "professional", "responsibility", "to", "accept", "direction", "from", "his", "client", "to", "be", "be", "go", "to", "represent", "him", "at", "all"]]}, {"text": "But I'll tell you what else Mr. Wendell Willkie didas it appears in this record.", "start": 2269.139, "stop": 2272.685, "duration": 3.55, "cleanText": [["but", "I", "will", "tell", "you", "what", "else", "mr", "wendell", "willkie", "didas", "it", "appear", "in", "this", "record"]]}, {"text": "He wrote a letter to Mr. Abner Green the executive secretary of the committee the -- that war of the Government and he said, Dear Mr. Green, I want you to know that I think you're doing a great job.", "start": 2272.685, "stop": 2284.012, "duration": 11.33, "cleanText": [["he", "write", "a", "letter", "to", "mr", "abner", "green", "the", "executive", "secretary", "of", "the", "committee", "the", "that", "war", "of", "the", "government", "and", "he", "say", "dear", "mr", "green", "i", "want", "you", "to", "know", "that", "i", "think", "you", "be", "do", "a", "great", "job"]]}, {"text": "Keep up with this work.", "start": 2284.012, "stop": 2286.16, "duration": 2.15, "cleanText": [["keep", "up", "with", "this", "work"]]}, {"text": "And he didn't have to do that.", "start": 2286.16, "stop": 2288.235, "duration": 2.08, "cleanText": [["and", "he", "do", "not", "have", "to", "do", "that"]]}, {"text": "It wasn't essential to his representation of William Schneiderman and that is the kind of evidence that they used to determine this -- but I won't say ulterior, this real motive and this kind of thing that you inevitably get into if you go around determining real motive by something other than the objective nature of their activities.", "start": 2288.235, "stop": 2310.424, "duration": 22.19, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "essential", "to", "his", "representation", "of", "william", "schneiderman", "and", "that", "be", "the", "kind", "of", "evidence", "that", "they", "use", "to", "determine", "this", "but", "i", "will", "not", "say", "ulterior", "this", "real", "motive", "and", "this", "kind", "of", "thing", "that", "you", "inevitably", "get", "into", "if", "you", "go", "around", "determine", "real", "motive", "by", "something", "other", "than", "the", "objective", "nature", "of", "their", "activity"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "May I ask you --", "start": 2310.424, "stop": 2310.957, "duration": 0.53, "cleanText": [["may", "i", "ask", "you"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Now, so far -- now, may I just say this one thing about my -- sure.", "start": 2310.957, "stop": 2312.586, "duration": 1.63, "cleanText": [["now", "so", "far", "now", "may", "i", "just", "say", "this", "one", "thing", "about", "my", "sure"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "May I ask you the truth of the matter of this generalization?", "start": 2312.586, "stop": 2317.946, "duration": 5.36, "cleanText": [["may", "i", "ask", "you", "the", "truth", "of", "the", "matter", "of", "this", "generalization"]]}, {"text": "Are you rendering that you have a case (Inaudible)?", "start": 2317.946, "stop": 2325.425, "duration": 7.48, "cleanText": [["be", "you", "render", "that", "you", "have", "a", "case", "inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "I was one of the counsels for the Communist Party in that case, Your Honor.", "start": 2325.425, "stop": 2329.313, "duration": 3.89, "cleanText": [["i", "be", "one", "of", "the", "counsel", "for", "the", "communist", "party", "in", "that", "case", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Would you characterize this evidence in this record is (Inaudible)?", "start": 2329.313, "stop": 2335.436, "duration": 6.12, "cleanText": [["would", "you", "characterize", "this", "evidence", "in", "this", "record", "be", "inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well of course it is, of course it is.", "start": 2335.436, "stop": 2337.419, "duration": 1.98, "cleanText": [["well", "of", "course", "it", "be", "of", "course", "it", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Voice Overlap)", "start": 2337.419, "stop": 2338.242, "duration": 0.82, "cleanText": [["voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Oh, yes.", "start": 2338.242, "stop": 2338.647, "duration": 0.4, "cleanText": [["oh", "yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Where in the record says that?", "start": 2338.647, "stop": 2339.96, "duration": 1.31, "cleanText": [["where", "in", "the", "record", "say", "that"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, I take non-deviation.", "start": 2339.96, "stop": 2342.063, "duration": 2.1, "cleanText": [["well", "i", "take", "non", "deviation"]]}, {"text": "In the Communist Party case they're big -- they're a big deal leaving aside this pre-1940 evidence about the Communist International but the big deal was this evidence in non-deviation.", "start": 2342.063, "stop": 2353.287, "duration": 11.22, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "they", "be", "big", "they", "be", "a", "big", "deal", "leave", "aside", "this", "pre", "evidence", "about", "the", "communist", "international", "but", "the", "big", "deal", "be", "this", "evidence", "in", "non", "deviation"]]}, {"text": "And Justice Frankfurter have said, Look, they agreed what the Soviet Union over a best variety of topics over -- over all the years of their existence in regardless of twist and turns and that was the big deal in the Communist Party case so the Board here makes a finding in non-deviation.", "start": 2353.287, "stop": 2370.783, "duration": 17.5, "cleanText": [["and", "justice", "frankfurter", "have", "say", "look", "they", "agree", "what", "the", "soviet", "union", "over", "a", "best", "variety", "of", "topic", "over", "over", "all", "the", "year", "of", "their", "existence", "in", "regardless", "of", "twist", "and", "turn", "and", "that", "be", "the", "big", "deal", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "so", "the", "board", "here", "make", "a", "finding", "in", "non", "deviation"]]}, {"text": "Do you know what it's based on?", "start": 2370.783, "stop": 2372.7, "duration": 1.92, "cleanText": [["do", "you", "know", "what", "it", "be", "base", "on"]]}, {"text": "It said the American Committee for Protection of Foreign Born is opposed to political deportations and political denaturalization as well as every other kind and the Communist Party of the United States is also and this I suppose is a sinister opposed the statute for the deporting of Communists.", "start": 2372.7, "stop": 2389.862, "duration": 17.16, "cleanText": [["it", "say", "the", "american", "committee", "for", "protection", "of", "foreign", "bear", "be", "oppose", "to", "political", "deportation", "and", "political", "denaturalization", "as", "well", "as", "every", "other", "kind", "and", "the", "communist", "party", "of", "the", "united", "state", "be", "also", "and", "this", "i", "suppose", "be", "a", "sinister", "oppose", "the", "statute", "for", "the", "deporting", "of", "communist"]]}, {"text": "And that's the basis of their finding at non-deviation.", "start": 2389.862, "stop": 2393.003, "duration": 3.14, "cleanText": [["and", "that", "be", "the", "basis", "of", "their", "finding", "at", "non", "deviation"]]}, {"text": "Now, talking about funds, there's no suggestion here and no evidence here that the American Committee made any profits from this.", "start": 2393.003, "stop": 2403.759, "duration": 10.76, "cleanText": [["now", "talk", "about", "fund", "there", "be", "no", "suggestion", "here", "and", "no", "evidence", "here", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "make", "any", "profit", "from", "this"]]}, {"text": "In fact anybody that -- you could read directly, the idea that made any profits is really fantastic or that they ever gave a single penny to the Communist Party or that they had misappropriated funds.", "start": 2403.759, "stop": 2416.995, "duration": 13.24, "cleanText": [["in", "fact", "anybody", "that", "you", "could", "read", "directly", "the", "idea", "that", "make", "any", "profit", "be", "really", "fantastic", "or", "that", "they", "ever", "give", "a", "single", "penny", "to", "the", "communist", "party", "or", "that", "they", "have", "misappropriate", "fund"]]}, {"text": "And thought about concealment in getting money from non-Communist, how any person who gave money to the American Committee could have been unconscious of the fact that the American Committee would very likely use that money to defend among others people accused of being Communist including people as to whom the accusation even happen to be right, in anyone could believe that their money was not being used for that purpose is inconceivable.", "start": 2416.995, "stop": 2446.07, "duration": 29.08, "cleanText": [["and", "think", "about", "concealment", "in", "get", "money", "from", "non", "communist", "how", "any", "person", "who", "give", "money", "to", "the", "american", "committee", "could", "have", "be", "unconscious", "of", "the", "fact", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "would", "very", "likely", "use", "that", "money", "to", "defend", "among", "others", "people", "accuse", "of", "be", "communist", "include", "people", "as", "to", "whom", "the", "accusation", "even", "happen", "to", "be", "right", "in", "anyone", "could", "believe", "that", "their", "money", "be", "not", "be", "use", "for", "that", "purpose", "be", "inconceivable"]]}, {"text": "They would have to be deaf, dumb, and blind.", "start": 2446.07, "stop": 2448.876, "duration": 2.81, "cleanText": [["they", "would", "have", "to", "be", "deaf", "dumb", "and", "blind"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Is this record disclosed is not the whole record?", "start": 2448.876, "stop": 2451.71, "duration": 2.83, "cleanText": [["be", "this", "record", "disclose", "be", "not", "the", "whole", "record"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, it's not the whole record, but if you read the findings of the Board with any perception, their findings demonstrate how hollow their thing is.", "start": 2451.71, "stop": 2458.68, "duration": 6.97, "cleanText": [["no", "it", "be", "not", "the", "whole", "record", "but", "if", "you", "read", "the", "finding", "of", "the", "board", "with", "any", "perception", "their", "finding", "demonstrate", "how", "hollow", "their", "thing", "be"]]}, {"text": "And my brief takes up their findings and does it in terms -- some of their findings are sheer inventions like the invention that was made in the Government's brief about the International Labor Defense.", "start": 2458.68, "stop": 2468.94, "duration": 10.26, "cleanText": [["and", "my", "brief", "take", "up", "their", "finding", "and", "do", "it", "in", "term", "some", "of", "their", "finding", "be", "sheer", "invention", "like", "the", "invention", "that", "be", "make", "in", "the", "government", "s", "brief", "about", "the", "international", "labor", "defense"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Voice Overlap)", "start": 2468.94, "stop": 2469.393, "duration": 0.45, "cleanText": [["voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "What?", "start": 2469.393, "stop": 2469.962, "duration": 0.57, "cleanText": [["what"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "You have to go to the evidence?", "start": 2469.962, "stop": 2470.768, "duration": 0.81, "cleanText": [["you", "have", "to", "go", "to", "the", "evidence"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "I don't think you have to go to the evidence.", "start": 2470.768, "stop": 2473.349, "duration": 2.58, "cleanText": [["i", "do", "not", "think", "you", "have", "to", "go", "to", "the", "evidence"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, you mean the findings are on their face are --", "start": 2473.349, "stop": 2475.555, "duration": 2.21, "cleanText": [["well", "you", "mean", "the", "finding", "be", "on", "their", "face", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "I think so.", "start": 2475.555, "stop": 2476.755, "duration": 1.2, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "so"]]}, {"text": "There are very few instances where you have to go the evidence and where you do, I quote the evidence.", "start": 2476.755, "stop": 2481.331, "duration": 4.58, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "very", "few", "instance", "where", "you", "have", "to", "go", "the", "evidence", "and", "where", "you", "do", "i", "quote", "the", "evidence"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Hollow, should I have --", "start": 2481.331, "stop": 2483.227, "duration": 1.9, "cleanText": [["hollow", "should", "i", "have"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, I think the findings on that face sir are quite absurd.", "start": 2483.227, "stop": 2487.6, "duration": 4.37, "cleanText": [["well", "i", "think", "the", "finding", "on", "that", "face", "sir", "be", "quite", "absurd"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Does it stand above these when they say they have served the evidence?", "start": 2487.6, "stop": 2491.959, "duration": 4.36, "cleanText": [["do", "it", "stand", "above", "these", "when", "they", "say", "they", "have", "serve", "the", "evidence"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "You can look at their findings of the evidence and even on their own doctored version of the evidence.", "start": 2491.959, "stop": 2497.832, "duration": 5.87, "cleanText": [["you", "can", "look", "at", "their", "finding", "of", "the", "evidence", "and", "even", "on", "their", "own", "doctored", "version", "of", "the", "evidence"]]}, {"text": "Their findings, their evidentiary findings are insufficient to support their conclusory findings.", "start": 2497.832, "stop": 2503.587, "duration": 5.76, "cleanText": [["their", "finding", "their", "evidentiary", "finding", "be", "insufficient", "to", "support", "their", "conclusory", "finding"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Where is the record?", "start": 2503.587, "stop": 2505.361, "duration": 1.77, "cleanText": [["where", "be", "the", "record"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "It's here, now I imagine it's a big record, it's very -- it's big.", "start": 2505.361, "stop": 2509.76, "duration": 4.4, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "here", "now", "i", "imagine", "it", "be", "a", "big", "record", "it", "be", "very", "it", "be", "big"]]}, {"text": "It's big there's a -- awful lot of stuff in there that's about nothing but it's a big record.", "start": 2509.76, "stop": 2513.786, "duration": 4.03, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "big", "there", "be", "a", "awful", "lot", "of", "stuff", "in", "there", "that", "be", "about", "nothing", "but", "it", "be", "a", "big", "record"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible) even though that if an expert did -- did testify that they were actually with the Communist Party --", "start": 2513.786, "stop": 2526.557, "duration": 12.77, "cleanText": [["inaudible", "even", "though", "that", "if", "an", "expert", "do", "do", "testify", "that", "they", "we", "be", "actually", "with", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 2526.557, "stop": 2526.966, "duration": 0.41, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "At present, it is.", "start": 2526.966, "stop": 2528.321, "duration": 1.36, "cleanText": [["at", "present", "it", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, and may I say -- and may I say about that.", "start": 2528.321, "stop": 2532.286, "duration": 3.97, "cleanText": [["yes", "and", "may", "i", "say", "and", "may", "i", "say", "about", "that"]]}, {"text": "In the first place, the Board relied on that for its control findings and if you analyze it carefully you will see that that's all that it has to do with it.", "start": 2532.286, "stop": 2540.193, "duration": 7.91, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "first", "place", "the", "board", "rely", "on", "that", "for", "its", "control", "finding", "and", "if", "you", "analyze", "it", "carefully", "you", "will", "see", "that", "that", "be", "all", "that", "it", "have", "to", "do", "with", "it"]]}, {"text": "In the second place, this episode which -- which was flatly contradicted by Abner Green although you couldn't tell it from the Boards, a version the Court admitted that it is flatly contradicted.", "start": 2540.193, "stop": 2551.587, "duration": 11.39, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "second", "place", "this", "episode", "which", "which", "be", "flatly", "contradict", "by", "abner", "green", "although", "you", "could", "not", "tell", "it", "from", "the", "board", "a", "version", "the", "court", "admit", "that", "it", "be", "flatly", "contradict"]]}, {"text": "Even if you believe that this episode happened.", "start": 2551.587, "stop": 2554.896, "duration": 3.31, "cleanText": [["even", "if", "you", "believe", "that", "this", "episode", "happen"]]}, {"text": "In the first place according to Lautner, it happened at neither 1941 and 1942 which is 10 years or 11 years before the beginning of the critical period.", "start": 2554.896, "stop": 2566.013, "duration": 11.12, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "first", "place", "accord", "to", "lautner", "it", "happen", "at", "neither", "and", "which", "be", "year", "or", "year", "before", "the", "beginning", "of", "the", "critical", "period"]]}, {"text": "In the second place, it is still doesn't indicate why he was picked -- or why the Communist Party preferred him over another candidate.", "start": 2566.013, "stop": 2574.753, "duration": 8.74, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "second", "place", "it", "be", "still", "do", "not", "indicate", "why", "he", "be", "pick", "or", "why", "the", "communist", "party", "prefer", "him", "over", "another", "candidate"]]}, {"text": "And that there are other objections, allow me to specify.", "start": 2574.753, "stop": 2577.038, "duration": 2.28, "cleanText": [["and", "that", "there", "be", "other", "objection", "allow", "me", "to", "specify"]]}, {"text": "So far as the aid component is concerned, they rely on Lautner's opinion testimony.", "start": 2577.038, "stop": 2583.445, "duration": 6.41, "cleanText": [["so", "far", "as", "the", "aid", "component", "be", "concern", "they", "rely", "on", "lautner", "s", "opinion", "testimony"]]}, {"text": "Now, Lautner may have been an expert on the Communist Party, he was no expert on the American Committee.", "start": 2583.445, "stop": 2589.163, "duration": 5.72, "cleanText": [["now", "lautner", "may", "have", "be", "an", "expert", "on", "the", "communist", "party", "he", "be", "no", "expert", "on", "the", "american", "committee"]]}, {"text": "I'd like to say one other thing which is really prompted by a remark that Mr. Justice Goldberg made earlier.", "start": 2589.163, "stop": 2596.567, "duration": 7.4, "cleanText": [["I", "would", "like", "to", "say", "one", "other", "thing", "which", "be", "really", "prompt", "by", "a", "remark", "that", "mr", "justice", "goldberg", "make", "earlier"]]}, {"text": "The fact that I fairly touched on the control of component doesn't mean that I think that we have a weak case on the control of component.", "start": 2596.567, "stop": 2605.485, "duration": 8.92, "cleanText": [["the", "fact", "that", "i", "fairly", "touch", "on", "the", "control", "of", "component", "do", "not", "mean", "that", "i", "think", "that", "we", "have", "a", "weak", "case", "on", "the", "control", "of", "component"]]}, {"text": "It's just that there are an awful lot of points here that could be argued and for purposes of oral argument, I just had to be very selective to the point where I couldn't really say much about the controller component.", "start": 2605.485, "stop": 2617.331, "duration": 11.85, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "just", "that", "there", "be", "an", "awful", "lot", "of", "point", "here", "that", "could", "be", "argue", "and", "for", "purpose", "of", "oral", "argument", "i", "just", "have", "to", "be", "very", "selective", "to", "the", "point", "where", "i", "could", "not", "really", "say", "much", "about", "the", "controller", "component"]]}, {"text": "But I would like to give you one example, not because of the evidence itself but it's an example of what you face when you get this kind of a case.", "start": 2617.331, "stop": 2628.126, "duration": 10.8, "cleanText": [["but", "i", "would", "like", "to", "give", "you", "one", "example", "not", "because", "of", "the", "evidence", "itself", "but", "it", "be", "an", "example", "of", "what", "you", "face", "when", "you", "get", "this", "kind", "of", "a", "case"]]}, {"text": "One of the big items that the Court of Appeals singled out is evidence singled out is evidence of control is that the American Committee in 1952 referred to three decisions of this Court in the alien field and said that those decisions were terrible, they destroyed democratic rights and this Court has deserted its duty to protect the Bill of Rights.", "start": 2628.126, "stop": 2656.408, "duration": 28.28, "cleanText": [["one", "of", "the", "big", "item", "that", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "single", "out", "be", "evidence", "single", "out", "be", "evidence", "of", "control", "be", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "in", "refer", "to", "three", "decision", "of", "this", "court", "in", "the", "alien", "field", "and", "say", "that", "those", "decision", "we", "be", "terrible", "they", "destroy", "democratic", "right", "and", "this", "court", "have", "desert", "its", "duty", "to", "protect", "the", "bill", "of", "right"]]}, {"text": "And you know what was the special sinister is that the Daily Worker all said similar things about two of the decisions.", "start": 2656.408, "stop": 2664.097, "duration": 7.69, "cleanText": [["and", "you", "know", "what", "be", "the", "special", "sinister", "be", "that", "the", "daily", "worker", "all", "say", "similar", "thing", "about", "two", "of", "the", "decision"]]}, {"text": "Now, those decisions were Carlson against Landon which upheld the right of the Attorney General to hold aliens choose to be a Communist and deportation proceedings without bail, Harisiades against Landon which upheld the constitutionality of the retroactive Communist deportation statute and the Spector case which upheld the constitutionality of the self deportation law though very narrow.", "start": 2664.097, "stop": 2693.156, "duration": 29.06, "cleanText": [["now", "those", "decision", "we", "be", "carlson", "against", "landon", "which", "uphold", "the", "right", "of", "the", "attorney", "general", "to", "hold", "alien", "choose", "to", "be", "a", "communist", "and", "deportation", "proceeding", "without", "bail", "harisiades", "against", "landon", "which", "uphold", "the", "constitutionality", "of", "the", "retroactive", "communist", "deportation", "statute", "and", "the", "spector", "case", "which", "uphold", "the", "constitutionality", "of", "the", "self", "deportation", "law", "though", "very", "narrow"]]}, {"text": "In each of those -- each of those cases was sponsored by the American Committee.", "start": 2693.156, "stop": 2697.141, "duration": 3.99, "cleanText": [["in", "each", "of", "those", "each", "of", "those", "case", "be", "sponsor", "by", "the", "american", "committee"]]}, {"text": "And as a disappointed litigant, I think it had the judicial right of disappointed litigants to go to the tavern and curse out the judge.", "start": 2697.141, "stop": 2705.551, "duration": 8.41, "cleanText": [["and", "as", "a", "disappointed", "litigant", "i", "think", "it", "have", "the", "judicial", "right", "of", "disappointed", "litigant", "to", "go", "to", "the", "tavern", "and", "curse", "out", "the", "judge"]]}, {"text": "But what the Court overlooked in its hurry to see what the Daily Worker said was what the dissenters said about those opinions.", "start": 2705.551, "stop": 2714.632, "duration": 9.08, "cleanText": [["but", "what", "the", "court", "overlook", "in", "its", "hurry", "to", "see", "what", "the", "daily", "worker", "say", "be", "what", "the", "dissenter", "say", "about", "those", "opinion"]]}, {"text": "Justice Black in the Carlson case said that the majority showed a shocking disregard of the provisions of the Bill of Rights.", "start": 2714.632, "stop": 2721.669, "duration": 7.04, "cleanText": [["justice", "black", "in", "the", "carlson", "case", "say", "that", "the", "majority", "show", "a", "shock", "disregard", "of", "the", "provision", "of", "the", "bill", "of", "right"]]}, {"text": "Justice Douglas in Harisiades case said that the majority was repudiating the traditions of -- which underlay the Bill of Rights and I won't take time to quote -- but Justices Jackson and Frankfurter didn't think very much of the majority opinion in the Spector case.", "start": 2721.669, "stop": 2738.148, "duration": 16.48, "cleanText": [["justice", "douglas", "in", "harisiades", "case", "say", "that", "the", "majority", "be", "repudiate", "the", "tradition", "of", "which", "underlay", "the", "bill", "of", "right", "and", "i", "will", "not", "take", "time", "to", "quote", "but", "justice", "jackson", "and", "frankfurter", "do", "not", "think", "very", "much", "of", "the", "majority", "opinion", "in", "the", "spector", "case"]]}, {"text": "The point is that you get a situation where -- where the Courts are beguiled by this pseudo-historical discussion about in the abstract, about the menace of Communism, some Communist-front though who raises and gives money to the party, it does things which have nothing to do with this record, and the Court gets so beguiled by this theoretical abstract concept that it just departs from its responsibility to review the record in the light of the evidence in the way the Court is supposed to review the record.", "start": 2738.148, "stop": 2768.986, "duration": 30.84, "cleanText": [["the", "point", "be", "that", "you", "get", "a", "situation", "where", "where", "the", "court", "be", "beguile", "by", "this", "pseudo", "historical", "discussion", "about", "in", "the", "abstract", "about", "the", "menace", "of", "communism", "some", "communist", "front", "though", "who", "raise", "and", "give", "money", "to", "the", "party", "it", "do", "thing", "which", "have", "nothing", "to", "do", "with", "this", "record", "and", "the", "court", "get", "so", "beguile", "by", "this", "theoretical", "abstract", "concept", "that", "it", "just", "depart", "from", "its", "responsibility", "to", "review", "the", "record", "in", "the", "light", "of", "the", "evidence", "in", "the", "way", "the", "court", "be", "suppose", "to", "review", "the", "record"]]}, {"text": "And that is what happened in this case.", "start": 2768.986, "stop": 2770.721, "duration": 1.74, "cleanText": [["and", "that", "be", "what", "happen", "in", "this", "case"]]}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 2770.721, "stop": 2772.231, "duration": 1.51, "cleanText": [["thank", "you"]]}]}]}, {"transcriptTitle": "Oral Argument - December 08, 1964", "transcriptLink": "https://apps.oyez.org/player/#/warren11/oral_argument_audio/14793", "transcript": [{"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "Number 44, American Committee for Protection of Foreign Born, Petitioner, versus Subversive Activities Control Board.", "start": 0, "stop": 19.046, "duration": 19.05, "cleanText": [["number", "american", "committee", "for", "protection", "of", "foreign", "bear", "petitioner", "versus", "subversive", "activity", "control", "board"]]}, {"text": "Mr. Forer.", "start": 19.046, "stop": 21.015, "duration": 1.97, "cleanText": [["mr", "forer"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Chief Justice, may it please the Court.", "start": 21.015, "stop": 27.915, "duration": 6.9, "cleanText": [["mr", "chief", "justice", "may", "it", "please", "the", "court"]]}, {"text": "This case presents a review an order of the Subversive Activities Control Board directing the petitioner, the American Committee for Protection of Foreign Born to register as a Communist-front organization in accordance with the provisions of the Subversive Activities Control Act.", "start": 27.915, "stop": 51.349, "duration": 23.43, "cleanText": [["this", "case", "present", "a", "review", "an", "order", "of", "the", "subversive", "activity", "control", "board", "direct", "the", "petitioner", "the", "american", "committee", "for", "protection", "of", "foreign", "bear", "to", "register", "as", "a", "communist", "front", "organization", "in", "accordance", "with", "the", "provision", "of", "the", "subversive", "activity", "control", "act"]]}, {"text": "Such an order has very serious and drastic consequences to any organization to which it is addressed.", "start": 51.349, "stop": 59.58, "duration": 8.23, "cleanText": [["such", "an", "order", "have", "very", "serious", "and", "drastic", "consequence", "to", "any", "organization", "to", "which", "it", "be", "address"]]}, {"text": "In the first place, the order represents and it is accompanied by a governmental -- a governmental determination that the organization to which it is addressed is a subversive organization.", "start": 59.58, "stop": 78.536, "duration": 18.96, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "first", "place", "the", "order", "represent", "and", "it", "be", "accompany", "by", "a", "governmental", "a", "governmental", "determination", "that", "the", "organization", "to", "which", "it", "be", "address", "be", "a", "subversive", "organization"]]}, {"text": "Secondly, the organization has to acquiesce in that brand of it by the government by registering itself with the Attorney General as a Communist-front organization.", "start": 78.536, "stop": 94.055, "duration": 15.52, "cleanText": [["secondly", "the", "organization", "have", "to", "acquiesce", "in", "that", "brand", "of", "it", "by", "the", "government", "by", "register", "itself", "with", "the", "attorney", "general", "as", "a", "communist", "front", "organization"]]}, {"text": "In addition, it must file a registration statement in which it divulges to the eyes of the public and to the Attorney General with whom it has filed various details concerning its internal affairs including the names of all its dues paying members and all its contributors.", "start": 94.055, "stop": 114.823, "duration": 20.77, "cleanText": [["in", "addition", "it", "must", "file", "a", "registration", "statement", "in", "which", "it", "divulge", "to", "the", "eye", "of", "the", "public", "and", "to", "the", "attorney", "general", "with", "whom", "it", "have", "file", "various", "detail", "concern", "its", "internal", "affair", "include", "the", "name", "of", "all", "its", "due", "pay", "member", "and", "all", "its", "contributor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Byron R. White", "textObjs": [{"text": "This is for a front organization?", "start": 114.823, "stop": 118.425, "duration": 3.6, "cleanText": [["this", "be", "for", "a", "front", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 118.425, "stop": 119.175, "duration": 0.75, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Byron R. White", "textObjs": [{"text": "I thought -- I thought for action organization --", "start": 119.175, "stop": 121.487, "duration": 2.31, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "i", "think", "for", "action", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "No.", "start": 121.487, "stop": 123.052, "duration": 1.57, "cleanText": [["no"]]}, {"text": "The Communist-action organizations have to list all their members and contributors.", "start": 123.052, "stop": 130.84, "duration": 7.79, "cleanText": [["the", "communist", "action", "organization", "have", "to", "list", "all", "their", "member", "and", "contributor"]]}, {"text": "Communist-front organizations don't have to list all their members but they do have to list all the sources from which they receive their revenue.", "start": 130.84, "stop": 140.44, "duration": 9.6, "cleanText": [["communist", "front", "organization", "do", "not", "have", "to", "list", "all", "their", "member", "but", "they", "do", "have", "to", "list", "all", "the", "source", "from", "which", "they", "receive", "their", "revenue"]]}, {"text": "And under the regulations of the Attorney General in fact they have a copy of the form right there.", "start": 140.44, "stop": 146.607, "duration": 6.17, "cleanText": [["and", "under", "the", "regulation", "of", "the", "attorney", "general", "in", "fact", "they", "have", "a", "copy", "of", "the", "form", "right", "there"]]}, {"text": "They have to list the names and address of every person from whom they received a nickel.", "start": 146.607, "stop": 151.668, "duration": 5.06, "cleanText": [["they", "have", "to", "list", "the", "name", "and", "address", "of", "every", "person", "from", "whom", "they", "receive", "a", "nickel"]]}, {"text": "And that is why I was careful to say not that they have to list all their members but that they have to list all their dues paying members.", "start": 151.668, "stop": 158.886, "duration": 7.22, "cleanText": [["and", "that", "be", "why", "i", "be", "careful", "to", "say", "not", "that", "they", "have", "to", "list", "all", "their", "member", "but", "that", "they", "have", "to", "list", "all", "their", "due", "pay", "member"]]}, {"text": "They don't have to list members that don't pay their dues.", "start": 158.886, "stop": 163.62, "duration": 4.73, "cleanText": [["they", "do", "not", "have", "to", "list", "member", "that", "do", "not", "pay", "their", "due"]]}, {"text": "In addition to that, the Act imposes certain sanctions on the organization and on its members which become effective as soon as the registration order becomes effective.", "start": 163.62, "stop": 177.217, "duration": 13.6, "cleanText": [["in", "addition", "to", "that", "the", "act", "impose", "certain", "sanction", "on", "the", "organization", "and", "on", "its", "member", "which", "become", "effective", "as", "soon", "as", "the", "registration", "order", "becomes", "effective"]]}, {"text": "The organization is required to label its publications, its radio broadcast and any television broadcast as being disseminated by a Communist organization.", "start": 177.217, "stop": 191.562, "duration": 14.35, "cleanText": [["the", "organization", "be", "require", "to", "label", "its", "publication", "its", "radio", "broadcast", "and", "any", "television", "broadcast", "as", "be", "disseminate", "by", "a", "communist", "organization"]]}, {"text": "The organization is denied any tax exemptions and contributions to it are not tax deductible.", "start": 191.562, "stop": 198.812, "duration": 7.25, "cleanText": [["the", "organization", "be", "deny", "any", "tax", "exemption", "and", "contribution", "to", "it", "be", "not", "tax", "deductible"]]}, {"text": "Employees of the organization are not permitted to be on the social security roles and no government employee and no employee in a defense plan may make any contributions or perform any services for the organization.", "start": 198.812, "stop": 216.506, "duration": 17.69, "cleanText": [["employee", "of", "the", "organization", "be", "not", "permit", "to", "be", "on", "the", "social", "security", "role", "and", "no", "government", "employee", "and", "no", "employee", "in", "a", "defense", "plan", "may", "make", "any", "contribution", "or", "perform", "any", "service", "for", "the", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Are the sanction equivalent for Communist-action organizations?", "start": 216.506, "stop": 221.29, "duration": 4.78, "cleanText": [["be", "the", "sanction", "equivalent", "for", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "There are a few minor differences.", "start": 221.29, "stop": 227.537, "duration": 6.25, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "a", "few", "minor", "difference"]]}, {"text": "And I'll -- and those are basic -- those differences are basically with regard to the sanctions on the members rather than on the organization itself.", "start": 227.537, "stop": 237.531, "duration": 9.99, "cleanText": [["and", "I", "will", "and", "those", "be", "basic", "those", "difference", "be", "basically", "with", "regard", "to", "the", "sanction", "on", "the", "member", "rather", "than", "on", "the", "organization", "itself"]]}, {"text": "These that I have just mentioned, the sanctions on the organization are true of the Communist-action and Communist-front organization.", "start": 237.531, "stop": 244.34, "duration": 6.81, "cleanText": [["these", "that", "i", "have", "just", "mention", "the", "sanction", "on", "the", "organization", "be", "true", "of", "the", "communist", "action", "and", "communist", "front", "organization"]]}, {"text": "So far as the members are concerned, in both front and action organization, the members are denied employment with the Federal Government or with labor unions.", "start": 244.34, "stop": 255.988, "duration": 11.65, "cleanText": [["so", "far", "as", "the", "member", "be", "concerned", "in", "both", "front", "and", "action", "organization", "the", "member", "be", "denied", "employment", "with", "the", "federal", "government", "or", "with", "labor", "union"]]}, {"text": "In an action organization, the members can even work in privately owned defense plans or defense facilities.", "start": 255.988, "stop": 263.522, "duration": 7.53, "cleanText": [["in", "an", "action", "organization", "the", "member", "can", "even", "work", "in", "privately", "own", "defense", "plan", "or", "defense", "facility"]]}, {"text": "In the front organization, they make a nominal distinction in favor of the members of the front.", "start": 263.522, "stop": 270.209, "duration": 6.69, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "front", "organization", "they", "make", "a", "nominal", "distinction", "in", "favor", "of", "the", "member", "of", "the", "front"]]}, {"text": "Theoretically, they are allowed to work for a defense facility but only if they volunteer to the management and disclose to the management that they are members of the subversive organization, then if the management is still willing to employ them why then they can have such employment.", "start": 270.209, "stop": 290.722, "duration": 20.51, "cleanText": [["theoretically", "they", "be", "allow", "to", "work", "for", "a", "defense", "facility", "but", "only", "if", "they", "volunteer", "to", "the", "management", "and", "disclose", "to", "the", "management", "that", "they", "be", "member", "of", "the", "subversive", "organization", "then", "if", "the", "management", "be", "still", "willing", "to", "employ", "them", "why", "then", "they", "can", "have", "such", "employment"]]}, {"text": "Members of the organization are not elligible to receive scholarships or tuition loans under a federal aid education programs.", "start": 290.722, "stop": 300.937, "duration": 10.22, "cleanText": [["member", "of", "the", "organization", "be", "not", "elligible", "to", "receive", "scholarship", "or", "tuition", "loan", "under", "a", "federal", "aid", "education", "program"]]}, {"text": "Members of the organization if they are -- who are aliens cannot be -- cannot be naturalized, they are subject to deportation, and if they were recently naturalized within the preceding five years, they are liable to denaturalization.", "start": 300.937, "stop": 317.505, "duration": 16.57, "cleanText": [["member", "of", "the", "organization", "if", "they", "be", "who", "be", "alien", "can", "not", "be", "can", "not", "be", "naturalize", "they", "be", "subject", "to", "deportation", "and", "if", "they", "we", "be", "recently", "naturalize", "within", "the", "precede", "five", "year", "they", "be", "liable", "to", "denaturalization"]]}, {"text": "Now, it's perfectly obvious that the net effect of the brand, the registration, the laws of privacy, and these sanctions is to destroy any organization which like this organization depends on the goodwill of the public, to destroy the right of association in the organization.", "start": 317.505, "stop": 336.88, "duration": 19.38, "cleanText": [["now", "it", "be", "perfectly", "obvious", "that", "the", "net", "effect", "of", "the", "brand", "the", "registration", "the", "law", "of", "privacy", "and", "these", "sanction", "be", "to", "destroy", "any", "organization", "which", "like", "this", "organization", "depend", "on", "the", "goodwill", "of", "the", "public", "to", "destroy", "the", "right", "of", "association", "in", "the", "organization"]]}, {"text": "It should destroy the ability of the organization to promote its cause and to attempt to enlist public support.", "start": 336.88, "stop": 345.2, "duration": 8.32, "cleanText": [["it", "should", "destroy", "the", "ability", "of", "the", "organization", "to", "promote", "its", "because", "and", "to", "attempt", "to", "enlist", "public", "support"]]}, {"text": "Now, why was this done to this organization, and that brings me to the definition of a Communist-front organization.", "start": 345.2, "stop": 354.381, "duration": 9.18, "cleanText": [["now", "why", "be", "this", "do", "to", "this", "organization", "and", "that", "bring", "me", "to", "the", "definition", "of", "a", "communist", "front", "organization"]]}, {"text": "In order to get to that, let me first take up the definition of a Communist-action organization.", "start": 354.381, "stop": 360.711, "duration": 6.33, "cleanText": [["in", "order", "to", "get", "to", "that", "let", "me", "first", "take", "up", "the", "definition", "of", "a", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}, {"text": "That definition in substance is an organization which is substantially controlled by the Soviet Union and which operates to advance the seditious objectives attributed to the World Communist Movement in Section 2 of the Act.", "start": 360.711, "stop": 380.649, "duration": 19.94, "cleanText": [["that", "definition", "in", "substance", "be", "an", "organization", "which", "be", "substantially", "control", "by", "the", "soviet", "union", "and", "which", "operate", "to", "advance", "the", "seditious", "objective", "attribute", "to", "the", "world", "communist", "movement", "in", "section", "of", "the", "act"]]}, {"text": "And the Communist-action organization meant to refer to the Communist Party and that no one's amazement on April 20th, 1953 the Subversive Activities Control Board found that the Communist Party was the Communist-action organization.", "start": 380.649, "stop": 397.722, "duration": 17.07, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "communist", "action", "organization", "mean", "to", "refer", "to", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "that", "no", "one", "s", "amazement", "on", "april", "th", "the", "subversive", "activity", "control", "board", "find", "that", "the", "communist", "party", "be", "the", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}, {"text": "Now, a Communist-front organization has somewhat the same relationship to a Communist-action organization.", "start": 397.722, "stop": 407.156, "duration": 9.43, "cleanText": [["now", "a", "communist", "front", "organization", "have", "somewhat", "the", "same", "relationship", "to", "a", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}, {"text": "In this sense, first of all, there are two components of what constitutes a Communist-front organization.", "start": 407.156, "stop": 416.618, "duration": 9.46, "cleanText": [["in", "this", "sense", "first", "of", "all", "there", "be", "two", "component", "of", "what", "constitute", "a", "communist", "front", "organization"]]}, {"text": "First, the organization has to be substantially controlled by the Communist-action organization, that is by the Communist Party.", "start": 416.618, "stop": 424.86, "duration": 8.24, "cleanText": [["first", "the", "organization", "have", "to", "be", "substantially", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "action", "organization", "that", "be", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "I may say to begin with that this control isn't the kind of enforcible control that you could put your hand on that a master has over a servant, that a parent corporation has over a subsidiary.", "start": 424.86, "stop": 439.438, "duration": 14.58, "cleanText": [["i", "may", "say", "to", "begin", "with", "that", "this", "control", "be", "not", "the", "kind", "of", "enforcible", "control", "that", "you", "could", "put", "your", "hand", "on", "that", "a", "master", "have", "over", "a", "servant", "that", "a", "parent", "corporation", "have", "over", "a", "subsidiary"]]}, {"text": "Control for the purposes of the Act as it was interpreted in the Communist Party case is a kind of psychological disposition to whereby the body that is controlled tends to agree or with the body which controls it because of the source from which the opinion comes rather than on the basis of it's own independent judgment.", "start": 439.438, "stop": 463.634, "duration": 24.2, "cleanText": [["control", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "act", "as", "it", "be", "interpret", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "be", "a", "kind", "of", "psychological", "disposition", "to", "whereby", "the", "body", "that", "be", "control", "tends", "to", "agree", "or", "with", "the", "body", "which", "control", "it", "because", "of", "the", "source", "from", "which", "the", "opinion", "come", "rather", "than", "on", "the", "basis", "of", "it", "be", "own", "independent", "judgment"]]}, {"text": "So the first component is -- of a Communist-front organization is that is substantially controlled in this sense by the Communist Party.", "start": 463.634, "stop": 473.091, "duration": 9.46, "cleanText": [["so", "the", "first", "component", "be", "of", "a", "communist", "front", "organization", "be", "that", "be", "substantially", "control", "in", "this", "sense", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "And the second component, which is what I call in my brief the aid component has to do with what the organization does, and it must be and I quote now, Primarily operated for the purpose of giving aid and support to the Communist Party or to a Communist-action organization.", "start": 473.091, "stop": 493.707, "duration": 20.62, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "second", "component", "which", "be", "what", "i", "call", "in", "my", "brief", "the", "aid", "component", "have", "to", "do", "with", "what", "the", "organization", "do", "and", "it", "must", "be", "and", "i", "quote", "now", "primarily", "operate", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "give", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "party", "or", "to", "a", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}, {"text": "Now, I would like to take up first the -- what I consider to be the most important issue in this case and that is the Board's construction of the aid component and my contention that first the Board must construe the aid component and secondly if it'sconstruction is right the Act is palpably unconstitutional.", "start": 493.707, "stop": 512.799, "duration": 19.09, "cleanText": [["now", "i", "would", "like", "to", "take", "up", "first", "the", "what", "i", "consider", "to", "be", "the", "most", "important", "issue", "in", "this", "case", "and", "that", "be", "the", "board", "s", "construction", "of", "the", "aid", "component", "and", "my", "contention", "that", "first", "the", "board", "must", "construe", "the", "aid", "component", "and", "secondly", "if", "itsconstruction", "be", "right", "the", "act", "be", "palpably", "unconstitutional"]]}, {"text": "So far as the control component is concerned and I'll try to get to that if time permits, I have attempted in the briefs to examine the various elements on which the Board based its determination of control.", "start": 512.799, "stop": 525.451, "duration": 12.65, "cleanText": [["so", "far", "as", "the", "control", "component", "be", "concern", "and", "I", "will", "try", "to", "get", "to", "that", "if", "time", "permit", "i", "have", "attempt", "in", "the", "brief", "to", "examine", "the", "various", "element", "on", "which", "the", "board", "base", "its", "determination", "of", "control"]]}, {"text": "And in my opinion, we stablished that the Board used erroneous standards that it misconstrued the Act in numerous respects and made many evidentiary mistakes.", "start": 525.451, "stop": 536.482, "duration": 11.03, "cleanText": [["and", "in", "my", "opinion", "we", "stablished", "that", "the", "board", "use", "erroneous", "standard", "that", "it", "misconstrue", "the", "act", "in", "numerous", "respect", "and", "make", "many", "evidentiary", "mistake"]]}, {"text": "But let me first get to the aid component, in the basis on which the American Committee was held that they primarily operated for the purpose of giving aid and support to the Communist Party.", "start": 536.482, "stop": 551.697, "duration": 15.22, "cleanText": [["but", "let", "me", "first", "get", "to", "the", "aid", "component", "in", "the", "basis", "on", "which", "the", "american", "committee", "be", "hold", "that", "they", "primarily", "operate", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "give", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Now, the American Committee has been actively in business since 1933 and the first thing that we know is what it does not do that conceivably might constitute giving aid and support to a Communist-action organization.", "start": 551.697, "stop": 568.513, "duration": 16.82, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "american", "committee", "have", "be", "actively", "in", "business", "since", "and", "the", "first", "thing", "that", "we", "know", "be", "what", "it", "do", "not", "do", "that", "conceivably", "might", "constitute", "give", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "a", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}, {"text": "There is no contention, no suggestion, no evidence and no finding that the American Committee engages or has ever engaged in violence or insurrection or has advocated violence or insurrection.", "start": 568.513, "stop": 581.426, "duration": 12.91, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "no", "contention", "no", "suggestion", "no", "evidence", "and", "no", "finding", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "engages", "or", "have", "ever", "engage", "in", "violence", "or", "insurrection", "or", "have", "advocate", "violence", "or", "insurrection"]]}, {"text": "In fact, there is no contention that the American Committee has ever attempted to promote any kind of Marx's ideology or any other doctrine seeking fundamental change in society, in our society as distinguished from reforms within the structure of our society.", "start": 581.426, "stop": 600.028, "duration": 18.6, "cleanText": [["in", "fact", "there", "be", "no", "contention", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "have", "ever", "attempt", "to", "promote", "any", "kind", "of", "marx", "s", "ideology", "or", "any", "other", "doctrine", "seek", "fundamental", "change", "in", "society", "in", "our", "society", "as", "distinguish", "from", "reform", "within", "the", "structure", "of", "our", "society"]]}, {"text": "Neither is there any suggestion that the American Committee has at anytime aided the Communist Party organizationally, there is no suggestion and no finding that the American Committee is going out and recruited members for the Communist Party or that it has raised money for the Communist Party.", "start": 600.028, "stop": 619.568, "duration": 19.54, "cleanText": [["neither", "be", "there", "any", "suggestion", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "have", "at", "anytime", "aid", "the", "communist", "party", "organizationally", "there", "be", "no", "suggestion", "and", "no", "finding", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "be", "go", "out", "and", "recruit", "member", "for", "the", "communist", "party", "or", "that", "it", "have", "raise", "money", "for", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "This is what the organization does not do.", "start": 619.568, "stop": 623.02, "duration": 3.45, "cleanText": [["this", "be", "what", "the", "organization", "do", "not", "do"]]}, {"text": "Now, what does it do or what has it done that was held to constitute aiding and supporting the Communist Party.", "start": 623.02, "stop": 630.724, "duration": 7.7, "cleanText": [["now", "what", "do", "it", "do", "or", "what", "have", "it", "do", "that", "be", "hold", "to", "constitute", "aid", "and", "support", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Both the Board and the Court found that the American Committee's primary activity and in fact its only activity consisted of a best variety of activities designed to advanced the interest of the Foreign Born in this country.", "start": 630.724, "stop": 646.771, "duration": 16.05, "cleanText": [["both", "the", "board", "and", "the", "court", "find", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "s", "primary", "activity", "and", "in", "fact", "its", "only", "activity", "consist", "of", "a", "best", "variety", "of", "activity", "design", "to", "advance", "the", "interest", "of", "the", "foreign", "bear", "in", "this", "country"]]}, {"text": "There was educational works, service works such as helping people with their naturalization problems, legislative work and so forth.", "start": 646.771, "stop": 654.613, "duration": 7.84, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "educational", "work", "service", "work", "such", "as", "help", "people", "with", "their", "naturalization", "problem", "legislative", "work", "and", "so", "forth"]]}, {"text": "But the thing that bulks the largest in this case is what is called the American Committee's defense work, and this defense work consists of the defending aliens who are involved in deportation proceedings or naturalized citizens who are involved in the denaturalization proceedings.", "start": 654.613, "stop": 676.423, "duration": 21.81, "cleanText": [["but", "the", "thing", "that", "bulk", "the", "large", "in", "this", "case", "be", "what", "be", "call", "the", "american", "committee", "s", "defense", "work", "and", "this", "defense", "work", "consist", "of", "the", "defend", "alien", "who", "be", "involve", "in", "deportation", "proceeding", "or", "naturalize", "citizen", "who", "be", "involve", "in", "the", "denaturalization", "proceeding"]]}, {"text": "In those cases, the American Committee sponsors the litigation if it is asked for a sponsored litigation at all levels and if it is a litigable case from the Immigration Service to and including this Court and there has been numerous cases sponsored by the American Committee in this Court.", "start": 676.423, "stop": 696.093, "duration": 19.67, "cleanText": [["in", "those", "case", "the", "american", "committee", "sponsor", "the", "litigation", "if", "it", "be", "ask", "for", "a", "sponsored", "litigation", "at", "all", "level", "and", "if", "it", "be", "a", "litigable", "case", "from", "the", "immigration", "service", "to", "and", "include", "this", "court", "and", "there", "have", "be", "numerous", "case", "sponsor", "by", "the", "american", "committee", "in", "this", "court"]]}, {"text": "It furnishes counsel if the alien doesn't have its own counsel, it pays all expenses of the litigation.", "start": 696.093, "stop": 704.557, "duration": 8.46, "cleanText": [["it", "furnish", "counsel", "if", "the", "alien", "do", "not", "have", "its", "own", "counsel", "it", "pay", "all", "expense", "of", "the", "litigation"]]}, {"text": "And also, it is customary that the American Committee not only defends the individual in the litigation itself but it puts on the public defense forum.", "start": 704.557, "stop": 712.294, "duration": 7.74, "cleanText": [["and", "also", "it", "be", "customary", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "not", "only", "defend", "the", "individual", "in", "the", "litigation", "itself", "but", "it", "put", "on", "the", "public", "defense", "forum"]]}, {"text": "That has caused the attention of the public to a sad situation to the action generally considered arbitrary of the Immigration Service, Department of Justice, and so forth.", "start": 712.294, "stop": 724.828, "duration": 12.53, "cleanText": [["that", "have", "cause", "the", "attention", "of", "the", "public", "to", "a", "sad", "situation", "to", "the", "action", "generally", "consider", "arbitrary", "of", "the", "immigration", "service", "department", "of", "justice", "and", "so", "forth"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "And this involves a denaturalization cases as well as --", "start": 724.828, "stop": 727.778, "duration": 2.95, "cleanText": [["and", "this", "involve", "a", "denaturalization", "case", "as", "well", "as"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, relatively few of those.", "start": 727.778, "stop": 730.738, "duration": 2.96, "cleanText": [["yes", "relatively", "few", "of", "those"]]}, {"text": "For one thing, there are -- there aren't --", "start": 730.738, "stop": 731.912, "duration": 1.17, "cleanText": [["for", "one", "thing", "there", "be", "there", "be", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "Not so many of them.", "start": 731.912, "stop": 732.673, "duration": 0.76, "cleanText": [["not", "so", "many", "of", "them"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- very many of those.", "start": 732.673, "stop": 733.646, "duration": 0.97, "cleanText": [["very", "many", "of", "those"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "And the --", "start": 733.646, "stop": 734.149, "duration": 0.5, "cleanText": [["and", "the"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "The great -- but mostly deportation cases but also some denaturalization case.", "start": 734.149, "stop": 739.565, "duration": 5.42, "cleanText": [["the", "great", "but", "mostly", "deportation", "case", "but", "also", "some", "denaturalization", "case"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "All kinds of deportation cases?", "start": 739.565, "stop": 741.444, "duration": 1.88, "cleanText": [["all", "kind", "of", "deportation", "case"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, I'm coming to that.", "start": 741.444, "stop": 743.52, "duration": 2.08, "cleanText": [["yes", "I", "be", "come", "to", "that"]]}, {"text": "The record is clear and it is undisputed that the American Committee defends every alien involved in a deportation case who seeks its help without any conditions, without asking any questions and regardless of the nature of the accusation and the same thing is true of a naturalized citizen faced with a denaturalization case.", "start": 743.52, "stop": 765.607, "duration": 22.09, "cleanText": [["the", "record", "be", "clear", "and", "it", "be", "undisputed", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "defends", "every", "alien", "involve", "in", "a", "deportation", "case", "who", "seek", "its", "help", "without", "any", "condition", "without", "ask", "any", "question", "and", "regardless", "of", "the", "nature", "of", "the", "accusation", "and", "the", "same", "thing", "be", "true", "of", "a", "naturalized", "citizen", "face", "with", "a", "denaturalization", "case"]]}, {"text": "And this stems from the general position of the American Committee that it is opposed to all deportations of resident aliens no matter for what reason and it's opposed to all denaturalizations no matter for what reasons.", "start": 765.607, "stop": 780.75, "duration": 15.14, "cleanText": [["and", "this", "stem", "from", "the", "general", "position", "of", "the", "american", "committee", "that", "it", "be", "oppose", "to", "all", "deportation", "of", "resident", "alien", "no", "matter", "for", "what", "reason", "and", "it", "be", "oppose", "to", "all", "denaturalizations", "no", "matter", "for", "what", "reason"]]}, {"text": "And that policy has been publicly proclaimed that was found by the Court, there's no evidence to the contrary, mountains of evidence in its face.", "start": 780.75, "stop": 791.354, "duration": 10.6, "cleanText": [["and", "that", "policy", "have", "be", "publicly", "proclaim", "that", "be", "find", "by", "the", "court", "there", "be", "no", "evidence", "to", "the", "contrary", "mountain", "of", "evidence", "in", "its", "face"]]}, {"text": "Now, among the cases, which the American Committee has defended and is all-time -- defended at in political cases.", "start": 791.354, "stop": 801.03, "duration": 9.68, "cleanText": [["now", "among", "the", "case", "which", "the", "american", "committee", "have", "defend", "and", "be", "all", "time", "defend", "at", "in", "political", "case"]]}, {"text": "As a matter of fact, the very first case that this record shows that the American Committee that we know about, this was a 1935, the American Committee was defending the case of a man by the name of Alfred Miller.", "start": 801.03, "stop": 814.912, "duration": 13.88, "cleanText": [["as", "a", "matter", "of", "fact", "the", "very", "first", "case", "that", "this", "record", "show", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "that", "we", "know", "about", "this", "be", "a", "the", "american", "committee", "be", "defend", "the", "case", "of", "a", "man", "by", "the", "name", "of", "alfred", "miller"]]}, {"text": "Alfred Miller was a Jewish refugee from Nazi, Germany and the Immigration and Naturalization Service was trying to deport him back to Nazi, Germany and sure death on an allegation that he has been a member of the Communist Party in Nazi, Germany.", "start": 814.912, "stop": 829.022, "duration": 14.11, "cleanText": [["alfred", "miller", "be", "a", "jewish", "refugee", "from", "nazi", "germany", "and", "the", "immigration", "and", "naturalization", "service", "be", "try", "to", "deport", "him", "back", "to", "nazi", "germany", "and", "sure", "death", "on", "an", "allegation", "that", "he", "have", "be", "a", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "in", "nazi", "germany"]]}, {"text": "That's the first political case that we know of that the American Committee was defending.", "start": 829.022, "stop": 833.965, "duration": 4.94, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "the", "first", "political", "case", "that", "we", "know", "of", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "be", "defend"]]}, {"text": "But these cases were relatively few and far between among the cases defended by the American Committee until the Cold War started in 1946 when the Department of Justice started a full-scale deportation drive against the alleged members or past members of the Communist Party.", "start": 833.965, "stop": 856.455, "duration": 22.49, "cleanText": [["but", "these", "case", "we", "be", "relatively", "few", "and", "far", "between", "among", "the", "case", "defend", "by", "the", "american", "committee", "until", "the", "cold", "war", "start", "in", "when", "the", "department", "of", "justice", "start", "a", "full", "scale", "deportation", "drive", "against", "the", "alleged", "member", "or", "past", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "They brought these cases by the hundreds and thousands as the record abundantly shows.", "start": 856.455, "stop": 863.161, "duration": 6.71, "cleanText": [["they", "bring", "these", "case", "by", "the", "hundred", "and", "thousand", "as", "the", "record", "abundantly", "show"]]}, {"text": "This drive was not limited to security risks.", "start": 863.161, "stop": 866.267, "duration": 3.11, "cleanText": [["this", "drive", "be", "not", "limit", "to", "security", "risk"]]}, {"text": "It was limited to people who are nominal members.", "start": 866.267, "stop": 869.792, "duration": 3.52, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "limit", "to", "people", "who", "be", "nominal", "member"]]}, {"text": "It included people who are nominal members, it included people who were long time passed members, who had been members of the Communist Party for only a short time, people who are long time residents, who's families were disrupted, often involved a dubious evidence and it also involved some pretty harsh procedures including holding aliens without debts.", "start": 869.792, "stop": 893.163, "duration": 23.37, "cleanText": [["it", "include", "people", "who", "be", "nominal", "member", "it", "include", "people", "who", "we", "be", "long", "time", "pass", "member", "who", "have", "be", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "for", "only", "a", "short", "time", "people", "who", "be", "long", "time", "resident", "who", "be", "family", "we", "be", "disrupt", "often", "involve", "a", "dubious", "evidence", "and", "it", "also", "involve", "some", "pretty", "harsh", "procedure", "include", "hold", "alien", "without", "debt"]]}, {"text": "Now, many of the aliens that got involved in this onslaught were poor, it couldn't afford a counsel, and this is all in the record, others could afford counsel, and they went to their regular lawyers in the 1940s and their lawyers refused to represent them because they were afraid.", "start": 893.163, "stop": 910.259, "duration": 17.1, "cleanText": [["now", "many", "of", "the", "alien", "that", "get", "involve", "in", "this", "onslaught", "we", "be", "poor", "it", "could", "not", "afford", "a", "counsel", "and", "this", "be", "all", "in", "the", "record", "others", "could", "afford", "counsel", "and", "they", "go", "to", "their", "regular", "lawyer", "in", "the", "s", "and", "their", "lawyer", "refuse", "to", "represent", "them", "because", "they", "we", "be", "afraid"]]}, {"text": "And still others who got counsel and the counsel didn't know anything about the deportation cases.", "start": 910.259, "stop": 917.187, "duration": 6.93, "cleanText": [["and", "still", "others", "who", "get", "counsel", "and", "the", "counsel", "do", "not", "know", "anything", "about", "the", "deportation", "case"]]}, {"text": "And it was natural for them and many of them did it, they go to the only place that was publicly commited to defending anybody involved in a deportation case and that had the ability and the resources and the knowhow of the defendant.", "start": 917.187, "stop": 934.224, "duration": 17.04, "cleanText": [["and", "it", "be", "natural", "for", "them", "and", "many", "of", "them", "do", "it", "they", "go", "to", "the", "only", "place", "that", "be", "publicly", "commit", "to", "defend", "anybody", "involve", "in", "a", "deportation", "case", "and", "that", "have", "the", "ability", "and", "the", "resource", "and", "the", "knowhow", "of", "the", "defendant"]]}, {"text": "And the American Committee litigated as a test case not knowing at the time that this would then be considered evidence against it, the case of Peter Harisiades in which this Court upheld for the first time the constitutionality of the political grounds for deporting past membership in the Communist Party and the American Committee lost that.", "start": 934.224, "stop": 955.506, "duration": 21.28, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "american", "committee", "litigate", "as", "a", "test", "case", "not", "know", "at", "the", "time", "that", "this", "would", "then", "be", "consider", "evidence", "against", "it", "the", "case", "of", "peter", "harisiades", "in", "which", "this", "court", "uphold", "for", "the", "first", "time", "the", "constitutionality", "of", "the", "political", "ground", "for", "deport", "past", "membership", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "the", "american", "committee", "lose", "that"]]}, {"text": "It then managed somewhat later to recoup some of that ground by interpretation by winning the Rowoldt case in which the majority opinion was written by Mr. Justice Frankfurter, and more recently the Gastelum-Quinones case in which a majority opinion was written by Mr. Justice Goldberg.", "start": 955.506, "stop": 973.706, "duration": 18.2, "cleanText": [["it", "then", "manage", "somewhat", "later", "to", "recoup", "some", "of", "that", "ground", "by", "interpretation", "by", "win", "the", "rowoldt", "case", "in", "which", "the", "majority", "opinion", "be", "write", "by", "mr", "justice", "frankfurter", "and", "more", "recently", "the", "gastelum", "quinone", "case", "in", "which", "a", "majority", "opinion", "be", "write", "by", "mr", "justice", "goldberg"]]}, {"text": "The one witness in the position denote the number of cases, political cases, as compared to other cases handled by the American Committee was Abner Green, the Executive Secretary of the Committee, now dead.", "start": 973.706, "stop": 988.877, "duration": 15.17, "cleanText": [["the", "one", "witness", "in", "the", "position", "denote", "the", "number", "of", "case", "political", "case", "as", "compare", "to", "other", "case", "handle", "by", "the", "american", "committee", "be", "abner", "green", "the", "executive", "secretary", "of", "the", "committee", "now", "dead"]]}, {"text": "And Mr. Green estimated that in a 20-year period, the American Committee has sponsored somewhere between three and 4000 cases of which 350 to 400 were political cases.", "start": 988.877, "stop": 1003.523, "duration": 14.65, "cleanText": [["and", "mr", "green", "estimate", "that", "in", "a", "year", "period", "the", "american", "committee", "have", "sponsor", "somewhere", "between", "three", "and", "case", "of", "which", "to", "we", "be", "political", "case"]]}, {"text": "The Board said -- well, it didn't think the proportion was particularly significant but it thought that the proportion was much larger and it estimated about 50%, it never said on where it based its estimate and there is nothing in the record on which it based its estimate.", "start": 1003.523, "stop": 1017.92, "duration": 14.4, "cleanText": [["the", "board", "say", "well", "it", "do", "not", "think", "the", "proportion", "be", "particularly", "significant", "but", "it", "think", "that", "the", "proportion", "be", "much", "large", "and", "it", "estimate", "about", "it", "never", "say", "on", "where", "it", "base", "its", "estimate", "and", "there", "be", "nothing", "in", "the", "record", "on", "which", "it", "base", "its", "estimate"]]}, {"text": "But the fact is that both estimates were the cases in which the accusation was a Communist Party membership and frequently the accusation turned out to be wrong and in which the accusation was not only a present membership but also of past membership.", "start": 1017.92, "stop": 1034.825, "duration": 16.91, "cleanText": [["but", "the", "fact", "be", "that", "both", "estimate", "we", "be", "the", "case", "in", "which", "the", "accusation", "be", "a", "communist", "party", "membership", "and", "frequently", "the", "accusation", "turn", "out", "to", "be", "wrong", "and", "in", "which", "the", "accusation", "be", "not", "only", "a", "present", "membership", "but", "also", "of", "past", "membership"]]}, {"text": "Now, when -- when the American Committee got involved in this case to this extent and in view of the atmosphere, the time at that point, the American Committee stopped being a respectable organization as far as the Government was concerned.", "start": 1034.825, "stop": 1047.234, "duration": 12.41, "cleanText": [["now", "when", "when", "the", "american", "committee", "get", "involve", "in", "this", "case", "to", "this", "extent", "and", "in", "view", "of", "the", "atmosphere", "the", "time", "at", "that", "point", "the", "american", "committee", "stop", "be", "a", "respectable", "organization", "as", "far", "as", "the", "government", "be", "concern"]]}, {"text": "Government officials no longer came to speak on its affairs and it made the Attorney General's list of subversive organizations in 1949.", "start": 1047.234, "stop": 1057.461, "duration": 10.23, "cleanText": [["government", "official", "no", "longer", "come", "to", "speak", "on", "its", "affair", "and", "it", "make", "the", "attorney", "general", "s", "list", "of", "subversive", "organization", "in"]]}, {"text": "Now, the Board's theory is that in determining that the meaning of the aid components of what is giving aid and support to the Communist Party, they said it doesn't matter what the organization actually does, it is what they called the motive -- purpose by which they meant motive for what Board does.", "start": 1057.461, "stop": 1077.748, "duration": 20.29, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "board", "s", "theory", "be", "that", "in", "determine", "that", "the", "meaning", "of", "the", "aid", "component", "of", "what", "be", "give", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "party", "they", "say", "it", "do", "not", "matter", "what", "the", "organization", "actually", "do", "it", "be", "what", "they", "call", "the", "motive", "purpose", "by", "which", "they", "mean", "motive", "for", "what", "board", "do"]]}, {"text": "And the Board found that the primary motive or primary purpose they call to the American Committee was to defend the members of theCommunist Party in deportation cases and it recognizes that they are always non-Communist cases, but it said that that wasn't inconsistent with its primary motivation, its primary purpose.", "start": 1077.748, "stop": 1103.207, "duration": 25.46, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "board", "find", "that", "the", "primary", "motive", "or", "primary", "purpose", "they", "call", "to", "the", "american", "committee", "be", "to", "defend", "the", "member", "of", "thecommunist", "party", "in", "deportation", "case", "and", "it", "recognize", "that", "they", "be", "always", "non", "communist", "case", "but", "it", "say", "that", "that", "be", "not", "inconsistent", "with", "its", "primary", "motivation", "its", "primary", "purpose"]]}, {"text": "And on that basis, it held that the American Committee satisfied the aid component of a Communist-front definition.", "start": 1103.207, "stop": 1112.103, "duration": 8.9, "cleanText": [["and", "on", "that", "basis", "it", "hold", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "satisfy", "the", "aid", "component", "of", "a", "communist", "front", "definition"]]}, {"text": "Now, I may say that the evidence on which they drew this inference of motive seems to me that the -- well, it just outlandish and I have a whole section of the brief devoted to each bit of evidence from which they drew that inference but I can't get into that now.", "start": 1112.103, "stop": 1131.075, "duration": 18.97, "cleanText": [["now", "i", "may", "say", "that", "the", "evidence", "on", "which", "they", "draw", "this", "inference", "of", "motive", "seem", "to", "me", "that", "the", "well", "it", "just", "outlandish", "and", "i", "have", "a", "whole", "section", "of", "the", "brief", "devote", "to", "each", "bit", "of", "evidence", "from", "which", "they", "draw", "that", "inference", "but", "i", "can", "not", "get", "into", "that", "now"]]}, {"text": "But that was the theory of the Board.", "start": 1131.075, "stop": 1134.113, "duration": 3.04, "cleanText": [["but", "that", "be", "the", "theory", "of", "the", "board"]]}, {"text": "Now, the Court of Appeals had a somewhat different theory.", "start": 1134.113, "stop": 1138.862, "duration": 4.75, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "have", "a", "somewhat", "different", "theory"]]}, {"text": "It didn't talk about motive, it said, Yes, the major emphasis of the Committee's work was this defense activity and it said This -- this defense of every alien that sought its help was a very laudable thing.", "start": 1138.862, "stop": 1155.676, "duration": 16.81, "cleanText": [["it", "do", "not", "talk", "about", "motive", "it", "say", "yes", "the", "major", "emphasis", "of", "the", "committee", "s", "work", "be", "this", "defense", "activity", "and", "it", "say", "this", "this", "defense", "of", "every", "alien", "that", "seek", "its", "help", "be", "a", "very", "laudable", "thing"]]}, {"text": "As a matter of fact, many of the cases that the American Committee won, were won in that very court.", "start": 1155.676, "stop": 1161.429, "duration": 5.75, "cleanText": [["as", "a", "matter", "of", "fact", "many", "of", "the", "case", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "win", "we", "be", "win", "in", "that", "very", "court"]]}, {"text": "It said it was a very laudable thing but this laudable activity constituted aid and support to the Communist Party and therefore made the organization subversive in two ways.", "start": 1161.429, "stop": 1172.146, "duration": 10.72, "cleanText": [["it", "say", "it", "be", "a", "very", "laudable", "thing", "but", "this", "laudable", "activity", "constitute", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "therefore", "make", "the", "organization", "subversive", "in", "two", "way"]]}, {"text": "First of all, it said some of the aliens whom it defended were accused of being Communist and some of them those who were so accused actually happened to be Communist, and in so far as the American Committee defended people who were members of the Communist Party.", "start": 1172.146, "stop": 1188.095, "duration": 15.95, "cleanText": [["first", "of", "all", "it", "say", "some", "of", "the", "alien", "whom", "it", "defend", "we", "be", "accuse", "of", "be", "communist", "and", "some", "of", "them", "those", "who", "we", "be", "so", "accuse", "actually", "happen", "to", "be", "communist", "and", "in", "so", "far", "as", "the", "american", "committee", "defend", "people", "who", "we", "be", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "They said, Obviously, that benefited the Communist Party and therefore in that respect the American Committee satisfied the aid component by aiding the Communist Party.", "start": 1188.095, "stop": 1198.103, "duration": 10.01, "cleanText": [["they", "say", "obviously", "that", "benefit", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "therefore", "in", "that", "respect", "the", "american", "committee", "satisfy", "the", "aid", "component", "by", "aid", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "But it said there was a more subtle way in which the American Committee aided the Communist Party.", "start": 1198.103, "stop": 1203.757, "duration": 5.65, "cleanText": [["but", "it", "say", "there", "be", "a", "more", "subtle", "way", "in", "which", "the", "american", "committee", "aid", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "It says the American Committee goes around engaging in all these laudable activities having laudable objectives and doing good deeds and it gets a lot of public credit for it and it said that helps the Ameri -- that helps the public image of the Communist Party.", "start": 1203.757, "stop": 1215.219, "duration": 11.46, "cleanText": [["it", "say", "the", "american", "committee", "go", "around", "engage", "in", "all", "these", "laudable", "activity", "have", "laudable", "objective", "and", "do", "good", "deed", "and", "it", "get", "a", "lot", "of", "public", "credit", "for", "it", "and", "it", "say", "that", "help", "the", "ameri", "that", "help", "the", "public", "image", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "And in that way, in this subtle way, the American Committee helps the Communist Party because the Communist Party gets credit for the good deeds of the American Committee.", "start": 1215.219, "stop": 1234.501, "duration": 19.28, "cleanText": [["and", "in", "that", "way", "in", "this", "subtle", "way", "the", "american", "committee", "help", "the", "communist", "party", "because", "the", "communist", "party", "get", "credit", "for", "the", "good", "deed", "of", "the", "american", "committee"]]}, {"text": "This on the face of it seems to me to be preposterous.", "start": 1234.501, "stop": 1238.805, "duration": 4.3, "cleanText": [["this", "on", "the", "face", "of", "it", "seem", "to", "me", "to", "be", "preposterous"]]}, {"text": "In any event, the Government's brief now repudiates that theory because it is manifestedly inconsistent with the Government's contention that one of the things that distinguishes and makes it necessary to apply the Act to Communist-front organizations is that they hide their connections with the Communist Party.", "start": 1238.805, "stop": 1258.376, "duration": 19.57, "cleanText": [["in", "any", "event", "the", "government", "s", "brief", "now", "repudiate", "that", "theory", "because", "it", "be", "manifestedly", "inconsistent", "with", "the", "government", "s", "contention", "that", "one", "of", "the", "thing", "that", "distinguishes", "and", "make", "it", "necessary", "to", "apply", "the", "act", "to", "communist", "front", "organization", "be", "that", "they", "hide", "their", "connection", "with", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Well, if they hide their connections with the Communist Party, it doesn't make any sense to say that the Communist Party gets credit for their good deeds.", "start": 1258.376, "stop": 1266.621, "duration": 8.25, "cleanText": [["well", "if", "they", "hide", "their", "connection", "with", "the", "communist", "party", "it", "do", "not", "make", "any", "sense", "to", "say", "that", "the", "communist", "party", "get", "credit", "for", "their", "good", "deed"]]}, {"text": "So that is repudiated by the Government and we come down to the proposition that the sin of the American Committee, the thing that makes the American Committee satisfy the aid component of the Act is that it depends among other aliens, persons who actually are members of the Communist Party.", "start": 1266.621, "stop": 1285.435, "duration": 18.81, "cleanText": [["so", "that", "be", "repudiate", "by", "the", "government", "and", "we", "come", "down", "to", "the", "proposition", "that", "the", "sin", "of", "the", "american", "committee", "the", "thing", "that", "make", "the", "american", "committee", "satisfy", "the", "aid", "component", "of", "the", "act", "be", "that", "it", "depend", "among", "other", "alien", "person", "who", "actually", "be", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Was there any evidence that the organization was doing things other than these activities that you're referring to?", "start": 1285.435, "stop": 1294.627, "duration": 9.19, "cleanText": [["be", "there", "any", "evidence", "that", "the", "organization", "be", "do", "thing", "other", "than", "these", "activity", "that", "you", "be", "refer", "to"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "No sir.", "start": 1294.627, "stop": 1297.024, "duration": 2.4, "cleanText": [["no", "sir"]]}, {"text": "The -- and that again is examined in detail in the brief, I may say incidentally, Mr. Justice Harlan, that the of course the aid component talked about its primary activity, so even if there were, it would still be a question of what its primary activities are.", "start": 1297.024, "stop": 1313.512, "duration": 16.49, "cleanText": [["the", "and", "that", "again", "be", "examine", "in", "detail", "in", "the", "brief", "i", "may", "say", "incidentally", "mr", "justice", "harlan", "that", "the", "of", "course", "the", "aid", "component", "talk", "about", "its", "primary", "activity", "so", "even", "if", "there", "we", "be", "it", "would", "still", "be", "a", "question", "of", "what", "its", "primary", "activity", "be"]]}, {"text": "But there is no eivdence that the American Committee did anything but seek to advance the interest of the Foreign Born according to its light.", "start": 1313.512, "stop": 1321.62, "duration": 8.11, "cleanText": [["but", "there", "be", "no", "eivdence", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "do", "anything", "but", "seek", "to", "advance", "the", "interest", "of", "the", "foreign", "born", "accord", "to", "its", "light"]]}, {"text": "Now, what the Board did and what the Government does in its brief, American Committee puts out a 47-page pamphlet written by Abner Green.", "start": 1321.62, "stop": 1330.728, "duration": 9.11, "cleanText": [["now", "what", "the", "board", "do", "and", "what", "the", "government", "do", "in", "its", "brief", "american", "committee", "put", "out", "a", "page", "pamphlet", "write", "by", "abner", "green"]]}, {"text": "This pro style, the Board couldn't stand and neither can the Government apparently.", "start": 1330.728, "stop": 1335.854, "duration": 5.13, "cleanText": [["this", "pro", "style", "the", "board", "could", "not", "stand", "and", "neither", "can", "the", "government", "apparently"]]}, {"text": "And in this 47-page pamphlet, he theorizes about why do you have these kind of political deportation, it says it's part of the whole atmosphere caused by persecuting Communists in the Smith Act prosecutions and so forth.", "start": 1335.854, "stop": 1349.477, "duration": 13.62, "cleanText": [["and", "in", "this", "page", "pamphlet", "he", "theorize", "about", "why", "do", "you", "have", "these", "kind", "of", "political", "deportation", "it", "say", "it", "be", "part", "of", "the", "whole", "atmosphere", "cause", "by", "persecute", "communist", "in", "the", "smith", "act", "prosecution", "and", "so", "forth"]]}, {"text": "So out of the 47-page pamhplet dealing with deportation cases, the Board picks out one sentence in which he says look at the Smith Act and look at the Rosenberg cases, and say, See the American Committee is the party from this purpose.", "start": 1349.477, "stop": 1363.355, "duration": 13.88, "cleanText": [["so", "out", "of", "the", "page", "pamhplet", "deal", "with", "deportation", "case", "the", "board", "pick", "out", "one", "sentence", "in", "which", "he", "say", "look", "at", "the", "smith", "act", "and", "look", "at", "the", "rosenberg", "case", "and", "say", "see", "the", "american", "committee", "be", "the", "party", "from", "this", "purpose"]]}, {"text": "All those things are examined and in my opinion, that's what I meant when I said the outlandish basis on which the Board infered its purpose and I'll go into that in detail.", "start": 1363.355, "stop": 1375.395, "duration": 12.04, "cleanText": [["all", "those", "thing", "be", "examine", "and", "in", "my", "opinion", "that", "be", "what", "i", "mean", "when", "i", "say", "the", "outlandish", "basis", "on", "which", "the", "board", "infer", "its", "purpose", "and", "I", "will", "go", "into", "that", "in", "detail"]]}, {"text": "The point I am making now is that there is no question on this record and from the findings of the Board and from the findings of the Court of Appeals that the American Committee sin was that it defends Communist in depotation cases.", "start": 1375.395, "stop": 1389.838, "duration": 14.44, "cleanText": [["the", "point", "i", "be", "make", "now", "be", "that", "there", "be", "no", "question", "on", "this", "record", "and", "from", "the", "finding", "of", "the", "board", "and", "from", "the", "finding", "of", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "that", "the", "american", "committee", "sin", "be", "that", "it", "defend", "communist", "in", "depotation", "case"]]}, {"text": "Now, I suppose that that sin is compounded because it had so often won some of those cases, of course, aided and defended in that respect by the federal courts, sometimes including this one.", "start": 1389.838, "stop": 1400.399, "duration": 10.56, "cleanText": [["now", "i", "suppose", "that", "that", "sin", "be", "compound", "because", "it", "have", "so", "often", "win", "some", "of", "those", "case", "of", "course", "aid", "and", "defend", "in", "that", "respect", "by", "the", "federal", "court", "sometimes", "include", "this", "one"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Not to the part of excluding the Government --", "start": 1400.399, "stop": 1402.414, "duration": 2.02, "cleanText": [["not", "to", "the", "part", "of", "exclude", "the", "government"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "What?", "start": 1402.414, "stop": 1403.147, "duration": 0.73, "cleanText": [["what"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- represented them in part and still the Government denies it, the other part (Voice Overlap) --", "start": 1403.147, "stop": 1406.631, "duration": 3.48, "cleanText": [["represent", "them", "in", "part", "and", "still", "the", "government", "deny", "it", "the", "other", "part", "voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "The other part is --", "start": 1406.631, "stop": 1407.702, "duration": 1.07, "cleanText": [["the", "other", "part", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- is control.", "start": 1407.702, "stop": 1408.036, "duration": 0.33, "cleanText": [["be", "control"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- control.", "start": 1408.036, "stop": 1409.837, "duration": 1.8, "cleanText": [["control"]]}, {"text": "But you have to have both sins in order to meet the statutory definition.", "start": 1409.837, "stop": 1415.792, "duration": 5.95, "cleanText": [["but", "you", "have", "to", "have", "both", "sin", "in", "order", "to", "meet", "the", "statutory", "definition"]]}, {"text": "Now, first I want to say that we think that that is a thoroughly unsound interpretation of the aid component.", "start": 1415.792, "stop": 1422.39, "duration": 6.6, "cleanText": [["now", "first", "i", "want", "to", "say", "that", "we", "think", "that", "that", "be", "a", "thoroughly", "unsound", "interpretation", "of", "the", "aid", "component"]]}, {"text": "And a correct interpretation of the aid component, in the first place, it wouldn't depend on motivation, it would depend on what the organization did and it means that the organization has to be engaged in activities or primarily engaged in activities, which aid in some reasonably direct manner.", "start": 1422.39, "stop": 1440.89, "duration": 18.5, "cleanText": [["and", "a", "correct", "interpretation", "of", "the", "aid", "component", "in", "the", "first", "place", "it", "would", "not", "depend", "on", "motivation", "it", "would", "depend", "on", "what", "the", "organization", "do", "and", "it", "mean", "that", "the", "organization", "have", "to", "be", "engage", "in", "activity", "or", "primarily", "engage", "in", "activity", "which", "aid", "in", "some", "reasonably", "direct", "manner"]]}, {"text": "The supposed illicit objectives, which by definition characterized a Communist-action organization which it supposedly aiding, for example, that it advocates violence or Marx's ideology or it aids the organization -- organizationally by recruiting for it, raising money or something of that sort.", "start": 1440.89, "stop": 1462.122, "duration": 21.23, "cleanText": [["the", "suppose", "illicit", "objective", "which", "by", "definition", "characterize", "a", "communist", "action", "organization", "which", "it", "supposedly", "aid", "for", "example", "that", "it", "advocate", "violence", "or", "marx", "s", "ideology", "or", "it", "aid", "the", "organization", "organizationally", "by", "recruit", "for", "it", "raise", "money", "or", "something", "of", "that", "sort"]]}, {"text": "But it does not in our opinion and cannot constitutionally hold activities which are considered laudable and benign if they are done by anybody else on the grounds that somehow these activities might conceivably in some possible indirect way or might be motivated to benefit the Communist Party or to coincide with some clauses that Communist support along with non-Communist.", "start": 1462.122, "stop": 1492.596, "duration": 30.47, "cleanText": [["but", "it", "do", "not", "in", "our", "opinion", "and", "can", "not", "constitutionally", "hold", "activity", "which", "be", "consider", "laudable", "and", "benign", "if", "they", "be", "do", "by", "anybody", "else", "on", "the", "ground", "that", "somehow", "these", "activity", "might", "conceivably", "in", "some", "possible", "indirect", "way", "or", "might", "be", "motivate", "to", "benefit", "the", "communist", "party", "or", "to", "coincide", "with", "some", "clause", "that", "communist", "support", "along", "with", "non", "communist"]]}, {"text": "Under the construction of the Board and the Court, if you had a hospital which was run by a member of the Communist Party and that hospital took in as part of its services, persons who are members of the Communist Party as well as persons who were not members of the Communist Party that would be aid and support for the Communist Party and it would satisfy the means component.", "start": 1492.596, "stop": 1515.32, "duration": 22.72, "cleanText": [["under", "the", "construction", "of", "the", "board", "and", "the", "court", "if", "you", "have", "a", "hospital", "which", "be", "run", "by", "a", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "that", "hospital", "take", "in", "as", "part", "of", "its", "service", "person", "who", "be", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "as", "well", "as", "person", "who", "we", "be", "not", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "that", "would", "be", "aid", "and", "support", "for", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "it", "would", "satisfy", "the", "mean", "component"]]}, {"text": "And since you had a member of the Communist Party running it, it would -- it would satisfy the control component and the hospital would have to register.", "start": 1515.32, "stop": 1521.9, "duration": 6.58, "cleanText": [["and", "since", "you", "have", "a", "member", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "run", "it", "it", "would", "it", "would", "satisfy", "the", "control", "component", "and", "the", "hospital", "would", "have", "to", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Let me have a very good example.", "start": 1521.9, "stop": 1523.612, "duration": 1.71, "cleanText": [["let", "me", "have", "a", "very", "good", "example"]]}, {"text": "Suppose the Communist Party who engaged and wanted insurrection against the government, to be in the hospital and take anybody in.", "start": 1523.612, "stop": 1531.431, "duration": 7.82, "cleanText": [["suppose", "the", "communist", "party", "who", "engage", "and", "want", "insurrection", "against", "the", "government", "to", "be", "in", "the", "hospital", "and", "take", "anybody", "in"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "I think it --", "start": 1531.431, "stop": 1531.966, "duration": 0.53, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Does that exempt the hospital?", "start": 1531.966, "stop": 1533.095, "duration": 1.13, "cleanText": [["do", "that", "exempt", "the", "hospital"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "I think if these were a field hospital on the battlefield, that would be different.", "start": 1533.095, "stop": 1537.984, "duration": 4.89, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "if", "these", "we", "be", "a", "field", "hospital", "on", "the", "battlefield", "that", "would", "be", "different"]]}, {"text": "But we don't have a battlefield here.", "start": 1537.984, "stop": 1540.484, "duration": 2.5, "cleanText": [["but", "we", "do", "not", "have", "a", "battlefield", "here"]]}, {"text": "And anyway, this is not a hospital in a battlefield in this case that had been in this Court.", "start": 1540.484, "stop": 1543.2, "duration": 2.72, "cleanText": [["and", "anyway", "this", "be", "not", "a", "hospital", "in", "a", "battlefield", "in", "this", "case", "that", "have", "be", "in", "this", "court"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "I'm using an example here.", "start": 1543.2, "stop": 1544.715, "duration": 1.51, "cleanText": [["I", "be", "use", "an", "example", "here"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Joseph Forer", "textObjs": [{"text": "I was using an example, I'm glad you pointed out it's not a very good one.", "start": 1544.715, "stop": 1549.164, "duration": 4.45, "cleanText": [["i", "be", "use", "an", "example", "I", "be", "glad", "you", "point", "out", "it", "be", "not", "a", "very", "good", "one"]]}, {"text": "I'll withdraw it.", "start": 1549.164, "stop": 1551.533, "duration": 2.37, "cleanText": [["I", "will", "withdraw", "it"]]}, {"text": "This interpretation in which organizations are condemned by this registration centers because of activities, which are conceededly laudable, is simply in confict with the Act's purpose, in the Act's term.", "start": 1551.533, "stop": 1567.762, "duration": 16.23, "cleanText": [["this", "interpretation", "in", "which", "organization", "be", "condemn", "by", "this", "registration", "center", "because", "of", "activity", "which", "be", "conceededly", "laudable", "be", "simply", "in", "confict", "with", "the", "act", "s", "purpose", "in", "the", "act", "s", "term"]]}, {"text": "The justification of the Act is set forth in Section 2 of the Act, is that the Act is necessary to avert a clear and present danger to American institution.", "start": 1567.762, "stop": 1577.459, "duration": 9.7, "cleanText": [["the", "justification", "of", "the", "act", "be", "set", "forth", "in", "section", "of", "the", "act", "be", "that", "the", "act", "be", "necessary", "to", "avert", "a", "clear", "and", "present", "danger", "to", "american", "institution"]]}, {"text": "The title of the Act is that it's -- to control subversive activities.", "start": 1577.459, "stop": 1582.341, "duration": 4.88, "cleanText": [["the", "title", "of", "the", "act", "be", "that", "it", "be", "to", "control", "subversive", "activity"]]}, {"text": "And the Board is a Subversive Activities Control Board.", "start": 1582.341, "stop": 1586.569, "duration": 4.23, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "board", "be", "a", "subversive", "activity", "control", "board"]]}, {"text": "In the Communist Party case, the majority opinion, the Court recognize that there was a restraint on the First Amendment interest of Communist by the registration order involved there but it held that these interests were outbalanced by the fact that the Communist Party supposedly engaged in actually dangerous activities.", "start": 1586.569, "stop": 1611.462, "duration": 24.89, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "the", "majority", "opinion", "the", "court", "recognize", "that", "there", "be", "a", "restraint", "on", "the", "first", "amendment", "interest", "of", "communist", "by", "the", "registration", "order", "involve", "there", "but", "it", "hold", "that", "these", "interest", "we", "be", "outbalance", "by", "the", "fact", "that", "the", "communist", "party", "supposedly", "engage", "in", "actually", "dangerous", "activity"]]}, {"text": "And it said that the interest of the Communist Party and its members were outbalanced by The exigency -- the exigencies of sole preservation and the values of liberty which were menaced by the supposed foreign control criminal conspiracy.", "start": 1611.462, "stop": 1628.569, "duration": 17.11, "cleanText": [["and", "it", "say", "that", "the", "interest", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "its", "member", "we", "be", "outbalance", "by", "the", "exigency", "the", "exigency", "of", "sole", "preservation", "and", "the", "value", "of", "liberty", "which", "we", "be", "menace", "by", "the", "suppose", "foreign", "control", "criminal", "conspiracy"]]}, {"text": "Now, we don't have any -- anything like that here or claim here.", "start": 1628.569, "stop": 1632.954, "duration": 4.38, "cleanText": [["now", "we", "do", "not", "have", "any", "anything", "like", "that", "here", "or", "claim", "here"]]}, {"text": "It is impossible to see how the exigencies of self-preservation and the values of liberty would be served by depriving aliens of counsel and upheld in cases in which they are proceeded against by the Department of Justice.", "start": 1632.954, "stop": 1651.391, "duration": 18.44, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "impossible", "to", "see", "how", "the", "exigency", "of", "self", "preservation", "and", "the", "value", "of", "liberty", "would", "be", "serve", "by", "deprive", "alien", "of", "counsel", "and", "upheld", "in", "case", "in", "which", "they", "be", "proceed", "against", "by", "the", "department", "of", "justice"]]}, {"text": "Under the holding of the Communist Party case, the Communist Party itself would be required to register even if it was held to satisfy the controlled component, on the grounds that -- if the only activity it participated in was concededly non-dangerous and non-subversive.", "start": 1651.391, "stop": 1673.438, "duration": 22.05, "cleanText": [["under", "the", "holding", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "the", "communist", "party", "itself", "would", "be", "require", "to", "register", "even", "if", "it", "be", "hold", "to", "satisfy", "the", "controlled", "component", "on", "the", "ground", "that", "if", "the", "only", "activity", "it", "participate", "in", "be", "concededly", "non", "dangerous", "and", "non", "subversive"]]}, {"text": "For example, if the Communist Party indirectly aided the Soviet Union by furnishing legal aid, the Russian citizens are promoting the Russian ballet in this country, they could not satisfy the requirements that the -- this Court found necessary as applied to Communist-action organization.", "start": 1673.438, "stop": 1694.439, "duration": 21, "cleanText": [["for", "example", "if", "the", "communist", "party", "indirectly", "aid", "the", "soviet", "union", "by", "furnish", "legal", "aid", "the", "russian", "citizen", "be", "promote", "the", "russian", "ballet", "in", "this", "country", "they", "could", "not", "satisfy", "the", "requirement", "that", "the", "this", "court", "find", "necessary", "as", "apply", "to", "communist", "action", "organization"]]}, {"text": "And yet here, an organization is required to regisrer without any showing of dangerous activity.", "start": 1694.439, "stop": 1702.562, "duration": 8.12, "cleanText": [["and", "yet", "here", "an", "organization", "be", "require", "to", "regisrer", "without", "any", "showing", "of", "dangerous", "activity"]]}, {"text": "In the Cramp case, this Court invalidated the Florida oath which made government employees disclaim aid and support to the Communist Party.", "start": 1702.562, "stop": 1715.554, "duration": 12.99, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "cramp", "case", "this", "court", "invalidate", "the", "florida", "oath", "which", "make", "government", "employee", "disclaim", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "And the Court said, Well, aid and support of the Communist Party has all kinds of possible absurd --  it has absurd possibility, that because of this absurd possibility, the oath is no good, well, it's too vague and well invalidated.", "start": 1715.554, "stop": 1730.654, "duration": 15.1, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "court", "say", "well", "aid", "and", "support", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "have", "all", "kind", "of", "possible", "absurd", "it", "have", "absurd", "possibility", "that", "because", "of", "this", "absurd", "possibility", "the", "oath", "be", "no", "good", "well", "it", "be", "too", "vague", "and", "well", "invalidate"]]}, {"text": "And among the absurd possibilities that the Court referred to in Cramp and which later on Mr. Justice White referred to in the Baggett case, a similar oath, was a lawyer who represented the Communist Party or its members or a journalist who defends the constitutional rights of the Communist Party or its members, or anybody who supports any clause which is likewise supported by Communist or the Communist Party.", "start": 1730.654, "stop": 1755.599, "duration": 24.94, "cleanText": [["and", "among", "the", "absurd", "possibility", "that", "the", "court", "refer", "to", "in", "cramp", "and", "which", "later", "on", "mr", "justice", "white", "refer", "to", "in", "the", "baggett", "case", "a", "similar", "oath", "be", "a", "lawyer", "who", "represent", "the", "communist", "party", "or", "its", "member", "or", "a", "journalist", "who", "defend", "the", "constitutional", "right", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "or", "its", "member", "or", "anybody", "who", "support", "any", "clause", "which", "be", "likewise", "support", "by", "communist", "or", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "And the Court just recoiled from the fact that this should be considered aid and support to the Communist Party but said that because such outrageous things could be considered aid and support to the Communist Party, they would invalidate the oath.", "start": 1755.599, "stop": 1770.813, "duration": 15.21, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "court", "just", "recoil", "from", "the", "fact", "that", "this", "should", "be", "consider", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "party", "but", "say", "that", "because", "such", "outrageous", "thing", "could", "be", "consider", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "party", "they", "would", "invalidate", "the", "oath"]]}, {"text": "Now, in Baggett against Bullitt, Mr. Justice Clark felt that the interpretation was so extravagant that nobody in their right mind could possibly so apply the oath.", "start": 1770.813, "stop": 1781.706, "duration": 10.89, "cleanText": [["now", "in", "baggett", "against", "bullitt", "mr", "justice", "clark", "felt", "that", "the", "interpretation", "be", "so", "extravagant", "that", "nobody", "in", "their", "right", "mind", "could", "possibly", "so", "apply", "the", "oath"]]}, {"text": "And he said to anybody who interpreted the oath that way would be like Gulliver's mad scientist.", "start": 1781.706, "stop": 1787.968, "duration": 6.26, "cleanText": [["and", "he", "say", "to", "anybody", "who", "interpret", "the", "oath", "that", "way", "would", "be", "like", "gulliver", "s", "mad", "scientist"]]}, {"text": "Now, in this case the -- we don't have a note but we have an Act which can be interpreted and administered by the Board and there's no reason for them to interpret the oath the way Gulliver's mad scientist might have interpreted and I think the legislative history supports the interpretation I proposed.", "start": 1787.968, "stop": 1808.079, "duration": 20.11, "cleanText": [["now", "in", "this", "case", "the", "we", "do", "not", "have", "a", "note", "but", "we", "have", "an", "act", "which", "can", "be", "interpret", "and", "administer", "by", "the", "board", "and", "there", "be", "no", "reason", "for", "them", "to", "interpret", "the", "oath", "the", "way", "gulliver", "s", "mad", "scientist", "might", "have", "interpret", "and", "i", "think", "the", "legislative", "history", "support", "the", "interpretation", "i", "propose"]]}, {"text": "At page 45 of my brief, I quote from the house report on the bill and the Committee there said that it found it necessary at the outset to distinguish those features the Communist activity against which legislation cannot and should not be directed from those in the case of which legislative restraints are clearly practicable and necessary.", "start": 1808.079, "stop": 1832.669, "duration": 24.59, "cleanText": [["at", "page", "of", "my", "brief", "i", "quote", "from", "the", "house", "report", "on", "the", "bill", "and", "the", "committee", "there", "say", "that", "it", "find", "it", "necessary", "at", "the", "outset", "to", "distinguish", "those", "feature", "the", "communist", "activity", "against", "which", "legislation", "can", "not", "and", "should", "not", "be", "direct", "from", "those", "in", "the", "case", "of", "which", "legislative", "restraint", "be", "clearly", "practicable", "and", "necessary"]]}, {"text": "So the Committee forwarded, it should and that it had to distinguish between benign activities and subversive activities, Communist activities and this -- most such distinction is made by the construction of the government.", "start": 1832.669, "stop": 1851.823, "duration": 19.15, "cleanText": [["so", "the", "committee", "forward", "it", "should", "and", "that", "it", "have", "to", "distinguish", "between", "benign", "activity", "and", "subversive", "activity", "communist", "activity", "and", "this", "most", "such", "distinction", "be", "make", "by", "the", "construction", "of", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "Section 2 (7) of the Act refers to Communist-front organizations as being organizations which are operated -- which Communist-action organization is operated in carrying on the activities refered to in paragraph 2 (6) of the Act.", "start": 1851.823, "stop": 1869.281, "duration": 17.46, "cleanText": [["section", "of", "the", "act", "refers", "to", "communist", "front", "organization", "as", "be", "organization", "which", "be", "operate", "which", "communist", "action", "organization", "be", "operate", "in", "carry", "on", "the", "activity", "refer", "to", "in", "paragraph", "of", "the", "act"]]}, {"text": "That is Communist-front organizations are used by action organizations to carry on the activities in 2 (6).", "start": 1869.281, "stop": 1876.297, "duration": 7.02, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "communist", "front", "organization", "be", "use", "by", "action", "organization", "to", "carry", "on", "the", "activity", "in"]]}, {"text": "If you look at 2 (6) these are all conspiratorial, wicked, danger-causing activities.", "start": 1876.297, "stop": 1883.165, "duration": 6.87, "cleanText": [["if", "you", "look", "at", "these", "be", "all", "conspiratorial", "wicked", "danger", "causing", "activity"]]}, {"text": "They have nothing to do with representing aliens in deportation cases.", "start": 1883.165, "stop": 1888.005, "duration": 4.84, "cleanText": [["they", "have", "nothing", "to", "do", "with", "represent", "alien", "in", "deportation", "case"]]}, {"text": "Now, the Government's theory as far as I can make it out is that you can stop Communists from engaging in protected activities which everybody else could engage in if it would in anyway benefit the Communist Party and since you can't stop the Communist from doing it, therefore you can stop an organization which is controlled by Communist, but it's the same thing.", "start": 1888.005, "stop": 1909.587, "duration": 21.58, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "government", "s", "theory", "as", "far", "as", "i", "can", "make", "it", "out", "be", "that", "you", "can", "stop", "communist", "from", "engage", "in", "protected", "activity", "which", "everybody", "else", "could", "engage", "in", "if", "it", "would", "in", "anyway", "benefit", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "since", "you", "can", "not", "stop", "the", "communist", "from", "do", "it", "therefore", "you", "can", "stop", "an", "organization", "which", "be", "control", "by", "communist", "but", "it", "be", "the", "same", "thing"]]}, {"text": "It seems to me that both parts of it syllogism are wrong.", "start": 1909.587, "stop": 1913.07, "duration": 3.48, "cleanText": [["it", "seem", "to", "me", "that", "both", "part", "of", "it", "syllogism", "be", "wrong"]]}, {"text": "According to them, it's alright for Wendell Willkie to represent Mr. Schneiderman in a denaturalization case in this Court because he's not controlled by Communists but it would be improper for Mr. Schneiderman to defend themselves because he himself was a Communist.", "start": 1913.07, "stop": 1928.732, "duration": 15.66, "cleanText": [["accord", "to", "them", "it", "be", "alright", "for", "wendell", "willkie", "to", "represent", "mr", "schneiderman", "in", "a", "denaturalization", "case", "in", "this", "court", "because", "he", "be", "not", "control", "by", "communist", "but", "it", "would", "be", "improper", "for", "mr", "schneiderman", "to", "defend", "themselves", "because", "he", "himself", "be", "a", "communist"]]}, {"text": "Now, since the Dijon case has been established that -- that Communists cannot be restrained from engaging in the First Ammendment activities, peaceful First Amendment activities, just because they are Communists, the point was again made in the Scales case which Mr. Justice Harlan wrote the majority opinion.", "start": 1928.732, "stop": 1948.576, "duration": 19.84, "cleanText": [["now", "since", "the", "dijon", "case", "have", "be", "establish", "that", "that", "communists", "can", "not", "be", "restrain", "from", "engage", "in", "the", "first", "ammendment", "activity", "peaceful", "first", "amendment", "activity", "just", "because", "they", "be", "communist", "the", "point", "be", "again", "make", "in", "the", "scale", "case", "which", "mr", "justice", "harlan", "write", "the", "majority", "opinion"]]}, {"text": "And in the Aptheker case, the past -- recent passport case, this Court again held that Communists can't be restrained from engaging in peaceful activities open everybody else just because they are Communists.", "start": 1948.576, "stop": 1961.359, "duration": 12.78, "cleanText": [["and", "in", "the", "aptheker", "case", "the", "past", "recent", "passport", "case", "this", "court", "again", "hold", "that", "communist", "can", "not", "be", "restrain", "from", "engage", "in", "peaceful", "activity", "open", "everybody", "else", "just", "because", "they", "be", "communist"]]}, {"text": "Insofar as this Court has upheld legislation address against Communists, like the Section 9 (h) Taft-Hartley anti-Communist affidavit, it is done so on the theory that the activity that was restrained had a direct connection with danger-causing activity.", "start": 1961.359, "stop": 1982.968, "duration": 21.61, "cleanText": [["insofar", "as", "this", "court", "have", "uphold", "legislation", "address", "against", "communist", "like", "the", "section", "h", "taft", "hartley", "anti", "communist", "affidavit", "it", "be", "do", "so", "on", "the", "theory", "that", "the", "activity", "that", "be", "restrain", "have", "a", "direct", "connection", "with", "danger", "cause", "activity"]]}, {"text": "So even Communists can't be engaged from an -- can't be restrained from engaging in such protected activity.", "start": 1982.968, "stop": 1990.202, "duration": 7.23, "cleanText": [["so", "even", "communist", "can", "not", "be", "engage", "from", "an", "can", "not", "be", "restrain", "from", "engage", "in", "such", "protected", "activity"]]}, {"text": "And the situation becomes worst when you extend this doctrine that Communists have no constitutional rights the Government is obliged to respect for organizations which are supposed to be controlled by the Communist Party.", "start": 1990.202, "stop": 2003.616, "duration": 13.41, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "situation", "become", "worst", "when", "you", "extend", "this", "doctrine", "that", "communist", "have", "no", "constitutional", "right", "the", "government", "be", "oblige", "to", "respect", "for", "organization", "which", "be", "suppose", "to", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "In the first place, this control is a metaphysical concept under the Act.", "start": 2003.616, "stop": 2007.844, "duration": 4.23, "cleanText": [["in", "the", "first", "place", "this", "control", "be", "a", "metaphysical", "concept", "under", "the", "act"]]}, {"text": "It's an opinion.", "start": 2007.844, "stop": 2008.592, "duration": 0.75, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "an", "opinion"]]}, {"text": "It's not a fact.", "start": 2008.592, "stop": 2010.346, "duration": 1.75, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "a", "fact"]]}, {"text": "The second place has been cited by adminstrative board not by a judicial body, not by a jury which relies and the Government says it is entitled to rely on hearsay, opinion evidence, remote evidence, speculative inferences and then after all that it's decision is entitled a great weight.", "start": 2010.346, "stop": 2029.014, "duration": 18.67, "cleanText": [["the", "second", "place", "have", "be", "cite", "by", "adminstrative", "board", "not", "by", "a", "judicial", "body", "not", "by", "a", "jury", "which", "relies", "and", "the", "government", "say", "it", "be", "entitle", "to", "rely", "on", "hearsay", "opinion", "evidence", "remote", "evidence", "speculative", "inference", "and", "then", "after", "all", "that", "it", "be", "decision", "be", "entitle", "a", "great", "weight"]]}, {"text": "The upshot of it is that under the Board's theory, the Act imposes, gives the federal government an unprecedented and virial in power to supervise close organizations.", "start": 2029.014, "stop": 2041.456, "duration": 12.44, "cleanText": [["the", "upshot", "of", "it", "be", "that", "under", "the", "board", "s", "theory", "the", "act", "impose", "give", "the", "federal", "government", "an", "unprecedented", "and", "virial", "in", "power", "to", "supervise", "close", "organization"]]}, {"text": "No matter how laudable and benign their activities, the Government is now supposed to spy on the organization to determine if they have hidden motivations.", "start": 2041.456, "stop": 2050.956, "duration": 9.5, "cleanText": [["no", "matter", "how", "laudable", "and", "benign", "their", "activity", "the", "government", "be", "now", "suppose", "to", "spy", "on", "the", "organization", "to", "determine", "if", "they", "have", "hide", "motivation"]]}, {"text": "Or if some of their officers are, or once were, or is said to be affiliated with the Communist Party, and then if it concludes that they are aware to hold them to account before the Subversive Activities Control Board.", "start": 2050.956, "stop": 2062.831, "duration": 11.88, "cleanText": [["or", "if", "some", "of", "their", "officer", "be", "or", "once", "we", "be", "or", "be", "say", "to", "be", "affiliate", "with", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "then", "if", "it", "conclude", "that", "they", "be", "aware", "to", "hold", "them", "to", "account", "before", "the", "subversive", "activity", "control", "board"]]}, {"text": "I would like to reserve the rest of my time for rebuttal.", "start": 2062.831, "stop": 2065.791, "duration": 2.96, "cleanText": [["i", "would", "like", "to", "reserve", "the", "rest", "of", "my", "time", "for", "rebuttal"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Earl Warren", "textObjs": [{"text": "You may.", "start": 2065.791, "stop": 2068.44, "duration": 2.65, "cleanText": [["you", "may"]]}, {"text": "Mr. Terris.", "start": 2068.44, "stop": 2069.369, "duration": 0.93, "cleanText": [["mr", "terris"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Chief Justice, may it please the Court.", "start": 2069.369, "stop": 2072.243, "duration": 2.87, "cleanText": [["mr", "chief", "justice", "may", "it", "please", "the", "court"]]}, {"text": "This case involves the constitutionality of a federal statute.", "start": 2072.243, "stop": 2076.574, "duration": 4.33, "cleanText": [["this", "case", "involve", "the", "constitutionality", "of", "a", "federal", "statute"]]}, {"text": "I want to emphasize that it is limited to the registration provisions with -- it is only the registration provisions which are before the Court and not any of the disabilities either as they apply to the organization or to the members.", "start": 2076.574, "stop": 2092.157, "duration": 15.58, "cleanText": [["i", "want", "to", "emphasize", "that", "it", "be", "limit", "to", "the", "registration", "provision", "with", "it", "be", "only", "the", "registration", "provision", "which", "be", "before", "the", "court", "and", "not", "any", "of", "the", "disability", "either", "as", "they", "apply", "to", "the", "organization", "or", "to", "the", "member"]]}, {"text": "These provisions do not prohibit petitioner from doing anything, they do require the Board to make a finding as to the character of the organization and if it finds the organization to be a Communist-front as defined in the Act to require it to disclose its officers and to make a financial accounting.", "start": 2092.157, "stop": 2115.129, "duration": 22.97, "cleanText": [["these", "provision", "do", "not", "prohibit", "petitioner", "from", "do", "anything", "they", "do", "require", "the", "board", "to", "make", "a", "finding", "as", "to", "the", "character", "of", "the", "organization", "and", "if", "it", "find", "the", "organization", "to", "be", "a", "communist", "front", "as", "define", "in", "the", "act", "to", "require", "it", "to", "disclose", "its", "officer", "and", "to", "make", "a", "financial", "accounting"]]}, {"text": "In considering the issues in this case, the Government believes that it is crucial to understand the nature of Communist-fronts and their relationship to the World Communist Movement.", "start": 2115.129, "stop": 2126.523, "duration": 11.39, "cleanText": [["in", "consider", "the", "issue", "in", "this", "case", "the", "government", "believe", "that", "it", "be", "crucial", "to", "understand", "the", "nature", "of", "communist", "front", "and", "their", "relationship", "to", "the", "world", "communist", "movement"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William O. Douglas", "textObjs": [{"text": "You're not suggesting that they -- they have to wait until one of the statutes were defined, to bring the case here, are you?", "start": 2126.523, "stop": 2132.49, "duration": 5.97, "cleanText": [["you", "be", "not", "suggest", "that", "they", "they", "have", "to", "wait", "until", "one", "of", "the", "statute", "we", "be", "define", "to", "bring", "the", "case", "here", "be", "you"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I am Your Honor.", "start": 2132.49, "stop": 2133.355, "duration": 0.87, "cleanText": [["i", "be", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William O. Douglas", "textObjs": [{"text": "Oh, you --", "start": 2133.355, "stop": 2133.514, "duration": 0.16, "cleanText": [["oh", "you"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That was the hold -- that was the holding of this Court in the Communist Party case, that provisions here are almost identical.", "start": 2133.514, "stop": 2139.8, "duration": 6.29, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "the", "hold", "that", "be", "the", "holding", "of", "this", "court", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "that", "provision", "here", "be", "almost", "identical"]]}, {"text": "They certainly are analogous and the relationship between the disabilities or sanctions and the registration provisions is identical.", "start": 2139.8, "stop": 2152.384, "duration": 12.58, "cleanText": [["they", "certainly", "be", "analogous", "and", "the", "relationship", "between", "the", "disability", "or", "sanction", "and", "the", "registration", "provision", "be", "identical"]]}, {"text": "In our brief, in the appendices, we described in considerable length, the nature of Communist-fronts.", "start": 2152.384, "stop": 2160.436, "duration": 8.05, "cleanText": [["in", "our", "brief", "in", "the", "appendix", "we", "describe", "in", "considerable", "length", "the", "nature", "of", "communist", "front"]]}, {"text": "I will not go into it in great detail but I think it is important to summarize the nature of these fronts here.", "start": 2160.436, "stop": 2168.83, "duration": 8.39, "cleanText": [["i", "will", "not", "go", "into", "it", "in", "great", "detail", "but", "i", "think", "it", "be", "important", "to", "summarize", "the", "nature", "of", "these", "front", "here"]]}, {"text": "After the Soviet Revolution according to Communist theory, it was expected that there would be armed revolutions in all capitalist countries.", "start": 2168.83, "stop": 2179.204, "duration": 10.37, "cleanText": [["after", "the", "soviet", "revolution", "accord", "to", "communist", "theory", "it", "be", "expect", "that", "there", "would", "be", "arm", "revolution", "in", "all", "capitalist", "country"]]}, {"text": "But this expectation turned out to be incorrect because the workers turned out not to be so eager to overthrow their governments.", "start": 2179.204, "stop": 2188.578, "duration": 9.37, "cleanText": [["but", "this", "expectation", "turn", "out", "to", "be", "incorrect", "because", "the", "worker", "turn", "out", "not", "to", "be", "so", "eager", "to", "overthrow", "their", "government"]]}, {"text": "Therefore, the Communist leaders in the Soviet Union and their theoreticians decided to attempt to win the allegiances to the workers, as well as of other groups more gradually than advocating and solely advocating armed revolution.", "start": 2188.578, "stop": 2204.405, "duration": 15.83, "cleanText": [["therefore", "the", "communist", "leader", "in", "the", "soviet", "union", "and", "their", "theoretician", "decide", "to", "attempt", "to", "win", "the", "allegiance", "to", "the", "worker", "as", "well", "as", "of", "other", "group", "more", "gradually", "than", "advocate", "and", "solely", "advocate", "arm", "revolution"]]}, {"text": "They did this not so much by changing the views of the Communist Parties which continued to support armed revolution.", "start": 2204.405, "stop": 2212.135, "duration": 7.73, "cleanText": [["they", "do", "this", "not", "so", "much", "by", "change", "the", "view", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "which", "continue", "to", "support", "armed", "revolution"]]}, {"text": "But rather by infiltrating, and if possible, controlling formally non-Communist organizations in all kinds of different fields, workers, farmers, veterans, ethnic groups, and the like, and if they were unsuccessful in doing this to set up new organizations to perform these tasks.", "start": 2212.135, "stop": 2230.594, "duration": 18.46, "cleanText": [["but", "rather", "by", "infiltrate", "and", "if", "possible", "control", "formally", "non", "communist", "organization", "in", "all", "kind", "of", "different", "field", "worker", "farmer", "veteran", "ethnic", "group", "and", "the", "like", "and", "if", "they", "we", "be", "unsuccessful", "in", "do", "this", "to", "set", "up", "new", "organization", "to", "perform", "these", "task"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Were the Communists before the Court?", "start": 2230.594, "stop": 2234.314, "duration": 3.72, "cleanText": [["we", "be", "the", "communist", "before", "the", "court"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, Your Honor, its not.", "start": 2234.314, "stop": 2236.231, "duration": 1.92, "cleanText": [["no", "your", "honor", "its", "not"]]}, {"text": "This is the kind of evidence that was before the Congress in enacting the statute.", "start": 2236.231, "stop": 2242.76, "duration": 6.53, "cleanText": [["this", "be", "the", "kind", "of", "evidence", "that", "be", "before", "the", "congress", "in", "enact", "the", "statute"]]}, {"text": "Now, the Congress found what a Communist-front was and therefore the evidence that was before the Board was just evidence which went to the character of the American Committee itself.", "start": 2242.76, "stop": 2256.347, "duration": 13.59, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "congress", "find", "what", "a", "communist", "front", "be", "and", "therefore", "the", "evidence", "that", "be", "before", "the", "board", "be", "just", "evidence", "which", "go", "to", "the", "character", "of", "the", "american", "committee", "itself"]]}, {"text": "In other words, the Board of course has no power to go beneath it and determine anew whether the Communist-fronts are in fact dangerous.", "start": 2256.347, "stop": 2265.181, "duration": 8.83, "cleanText": [["in", "other", "word", "the", "board", "of", "course", "have", "no", "power", "to", "go", "beneath", "it", "and", "determine", "anew", "whether", "the", "communist", "front", "be", "in", "fact", "dangerous"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "Summarizing the general characters and legislative history --", "start": 2265.181, "stop": 2267.973, "duration": 2.79, "cleanText": [["summarize", "the", "general", "character", "and", "legislative", "history"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 2267.973, "stop": 2268.537, "duration": 0.56, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- in this area.", "start": 2268.537, "stop": 2269.655, "duration": 1.12, "cleanText": [["in", "this", "area"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "There was a tendency, it seems to me in listening to petitioner's counsel here and in its brief to consider Communist-fronts as a completely benign organizations he repeatedly said.", "start": 2269.655, "stop": 2282.59, "duration": 12.93, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "a", "tendency", "it", "seem", "to", "me", "in", "listen", "to", "petitioner", "s", "counsel", "here", "and", "in", "its", "brief", "to", "consider", "communist", "front", "as", "a", "completely", "benign", "organization", "he", "repeatedly", "say"]]}, {"text": "It is an organization that does no more than defend people, which of course is perfectly, as he insists, a laudable objective.", "start": 2282.59, "stop": 2292.509, "duration": 9.92, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "an", "organization", "that", "do", "no", "more", "than", "defend", "people", "which", "of", "course", "be", "perfectly", "as", "he", "insist", "a", "laudable", "objective"]]}, {"text": "What we are trying to do, what I', trying to do now is to put these provisions in the context of the Communist Movement, which is what Congress was dealing with in the Internal Security Act.", "start": 2292.509, "stop": 2305.149, "duration": 12.64, "cleanText": [["what", "we", "be", "try", "to", "do", "what", "i", "try", "to", "do", "now", "be", "to", "put", "these", "provision", "in", "the", "context", "of", "the", "communist", "movement", "which", "be", "what", "congress", "be", "deal", "with", "in", "the", "internal", "security", "act"]]}, {"text": "One scholar has pointed out that with the aid of -- with 100 Communist members, it is possible to control an organization of a 150,000 people.", "start": 2305.149, "stop": 2317.564, "duration": 12.41, "cleanText": [["one", "scholar", "have", "point", "out", "that", "with", "the", "aid", "of", "with", "communist", "member", "it", "be", "possible", "to", "control", "an", "organization", "of", "a", "people"]]}, {"text": "That Communist control of these organizations was not revealed because if the Communist control was revealed non-Communist would be scared away.", "start": 2317.564, "stop": 2327.562, "duration": 10, "cleanText": [["that", "communist", "control", "of", "these", "organization", "be", "not", "reveal", "because", "if", "the", "communist", "control", "be", "reveal", "non", "communist", "would", "be", "scar", "away"]]}, {"text": "And these organizations utilized popular causes, good causes, higher wages, better working conditions are positioned to fascism and the like.", "start": 2327.562, "stop": 2337.513, "duration": 9.95, "cleanText": [["and", "these", "organization", "utilize", "popular", "cause", "good", "cause", "high", "wage", "good", "work", "condition", "be", "position", "to", "fascism", "and", "the", "like"]]}, {"text": "But these causes were not the ultimate objective of the Communist Party members who control the organizations.", "start": 2337.513, "stop": 2344.105, "duration": 6.59, "cleanText": [["but", "these", "cause", "we", "be", "not", "the", "ultimate", "objective", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "member", "who", "control", "the", "organization"]]}, {"text": "Their ultimate objective, which they did not directly advocate within these organizations, was forcible overthrow of the government of a particular country in which they were operating.", "start": 2344.105, "stop": 2356.148, "duration": 12.04, "cleanText": [["their", "ultimate", "objective", "which", "they", "do", "not", "directly", "advocate", "within", "these", "organization", "be", "forcible", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government", "of", "a", "particular", "country", "in", "which", "they", "we", "be", "operate"]]}, {"text": "Now, I would like to turn --", "start": 2356.148, "stop": 2356.672, "duration": 0.52, "cleanText": [["now", "i", "would", "like", "to", "turn"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "I don't quite see if -- if they didn't advocate these things within these organizations.", "start": 2356.672, "stop": 2362.714, "duration": 6.04, "cleanText": [["i", "do", "not", "quite", "see", "if", "if", "they", "do", "not", "advocate", "these", "thing", "within", "these", "organization"]]}, {"text": "In other words, that they put different hats on and these --", "start": 2362.714, "stop": 2364.75, "duration": 2.04, "cleanText": [["in", "other", "word", "that", "they", "put", "different", "hat", "on", "and", "these"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 2364.75, "stop": 2364.89, "duration": 0.14, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- organizations were -- are there only for a lot of -- laudable purposes, why -- what (Voice Overlap) --", "start": 2364.89, "stop": 2369.027, "duration": 4.14, "cleanText": [["organization", "we", "be", "be", "there", "only", "for", "a", "lot", "of", "laudable", "purpose", "why", "what", "voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, that's exactly what I was going to point --", "start": 2369.027, "stop": 2370.564, "duration": 1.54, "cleanText": [["well", "that", "be", "exactly", "what", "i", "be", "go", "to", "point"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "Alright.", "start": 2370.564, "stop": 2370.814, "duration": 0.25, "cleanText": [["alright"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- to you, Your Honor, what Communist purpose was served by having these organizations at all.", "start": 2370.814, "stop": 2377.478, "duration": 6.66, "cleanText": [["to", "you", "your", "honor", "what", "communist", "purpose", "be", "serve", "by", "have", "these", "organization", "at", "all"]]}, {"text": "Why have separate organizations from the Communist Party.", "start": 2377.478, "stop": 2381.082, "duration": 3.6, "cleanText": [["why", "have", "separate", "organization", "from", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Well, there's several reasons.", "start": 2381.082, "stop": 2383.006, "duration": 1.92, "cleanText": [["well", "there", "be", "several", "reason"]]}, {"text": "First of all, they want to propagandize far marginal numbers of people than they could through the Communist Party.", "start": 2383.006, "stop": 2390.741, "duration": 7.74, "cleanText": [["first", "of", "all", "they", "want", "to", "propagandize", "far", "marginal", "number", "of", "people", "than", "they", "could", "through", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "Propaganda is enticing people for better health and higher wages and so on, why is it --", "start": 2390.741, "stop": 2394.364, "duration": 3.62, "cleanText": [["propaganda", "be", "entice", "people", "for", "good", "health", "and", "high", "wage", "and", "so", "on", "why", "be", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor there are great many issues that aren't quite so --", "start": 2394.364, "stop": 2397.562, "duration": 3.2, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "there", "be", "great", "many", "issue", "that", "be", "not", "quite", "so"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "Alright --", "start": 2397.562, "stop": 2397.983, "duration": 0.42, "cleanText": [["alright"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- in two different pockets there.", "start": 2397.983, "stop": 2400.698, "duration": 2.71, "cleanText": [["in", "two", "different", "pocket", "there"]]}, {"text": "You can propagandize people towards economic measures, to move closer and closer to Communist dogma.", "start": 2400.698, "stop": 2410.387, "duration": 9.69, "cleanText": [["you", "can", "propagandize", "people", "towards", "economic", "measure", "to", "move", "closer", "and", "closer", "to", "communist", "dogma"]]}, {"text": "When they get close enough then the person they hope will say, well, really this -- I've been in favor of Communist dogma all along.", "start": 2410.387, "stop": 2419.174, "duration": 8.79, "cleanText": [["when", "they", "get", "close", "enough", "then", "the", "person", "they", "hope", "will", "say", "well", "really", "this", "I", "have", "be", "in", "favor", "of", "communist", "dogma", "all", "along"]]}, {"text": "The whole piece in the long run, the people will either become Communist Party members in this method and this of course does happen or at least that they will consider Communism not a serious menace.", "start": 2419.174, "stop": 2431.139, "duration": 11.97, "cleanText": [["the", "whole", "piece", "in", "the", "long", "run", "the", "people", "will", "either", "become", "communist", "party", "member", "in", "this", "method", "and", "this", "of", "course", "do", "happen", "or", "at", "least", "that", "they", "will", "consider", "communism", "not", "a", "serious", "menace"]]}, {"text": "Now, the second reason is that they hoped to get people non-Communists to support positions even though they are not Communist Party members that are taken by the Soviet Union or by the Communist Parties.", "start": 2431.139, "stop": 2443.569, "duration": 12.43, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "second", "reason", "be", "that", "they", "hop", "to", "get", "people", "non", "communist", "to", "support", "position", "even", "though", "they", "be", "not", "communist", "party", "member", "that", "be", "take", "by", "the", "soviet", "union", "or", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Now, they did this in their -- in the Soviet Peace Crusade after World War II, they set up various peace organizations throughout the world in order to get as many people to support Soviet views then hopefully the democratic governments would reflect the positions of these people.", "start": 2443.569, "stop": 2462.285, "duration": 18.72, "cleanText": [["now", "they", "do", "this", "in", "their", "in", "the", "soviet", "peace", "crusade", "after", "world", "war", "ii", "they", "set", "up", "various", "peace", "organization", "throughout", "the", "world", "in", "order", "to", "get", "as", "many", "people", "to", "support", "soviet", "view", "then", "hopefully", "the", "democratic", "government", "would", "reflect", "the", "position", "of", "these", "people"]]}, {"text": "The number of people in the Communist Party might be very, very much less.", "start": 2462.285, "stop": 2467.006, "duration": 4.72, "cleanText": [["the", "number", "of", "people", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "might", "be", "very", "very", "much", "less"]]}, {"text": "The third reason is that these Communist-led organizations often provide support to the Communist Party.", "start": 2467.006, "stop": 2473.314, "duration": 6.31, "cleanText": [["the", "third", "reason", "be", "that", "these", "communist", "lead", "organization", "often", "provide", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Now, this may be financial, they may take you in a great deal of additional money more than they spent or they may provide services, that's exactly what we allege.", "start": 2473.314, "stop": 2482.012, "duration": 8.7, "cleanText": [["now", "this", "may", "be", "financial", "they", "may", "take", "you", "in", "a", "great", "deal", "of", "additional", "money", "more", "than", "they", "spend", "or", "they", "may", "provide", "service", "that", "be", "exactly", "what", "we", "allege"]]}, {"text": "But the Government alleges and what the Government believes that is proved, the American Committee did it.", "start": 2482.012, "stop": 2486.49, "duration": 4.48, "cleanText": [["but", "the", "government", "alleges", "and", "what", "the", "government", "believe", "that", "be", "prove", "the", "american", "committee", "do", "it"]]}, {"text": "It was the way of the Communist Party defending its members through funds contributed by non-Communist and the non-Communist did not know that the organization they were contributing to was in fact controlled by the Communist Party.", "start": 2486.49, "stop": 2502.967, "duration": 16.48, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "the", "way", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "defend", "its", "member", "through", "fund", "contribute", "by", "non", "communist", "and", "the", "non", "communist", "do", "not", "know", "that", "the", "organization", "they", "we", "be", "contribute", "to", "be", "in", "fact", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "And fourth, these Communist-led organizations play an important role when and if the time ever comes for armed revolution before -- immediately before revolution, they may join in United Fronts, this was done in the 30's throughout most of Europe and in those United Fronts they try to cause chaos and turmoil and both in the society and in the government.", "start": 2502.967, "stop": 2526.006, "duration": 23.04, "cleanText": [["and", "fourth", "these", "communist", "lead", "organization", "play", "an", "important", "role", "when", "and", "if", "the", "time", "ever", "come", "for", "armed", "revolution", "before", "immediately", "before", "revolution", "they", "may", "join", "in", "united", "front", "this", "be", "do", "in", "the", "s", "throughout", "most", "of", "europe", "and", "in", "those", "united", "front", "they", "try", "to", "because", "chaos", "and", "turmoil", "and", "both", "in", "the", "society", "and", "in", "the", "government"]]}, {"text": "When the revolution actually cursed, they may attempt to make the organization actually back the revolution or else be neutral to it.", "start": 2526.006, "stop": 2534.055, "duration": 8.05, "cleanText": [["when", "the", "revolution", "actually", "curse", "they", "may", "attempt", "to", "make", "the", "organization", "actually", "back", "the", "revolution", "or", "else", "be", "neutral", "to", "it"]]}, {"text": "Now, what I'd been talking about sounds extremely theoretical and unreal.", "start": 2534.055, "stop": 2541.498, "duration": 7.44, "cleanText": [["now", "what", "I", "have", "be", "talk", "about", "sound", "extremely", "theoretical", "and", "unreal"]]}, {"text": "The appendices to our brief indicate that for some 40 years this is exactly what the Communist Party has been doing this country -- in this country and throughout the world.", "start": 2541.498, "stop": 2551.584, "duration": 10.09, "cleanText": [["the", "appendix", "to", "our", "brief", "indicate", "that", "for", "some", "year", "this", "be", "exactly", "what", "the", "communist", "party", "have", "be", "do", "this", "country", "in", "this", "country", "and", "throughout", "the", "world"]]}, {"text": "I think it's fair to say at least they didn't think it was unreal but I think it's fair to say that they thought they were accomplishing something by it.", "start": 2551.584, "stop": 2559.402, "duration": 7.82, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "it", "be", "fair", "to", "say", "at", "least", "they", "do", "not", "think", "it", "be", "unreal", "but", "i", "think", "it", "be", "fair", "to", "say", "that", "they", "think", "they", "we", "be", "accomplish", "something", "by", "it"]]}, {"text": "And how much they've accomplished?", "start": 2559.402, "stop": 2562.368, "duration": 2.97, "cleanText": [["and", "how", "much", "they", "have", "accomplish"]]}, {"text": "I suppose they haven't accomplished enough in all the democratic governments that haven't been overthrown.", "start": 2562.368, "stop": 2567.37, "duration": 5, "cleanText": [["i", "suppose", "they", "have", "not", "accomplish", "enough", "in", "all", "the", "democratic", "government", "that", "have", "not", "be", "overthrow"]]}, {"text": "But the fact is that there are two examples of where this method was extremely important to Communist overthrow of the government and that were within the two coup d'etats in Czechoslovakia and in Hungary.", "start": 2567.37, "stop": 2580.67, "duration": 13.3, "cleanText": [["but", "the", "fact", "be", "that", "there", "be", "two", "example", "of", "where", "this", "method", "be", "extremely", "important", "to", "communist", "overthrow", "of", "the", "government", "and", "that", "we", "be", "within", "the", "two", "coup", "detats", "in", "czechoslovakia", "and", "in", "hungary"]]}, {"text": "Unfortunately the Government's brief does not describe the use of the fronts in these two very specific instances in detail.", "start": 2580.67, "stop": 2588.681, "duration": 8.01, "cleanText": [["unfortunately", "the", "government", "s", "brief", "do", "not", "describe", "the", "use", "of", "the", "front", "in", "these", "two", "very", "specific", "instance", "in", "detail"]]}, {"text": "But they are described in several books and articles which are cited by Mr. Justice Jackson in his concurring opinion in the Dennis case.", "start": 2588.681, "stop": 2597.143, "duration": 8.46, "cleanText": [["but", "they", "be", "describe", "in", "several", "book", "and", "article", "which", "be", "cite", "by", "mr", "justice", "jackson", "in", "his", "concur", "opinion", "in", "the", "dennis", "case"]]}, {"text": "And these books and articles by scholars indicate just how Communist-fronts form an extremely vital role in the actual revolution when and if that time ever comes.", "start": 2597.143, "stop": 2611.157, "duration": 14.01, "cleanText": [["and", "these", "book", "and", "article", "by", "scholar", "indicate", "just", "how", "communist", "front", "form", "an", "extremely", "vital", "role", "in", "the", "actual", "revolution", "when", "and", "if", "that", "time", "ever", "come"]]}, {"text": "Now I'd like to turn more specifically to this statute and how it fits into the pattern of the Communist theory and practice which I've just described.", "start": 2611.157, "stop": 2622.657, "duration": 11.5, "cleanText": [["now", "I", "have", "like", "to", "turn", "more", "specifically", "to", "this", "statute", "and", "how", "it", "fit", "into", "the", "pattern", "of", "the", "communist", "theory", "and", "practice", "which", "I", "have", "just", "describe"]]}, {"text": "Section 2 (7) -- Section 2 of that Act describes the World Communist Movement in considerable detail.", "start": 2622.657, "stop": 2628.733, "duration": 6.08, "cleanText": [["section", "section", "of", "that", "act", "describe", "the", "world", "communist", "movement", "in", "considerable", "detail"]]}, {"text": "Subsection 7 describes Communist-fronts as being created and maintained.", "start": 2628.733, "stop": 2637.46, "duration": 8.73, "cleanText": [["subsection", "describes", "communist", "front", "as", "be", "create", "and", "maintain"]]}, {"text": "In order to obtain financial and other support from people who would not normally give their support to the Communist activities, and Congress found that these fronts conceal their true character and their purposes.", "start": 2637.46, "stop": 2651.852, "duration": 14.39, "cleanText": [["in", "order", "to", "obtain", "financial", "and", "other", "support", "from", "people", "who", "would", "not", "normally", "give", "their", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "activity", "and", "congress", "find", "that", "these", "front", "conceal", "their", "true", "character", "and", "their", "purpose"]]}, {"text": "Now, the Act then defines in Section 3 (4) what a Communist-front is.", "start": 2651.852, "stop": 2657.131, "duration": 5.28, "cleanText": [["now", "the", "act", "then", "define", "in", "section", "what", "a", "communist", "front", "be"]]}, {"text": "And essentially, insofar as it's relevant here, it says that a Communist-front is first controlled by a Communist-action organization, here at the Communist Party and second that it has the purpose of carrying -- of giving aid and support, the primary purpose of giving aid and support to the Communist-action organization, here at the Communist Party.", "start": 2657.131, "stop": 2681.005, "duration": 23.87, "cleanText": [["and", "essentially", "insofar", "as", "it", "be", "relevant", "here", "it", "say", "that", "a", "communist", "front", "be", "first", "control", "by", "a", "communist", "action", "organization", "here", "at", "the", "communist", "party", "and", "second", "that", "it", "have", "the", "purpose", "of", "carry", "of", "give", "aid", "and", "support", "the", "primary", "purpose", "of", "give", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "action", "organization", "here", "at", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Now, Communist-action organizations in turn are the --", "start": 2681.005, "stop": 2684.417, "duration": 3.41, "cleanText": [["now", "communist", "action", "organization", "in", "turn", "be", "the"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "How do use the word aid?", "start": 2684.417, "stop": 2686.609, "duration": 2.19, "cleanText": [["how", "do", "use", "the", "word", "aid"]]}, {"text": "How do you use the word aid?", "start": 2686.609, "stop": 2688.979, "duration": 2.37, "cleanText": [["how", "do", "you", "use", "the", "word", "aid"]]}, {"text": "Supposed we had a organization like this that all that it did was to -- I think Mr. Fortas has brought over the Russian ballet or --", "start": 2688.979, "stop": 2698.847, "duration": 9.87, "cleanText": [["suppose", "we", "have", "a", "organization", "like", "this", "that", "all", "that", "it", "do", "be", "to", "i", "think", "mr", "fortas", "have", "bring", "over", "the", "russian", "ballet", "or"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That would not --", "start": 2698.847, "stop": 2699.012, "duration": 0.16, "cleanText": [["that", "would", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- in order to exchange its students, that would --", "start": 2699.012, "stop": 2700.847, "duration": 1.84, "cleanText": [["in", "order", "to", "exchange", "its", "student", "that", "would"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That wouldn't even come close to being under the actuary.", "start": 2700.847, "stop": 2703.195, "duration": 2.35, "cleanText": [["that", "would", "not", "even", "come", "close", "to", "be", "under", "the", "actuary"]]}, {"text": "There are two reasons why, its purpose has to be not ballet.", "start": 2703.195, "stop": 2707.548, "duration": 4.35, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "two", "reason", "why", "its", "purpose", "have", "to", "be", "not", "ballet"]]}, {"text": "Its purpose has to be that it is trying to further there is the Communist Party or the Soviet Union or the World Communist Movement.", "start": 2707.548, "stop": 2714.477, "duration": 6.93, "cleanText": [["its", "purpose", "have", "to", "be", "that", "it", "be", "try", "to", "further", "there", "be", "the", "communist", "party", "or", "the", "soviet", "union", "or", "the", "world", "communist", "movement"]]}, {"text": "That has to be its purpose, not ballet.", "start": 2714.477, "stop": 2716.769, "duration": 2.29, "cleanText": [["that", "have", "to", "be", "its", "purpose", "not", "ballet"]]}, {"text": "But even if passing that, it has to be an organization which is controlled by the Communist Party.", "start": 2716.769, "stop": 2722.818, "duration": 6.05, "cleanText": [["but", "even", "if", "passing", "that", "it", "have", "to", "be", "an", "organization", "which", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Supposed that they met -- there were Communist who are members of this.", "start": 2722.818, "stop": 2725.742, "duration": 2.92, "cleanText": [["suppose", "that", "they", "meet", "there", "we", "be", "communist", "who", "be", "member", "of", "this"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That wouldn't be (Voice Overlap) controlling Your Honor, that would not be controlled.", "start": 2725.742, "stop": 2729.472, "duration": 3.73, "cleanText": [["that", "would", "not", "be", "voice", "overlap", "control", "your", "honor", "that", "would", "not", "be", "control"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Even though it helped to increase the prestige or --", "start": 2729.472, "stop": 2732.471, "duration": 3, "cleanText": [["even", "though", "it", "help", "to", "increase", "the", "prestige", "or"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That would not be a Communist-front, that's right Your Honor.", "start": 2732.471, "stop": 2735.065, "duration": 2.59, "cleanText": [["that", "would", "not", "be", "a", "communist", "front", "that", "be", "right", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "Control has -- has to be and is shown by all the cases that have been decided and more specifically by this case.", "start": 2735.065, "stop": 2742.416, "duration": 7.35, "cleanText": [["control", "have", "have", "to", "be", "and", "be", "show", "by", "all", "the", "case", "that", "have", "be", "decide", "and", "more", "specifically", "by", "this", "case"]]}, {"text": "It has to be that the people that run the organization are active party members.", "start": 2742.416, "stop": 2748.986, "duration": 6.57, "cleanText": [["it", "have", "to", "be", "that", "the", "people", "that", "run", "the", "organization", "be", "active", "party", "member"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, suppose that would be true, they would be bringing over -- promoting international exchange of students and promoting ballet.", "start": 2748.986, "stop": 2755.964, "duration": 6.98, "cleanText": [["well", "suppose", "that", "would", "be", "true", "they", "would", "be", "bring", "over", "promote", "international", "exchange", "of", "student", "and", "promote", "ballet"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "They're acting under instructions of the Communist Party.", "start": 2755.964, "stop": 2759.258, "duration": 3.29, "cleanText": [["they", "be", "act", "under", "instruction", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well that's -- were they here, I'm not --", "start": 2759.258, "stop": 2762.697, "duration": 3.44, "cleanText": [["well", "that", "be", "we", "be", "they", "here", "I", "be", "not"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Here we have testimony that the petitioner's offices were killing out the policies of the Communist Party.", "start": 2762.697, "stop": 2768.048, "duration": 5.35, "cleanText": [["here", "we", "have", "testimony", "that", "the", "petitioner", "s", "office", "we", "be", "kill", "out", "the", "policy", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "I supposed one of those policies might be to think that these people think well in Russia.", "start": 2768.048, "stop": 2775.207, "duration": 7.16, "cleanText": [["i", "suppose", "one", "of", "those", "policy", "might", "be", "to", "think", "that", "these", "people", "think", "well", "in", "russia"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "And the purpose of this organization was to bolster the prestige of the Soviet Union.", "start": 2775.207, "stop": 2778.976, "duration": 3.77, "cleanText": [["and", "the", "purpose", "of", "this", "organization", "be", "to", "bolster", "the", "prestige", "of", "the", "soviet", "union"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 2778.976, "stop": 2779.198, "duration": 0.22, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "If I can --", "start": 2779.198, "stop": 2779.747, "duration": 0.55, "cleanText": [["if", "i", "can"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 2779.747, "stop": 2779.782, "duration": 0.04, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "If I can rephrase your --", "start": 2779.782, "stop": 2780.902, "duration": 1.12, "cleanText": [["if", "i", "can", "rephrase", "your"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes, yes.", "start": 2780.902, "stop": 2781.423, "duration": 0.52, "cleanText": [["yes", "yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- your hypothetical.", "start": 2781.423, "stop": 2782.422, "duration": 1, "cleanText": [["your", "hypothetical"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "That would --", "start": 2782.422, "stop": 2782.457, "duration": 0.03, "cleanText": [["that", "would"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That would be a Communist-front.", "start": 2782.457, "stop": 2783.863, "duration": 1.41, "cleanText": [["that", "would", "be", "a", "communist", "front"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 2783.863, "stop": 2784.349, "duration": 0.49, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "If you have a purpose of bolstering the Soviet Union and it would at the same time be controlled by the Communist Party, that's right.", "start": 2784.349, "stop": 2797.87, "duration": 13.52, "cleanText": [["if", "you", "have", "a", "purpose", "of", "bolster", "the", "soviet", "union", "and", "it", "would", "at", "the", "same", "time", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "that", "be", "right"]]}, {"text": "Those are two are the two things.", "start": 2797.87, "stop": 2798.838, "duration": 0.97, "cleanText": [["those", "be", "two", "be", "the", "two", "thing"]]}, {"text": "Now, you have to be controlled by a Communist-action organization, it operates primarily for the purpose of giving aid and support to the Communist-action organization that were -- the foreign government controlling the Communist -- a Communist-foreign government or the Communist (Voice Overlap) --", "start": 2798.838, "stop": 2815.15, "duration": 16.31, "cleanText": [["now", "you", "have", "to", "be", "control", "by", "a", "communist", "action", "organization", "it", "operate", "primarily", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "give", "aid", "and", "support", "to", "the", "communist", "action", "organization", "that", "we", "be", "the", "foreign", "government", "control", "the", "communist", "a", "communist", "foreign", "government", "or", "the", "communist", "voice", "overlap"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, the way not to be a Communist-front would be then to actively engage and destroy the -- any good image of Russia.", "start": 2815.15, "stop": 2824.671, "duration": 9.52, "cleanText": [["well", "the", "way", "not", "to", "be", "a", "communist", "front", "would", "be", "then", "to", "actively", "engage", "and", "destroy", "the", "any", "good", "image", "of", "russia"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "We are -- and one of the things is that --", "start": 2824.671, "stop": 2827.241, "duration": 2.57, "cleanText": [["we", "be", "and", "one", "of", "the", "thing", "be", "that"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "Because, do you --", "start": 2827.241, "stop": 2828.286, "duration": 1.05, "cleanText": [["because", "do", "you"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That somehow, that we've -- there's -- we should make a game out of being -- whether there should be a Communist-front.", "start": 2828.286, "stop": 2833.443, "duration": 5.16, "cleanText": [["that", "somehow", "that", "we", "have", "there", "be", "we", "should", "make", "a", "game", "out", "of", "be", "whether", "there", "should", "be", "a", "communist", "front"]]}, {"text": "If you're a Communist-front you've got to do something.", "start": 2833.443, "stop": 2835.879, "duration": 2.44, "cleanText": [["if", "you", "be", "a", "communist", "front", "you", "have", "get", "to", "do", "something"]]}, {"text": "Congress thinks that that makes you a danger, if you are not a danger, presumably it won't be a Communist-front.", "start": 2835.879, "stop": 2841.128, "duration": 5.25, "cleanText": [["congress", "think", "that", "that", "make", "you", "a", "danger", "if", "you", "be", "not", "a", "danger", "presumably", "it", "will", "not", "be", "a", "communist", "front"]]}, {"text": "I mean --", "start": 2841.128, "stop": 2841.686, "duration": 0.56, "cleanText": [["i", "mean"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "William J. Brennan, Jr.", "textObjs": [{"text": "But the way you have -- you have defined it, it's much a pretty broader ambit, I would think of.", "start": 2841.686, "stop": 2847.671, "duration": 5.98, "cleanText": [["but", "the", "way", "you", "have", "you", "have", "define", "it", "it", "be", "much", "a", "pretty", "broad", "ambit", "i", "would", "think", "of"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor it doesn't seem to be that broader ambit.", "start": 2847.671, "stop": 2849.966, "duration": 2.3, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "it", "do", "not", "seem", "to", "be", "that", "broad", "ambit"]]}, {"text": "There had been 14 organizations that have been found by the Board to be Communist-fronts.", "start": 2849.966, "stop": 2857.767, "duration": 7.8, "cleanText": [["there", "have", "be", "organization", "that", "have", "be", "find", "by", "the", "board", "to", "be", "communist", "front"]]}, {"text": "I think 50, one of the members found by the Court of Appeals to not be a Communist-front.", "start": 2857.767, "stop": 2861.784, "duration": 4.02, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "one", "of", "the", "member", "find", "by", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "to", "not", "be", "a", "communist", "front"]]}, {"text": "So there'd been 14 organizations in which the findings, I believe had been upheld.", "start": 2861.784, "stop": 2866.295, "duration": 4.51, "cleanText": [["so", "there", "have", "be", "organization", "in", "which", "the", "finding", "i", "believe", "have", "be", "uphold"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "Mr. Terris, if you read what -- you really read out the way it reads, doesn't it mean anything that is controlled by the Communist Party by itself be an in any way --", "start": 2866.295, "stop": 2880.889, "duration": 14.59, "cleanText": [["mr", "terris", "if", "you", "read", "what", "you", "really", "read", "out", "the", "way", "it", "read", "do", "not", "it", "mean", "anything", "that", "be", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "by", "itself", "be", "an", "in", "any", "way"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well --", "start": 2880.889, "stop": 2881.116, "duration": 0.23, "cleanText": [["well"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- with any organizations?", "start": 2881.116, "stop": 2882.271, "duration": 1.16, "cleanText": [["with", "any", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Your Honor, I don't think there be many organizations controlled by the Communist Party that aren't doing something in order to help the Communist Party, that's the reason they've got controlled.", "start": 2882.271, "stop": 2890.427, "duration": 8.16, "cleanText": [["your", "honor", "i", "do", "not", "think", "there", "be", "many", "organization", "control", "by", "the", "communist", "party", "that", "be", "not", "do", "something", "in", "order", "to", "help", "the", "communist", "party", "that", "be", "the", "reason", "they", "have", "get", "control"]]}, {"text": "Now a writ --", "start": 2890.427, "stop": 2890.898, "duration": 0.47, "cleanText": [["now", "a", "writ"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "Suppose what has been -- been in the federal grounds --", "start": 2890.898, "stop": 2894.228, "duration": 3.33, "cleanText": [["suppose", "what", "have", "be", "be", "in", "the", "federal", "ground"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor there was a time let me say there -- there was an order between the two.", "start": 2894.228, "stop": 2898.249, "duration": 4.02, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "there", "be", "a", "time", "let", "me", "say", "there", "there", "be", "an", "order", "between", "the", "two"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Why is that?", "start": 2898.249, "stop": 2899.045, "duration": 0.8, "cleanText": [["why", "be", "that"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Now --", "start": 2899.045, "stop": 2900.181, "duration": 1.14, "cleanText": [["now"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "How did they put the end?", "start": 2900.181, "stop": 2901.677, "duration": 1.5, "cleanText": [["how", "do", "they", "put", "the", "end"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I think Your Honor because they didn't want an organization, there might be a few examples on which it wouldn't be doing anything.", "start": 2901.677, "stop": 2908.553, "duration": 6.88, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "your", "honor", "because", "they", "do", "not", "want", "an", "organization", "there", "might", "be", "a", "few", "example", "on", "which", "it", "would", "not", "be", "do", "anything"]]}, {"text": "Primarily, a member can't be just -- can't be an incidental thing.", "start": 2908.553, "stop": 2911.603, "duration": 3.05, "cleanText": [["primarily", "a", "member", "can", "not", "be", "just", "can", "not", "be", "an", "incidental", "thing"]]}, {"text": "There were -- in which you would not be primarily helping the Communist Party.", "start": 2911.603, "stop": 2916.061, "duration": 4.46, "cleanText": [["there", "we", "be", "in", "which", "you", "would", "not", "be", "primarily", "help", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "There might -- it might be -- in other words if it's  if it just control that turns out to really be benign in the -- in the -- in Congress' sense, in not giving any aid, there's no reason to make it register.", "start": 2916.061, "stop": 2926.217, "duration": 10.16, "cleanText": [["there", "might", "it", "might", "be", "in", "other", "word", "if", "it", "be", "if", "it", "just", "control", "that", "turn", "out", "to", "really", "be", "benign", "in", "the", "in", "the", "in", "congress", "sense", "in", "not", "give", "any", "aid", "there", "be", "no", "reason", "to", "make", "it", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "But as I heard you and I thought you were arguing pretty effectively in saying that no matter how benign it is, if is controlled --", "start": 2926.217, "stop": 2934.337, "duration": 8.12, "cleanText": [["but", "as", "i", "hear", "you", "and", "i", "think", "you", "we", "be", "argue", "pretty", "effectively", "in", "say", "that", "no", "matter", "how", "benign", "it", "be", "if", "be", "control"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No.", "start": 2934.337, "stop": 2935.635, "duration": 1.3, "cleanText": [["no"]]}, {"text": "The Congress (Voice Overlap) didn't find it benign to be -- to be helping the Communist Party in any way.", "start": 2935.635, "stop": 2941.087, "duration": 5.45, "cleanText": [["the", "congress", "voice", "overlap", "do", "not", "find", "it", "benign", "to", "be", "to", "be", "help", "the", "communist", "party", "in", "any", "way"]]}, {"text": "When I say benign, it's saying that it really wasn't interested in ballet.", "start": 2941.087, "stop": 2945.608, "duration": 4.52, "cleanText": [["when", "i", "say", "benign", "it", "be", "say", "that", "it", "really", "be", "not", "interested", "in", "ballet"]]}, {"text": "There were no people in the Communist Party that liked ballet, that they just thought they were -- they wanted to have some of the great ballet companies to come to the United States and the Soviet was obviously one of them, then it would not have to register.", "start": 2945.608, "stop": 2960.079, "duration": 14.47, "cleanText": [["there", "we", "be", "no", "people", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "that", "like", "ballet", "that", "they", "just", "think", "they", "we", "be", "they", "want", "to", "have", "some", "of", "the", "great", "ballet", "company", "to", "come", "to", "the", "united", "state", "and", "the", "soviet", "be", "obviously", "one", "of", "them", "then", "it", "would", "not", "have", "to", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "That would not have to register even though there's no control?", "start": 2960.079, "stop": 2962.838, "duration": 2.76, "cleanText": [["that", "would", "not", "have", "to", "register", "even", "though", "there", "be", "no", "control"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right, no control.", "start": 2962.838, "stop": 2964.283, "duration": 1.44, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "no", "control"]]}, {"text": "It has to have the purpose of helping a Communist-foreign government, the Soviet Union.", "start": 2964.283, "stop": 2970.26, "duration": 5.98, "cleanText": [["it", "have", "to", "have", "the", "purpose", "of", "help", "a", "communist", "foreign", "government", "the", "soviet", "union"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Wouldn't the Government argue that all the things that you are arguing would apply in that given situation?", "start": 2970.26, "stop": 2976.87, "duration": 6.61, "cleanText": [["would", "not", "the", "government", "argue", "that", "all", "the", "thing", "that", "you", "be", "argue", "would", "apply", "in", "that", "give", "situation"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor I -- I can't say what it would argue but, definitively --", "start": 2976.87, "stop": 2981.378, "duration": 4.51, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "i", "i", "can", "not", "say", "what", "it", "would", "argue", "but", "definitively"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "It helps the image of the Communist Party is --", "start": 2981.378, "stop": 2983.133, "duration": 1.75, "cleanText": [["it", "help", "the", "image", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "be"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, it's not good enough that it does in fact aid.", "start": 2983.133, "stop": 2985.892, "duration": 2.76, "cleanText": [["no", "it", "be", "not", "good", "enough", "that", "it", "do", "in", "fact", "aid"]]}, {"text": "It is not -- and that would -- and I may say that that is why the Cramp case is not at all in point.", "start": 2985.892, "stop": 2992.334, "duration": 6.44, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "and", "that", "would", "and", "i", "may", "say", "that", "that", "be", "why", "the", "cramp", "case", "be", "not", "at", "all", "in", "point"]]}, {"text": "It isn't enough that you -- Wendell Willkie does not have -- would not have to register, the fact that somebody does aid the Communist Party does not require it to --", "start": 2992.334, "stop": 3003.973, "duration": 11.64, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "not", "enough", "that", "you", "wendell", "willkie", "do", "not", "have", "would", "not", "have", "to", "register", "the", "fact", "that", "somebody", "do", "aid", "the", "communist", "party", "do", "not", "require", "it", "to"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Tom C. Clark", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, it's controlled.", "start": 3003.973, "stop": 3004.778, "duration": 0.8, "cleanText": [["well", "it", "be", "control"]]}, {"text": "I thought --", "start": 3004.778, "stop": 3004.805, "duration": 0.03, "cleanText": [["i", "think"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Even if controlled, even if controlled, it has to have a purpose of aid and it's not enough to happen to give aid.", "start": 3004.805, "stop": 3012.099, "duration": 7.29, "cleanText": [["even", "if", "control", "even", "if", "control", "it", "have", "to", "have", "a", "purpose", "of", "aid", "and", "it", "be", "not", "enough", "to", "happen", "to", "give", "aid"]]}, {"text": "In other words, what -- what I'm really trying to say here is that Congress said about Communist-fronts, these are part of the Communist Party.", "start": 3012.099, "stop": 3020.034, "duration": 7.93, "cleanText": [["in", "other", "word", "what", "what", "I", "be", "really", "try", "to", "say", "here", "be", "that", "congress", "say", "about", "communist", "front", "these", "be", "part", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "They've been split-off in order to attract non-Communists.", "start": 3020.034, "stop": 3023.953, "duration": 3.92, "cleanText": [["they", "have", "be", "split", "off", "in", "order", "to", "attract", "non", "communist"]]}, {"text": "But they're not really split-off.", "start": 3023.953, "stop": 3026.029, "duration": 2.08, "cleanText": [["but", "they", "be", "not", "really", "split", "off"]]}, {"text": "They're subsidiaries of the Communist Party.", "start": 3026.029, "stop": 3027.413, "duration": 1.38, "cleanText": [["they", "be", "subsidiary", "of", "the", "communist", "party"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "I understand that, but now when you go on -- and I understand that, in other words, there's a finding that the Communist-front organization and if it's controlled and it's a Communist activity, part of their activity.", "start": 3027.413, "stop": 3038.942, "duration": 11.53, "cleanText": [["i", "understand", "that", "but", "now", "when", "you", "go", "on", "and", "i", "understand", "that", "in", "other", "word", "there", "be", "a", "finding", "that", "the", "communist", "front", "organization", "and", "if", "it", "be", "control", "and", "it", "be", "a", "communist", "activity", "part", "of", "their", "activity"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 3038.942, "stop": 3039.484, "duration": 0.54, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "But then Congress wrote something else and it said --", "start": 3039.484, "stop": 3041.637, "duration": 2.15, "cleanText": [["but", "then", "congress", "write", "something", "else", "and", "it", "say"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Sure.", "start": 3041.637, "stop": 3041.66, "duration": 0.02, "cleanText": [["sure"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- you're not encompassing all of the controlled activities.", "start": 3041.66, "stop": 3046.274, "duration": 4.61, "cleanText": [["you", "be", "not", "encompass", "all", "of", "the", "controlled", "activity"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right, Your Honor.", "start": 3046.274, "stop": 3046.388, "duration": 0.11, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "your", "honor"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "And really here, the question is or in this particular activity, is the type that's controlled.", "start": 3046.388, "stop": 3052.452, "duration": 6.06, "cleanText": [["and", "really", "here", "the", "question", "be", "or", "in", "this", "particular", "activity", "be", "the", "type", "that", "be", "control"]]}, {"text": "That that's -- it's included encompassing the statute.", "start": 3052.452, "stop": 3056.603, "duration": 4.15, "cleanText": [["that", "that", "be", "it", "be", "include", "encompass", "the", "statute"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor, I was going to come to that specific intention a little later but since I think it's the only serious non-constitutional argument which is before the Court, the others in our view are really quibbles about minor bits of evidence and normally nobody would even argue here.", "start": 3056.603, "stop": 3072.565, "duration": 15.96, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "i", "be", "go", "to", "come", "to", "that", "specific", "intention", "a", "little", "later", "but", "since", "i", "think", "it", "be", "the", "only", "serious", "non", "constitutional", "argument", "which", "be", "before", "the", "court", "the", "others", "in", "our", "view", "be", "really", "quibble", "about", "minor", "bit", "of", "evidence", "and", "normally", "nobody", "would", "even", "argue", "here"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Arthur J. Goldberg", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, the controlled point wasn't argued very much and --", "start": 3072.565, "stop": 3074.825, "duration": 2.26, "cleanText": [["well", "the", "controlled", "point", "be", "not", "argue", "very", "much", "and"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, it is in the brief but even -- and I'm talking about the sufficiency of the evidence too under the aid component as opposed the statutory construction.", "start": 3074.825, "stop": 3082.361, "duration": 7.54, "cleanText": [["well", "it", "be", "in", "the", "brief", "but", "even", "and", "I", "be", "talk", "about", "the", "sufficiency", "of", "the", "evidence", "too", "under", "the", "aid", "component", "as", "oppose", "the", "statutory", "construction"]]}, {"text": "Most of these points would not even normally find their way to this Court.", "start": 3082.361, "stop": 3088.497, "duration": 6.14, "cleanText": [["most", "of", "these", "point", "would", "not", "even", "normally", "find", "their", "way", "to", "this", "court"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible) without the aid component as applied.", "start": 3088.497, "stop": 3101.035, "duration": 12.54, "cleanText": [["inaudible", "without", "the", "aid", "component", "as", "apply"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, I think that's what the Court of Appeals did.", "start": 3101.035, "stop": 3102.909, "duration": 1.87, "cleanText": [["no", "i", "think", "that", "be", "what", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "do"]]}, {"text": "It applied the --", "start": 3102.909, "stop": 3103.402, "duration": 0.49, "cleanText": [["it", "apply", "the"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Voice Overlap) in the Court of Appeals in a number of ways, isn't it?", "start": 3103.402, "stop": 3106.641, "duration": 3.24, "cleanText": [["voice", "overlap", "in", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "in", "a", "number", "of", "way", "be", "not", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well -- well, Your Honor, I know the petitioner makes much of the fact that --", "start": 3106.641, "stop": 3111.639, "duration": 5, "cleanText": [["well", "well", "your", "honor", "i", "know", "the", "petitioner", "make", "much", "of", "the", "fact", "that"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, anyway, is that what you're -- is that what you're arguing?", "start": 3111.639, "stop": 3115.402, "duration": 3.76, "cleanText": [["well", "anyway", "be", "that", "what", "you", "be", "be", "that", "what", "you", "be", "argue"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I'm arguing --", "start": 3115.402, "stop": 3115.832, "duration": 0.43, "cleanText": [["I", "be", "argue"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "That you look not at the character of that provision but you look at the purpose of which the activities are undertaken, is that it?", "start": 3115.832, "stop": 3123.387, "duration": 7.56, "cleanText": [["that", "you", "look", "not", "at", "the", "character", "of", "that", "provision", "but", "you", "look", "at", "the", "purpose", "of", "which", "the", "activity", "be", "undertaken", "be", "that", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I'm arguing, Your Honor that you have to have the purpose of aiding the Communist Party.", "start": 3123.387, "stop": 3129.421, "duration": 6.03, "cleanText": [["I", "be", "argue", "your", "honor", "that", "you", "have", "to", "have", "the", "purpose", "of", "aid", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Now, there is a dispute what you actually have to aid in addition.", "start": 3129.421, "stop": 3133.264, "duration": 3.84, "cleanText": [["now", "there", "be", "a", "dispute", "what", "you", "actually", "have", "to", "aid", "in", "addition"]]}, {"text": "Petitioner says that you should read the statute as requiring not just purpose but actual aid.", "start": 3133.264, "stop": 3139.471, "duration": 6.21, "cleanText": [["petitioner", "say", "that", "you", "should", "read", "the", "statute", "as", "require", "not", "just", "purpose", "but", "actual", "aid"]]}, {"text": "The Government's reply to that is that seems inconsistent with the statute but it's not important to this case because both the Board and the Court of Appeals found both purpose and actual aid.", "start": 3139.471, "stop": 3151.252, "duration": 11.78, "cleanText": [["the", "government", "s", "reply", "to", "that", "be", "that", "seem", "inconsistent", "with", "the", "statute", "but", "it", "be", "not", "important", "to", "this", "case", "because", "both", "the", "board", "and", "the", "court", "of", "appeal", "find", "both", "purpose", "and", "actual", "aid"]]}, {"text": "So for purposes -- on the purposes of this case, we would assume there has to be both a purpose of aiding the Communist Party as such not to just do what an Act which turns out to be aid and actual aid to the Communist Party.", "start": 3151.252, "stop": 3167.359, "duration": 16.11, "cleanText": [["so", "for", "purpose", "on", "the", "purpose", "of", "this", "case", "we", "would", "assume", "there", "have", "to", "be", "both", "a", "purpose", "of", "aid", "the", "communist", "party", "as", "such", "not", "to", "just", "do", "what", "an", "act", "which", "turn", "out", "to", "be", "aid", "and", "actual", "aid", "to", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "And we think the evidence supports both.", "start": 3167.359, "stop": 3168.327, "duration": 0.97, "cleanText": [["and", "we", "think", "the", "evidence", "support", "both"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "UNKNOWN", "textObjs": [{"text": "Are the aid itself may be partly -- involved perfectly laudable.", "start": 3168.327, "stop": 3173.737, "duration": 5.41, "cleanText": [["be", "the", "aid", "itself", "may", "be", "partly", "involve", "perfectly", "laudable"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right Your Honor.", "start": 3173.737, "stop": 3174.891, "duration": 1.15, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "And constant -- and activities which are protected which would come within the ambit of the First Amendment.", "start": 3174.891, "stop": 3181.366, "duration": 6.47, "cleanText": [["and", "constant", "and", "activity", "which", "be", "protect", "which", "would", "come", "within", "the", "ambit", "of", "the", "first", "amendment"]]}, {"text": "I may say this is nothing very strange that the Foreign Agents Registration Act normally applies to activities which are within the ambit of the -- of the First Amendment.", "start": 3181.366, "stop": 3189.387, "duration": 8.02, "cleanText": [["i", "may", "say", "this", "be", "nothing", "very", "strange", "that", "the", "foreign", "agent", "registration", "act", "normally", "apply", "to", "activity", "which", "be", "within", "the", "ambit", "of", "the", "of", "the", "first", "amendment"]]}, {"text": "So does the -- our Federal Regulation of Lobbying Act.", "start": 3189.387, "stop": 3192.372, "duration": 2.98, "cleanText": [["so", "do", "the", "our", "federal", "regulation", "of", "lobby", "act"]]}, {"text": "And other statutes which require a disclosure so that we don't -- we don't think this is anything very noble that we're saying, and after all what we're talking about here -- and we're not talking about the disabilities, we're talking about disclosing.", "start": 3192.372, "stop": 3208.048, "duration": 15.68, "cleanText": [["and", "other", "statute", "which", "require", "a", "disclosure", "so", "that", "we", "do", "not", "we", "do", "not", "think", "this", "be", "anything", "very", "noble", "that", "we", "be", "say", "and", "after", "all", "what", "we", "be", "talk", "about", "here", "and", "we", "be", "not", "talk", "about", "the", "disability", "we", "be", "talk", "about", "disclosing"]]}, {"text": "First of all the Board finding the character of an organization telling the people that -- of the country that this is -- is this kind of organization so that they are not deceived.", "start": 3208.048, "stop": 3219.536, "duration": 11.49, "cleanText": [["first", "of", "all", "the", "board", "find", "the", "character", "of", "an", "organization", "tell", "the", "people", "that", "of", "the", "country", "that", "this", "be", "be", "this", "kind", "of", "organization", "so", "that", "they", "be", "not", "deceive"]]}, {"text": "And second of all requiring disclosure, the kind of disclosure that was -- that existed in the Federal Regulation of Lobbying Act and in several other federal statutes.", "start": 3219.536, "stop": 3229.825, "duration": 10.29, "cleanText": [["and", "second", "of", "all", "require", "disclosure", "the", "kind", "of", "disclosure", "that", "be", "that", "exist", "in", "the", "federal", "regulation", "of", "lobby", "act", "and", "in", "several", "other", "federal", "statute"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "What does -- what does the Act provides they should move people who register and lobby it?", "start": 3229.825, "stop": 3236.44, "duration": 6.62, "cleanText": [["what", "do", "what", "do", "the", "act", "provide", "they", "should", "move", "people", "who", "register", "and", "lobby", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Your Honor, if there -- Your Honor's question suggest and it is of course quite true that if we are to consider here all the disabilities, this statute with the disabilities is quite different than Federal Regulation of Lobbying Act, there's no doubt about that, I wouldn't -- I wouldn't suggest that contrary for a moment.", "start": 3236.44, "stop": 3256.768, "duration": 20.33, "cleanText": [["your", "honor", "if", "there", "your", "honor", "s", "question", "suggest", "and", "it", "be", "of", "course", "quite", "true", "that", "if", "we", "be", "to", "consider", "here", "all", "the", "disability", "this", "statute", "with", "the", "disability", "be", "quite", "different", "than", "federal", "regulation", "of", "lobby", "act", "there", "be", "no", "doubt", "about", "that", "i", "would", "not", "i", "would", "not", "suggest", "that", "contrary", "for", "a", "moment"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "What can be done for them for lobbying?", "start": 3256.768, "stop": 3259.579, "duration": 2.81, "cleanText": [["what", "can", "be", "do", "for", "them", "for", "lobby"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Nothing Your Honor.", "start": 3259.579, "stop": 3261.36, "duration": 1.78, "cleanText": [["nothing", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "What I -- that would --", "start": 3261.36, "stop": 3261.91, "duration": 0.55, "cleanText": [["what", "i", "that", "would"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "Isn't that a pretty bad analogy you used in this case?", "start": 3261.91, "stop": 3264.503, "duration": 2.59, "cleanText": [["be", "not", "that", "a", "pretty", "bad", "analogy", "you", "use", "in", "this", "case"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "No, Your Honor.", "start": 3264.503, "stop": 3265.042, "duration": 0.54, "cleanText": [["no", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "Because it seems to us that the Communist Party case establishes that we are not to look to the disabilities now.", "start": 3265.042, "stop": 3271.719, "duration": 6.68, "cleanText": [["because", "it", "seem", "to", "us", "that", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "establish", "that", "we", "be", "not", "to", "look", "to", "the", "disability", "now"]]}, {"text": "That those would be litigated individually.", "start": 3271.719, "stop": 3274.009, "duration": 2.29, "cleanText": [["that", "those", "would", "be", "litigate", "individually"]]}, {"text": "I may say the Aptheker case as an example of litigation of them and maybe that there will be other provisions that will not be constitutional but each one of those will have to be examined on its own merits.", "start": 3274.009, "stop": 3286.755, "duration": 12.75, "cleanText": [["i", "may", "say", "the", "aptheker", "case", "as", "an", "example", "of", "litigation", "of", "them", "and", "maybe", "that", "there", "will", "be", "other", "provision", "that", "will", "not", "be", "constitutional", "but", "each", "one", "of", "those", "will", "have", "to", "be", "examine", "on", "its", "own", "merit"]]}, {"text": "That is, in our view, was the teaching of the Communist Party case and it's perfectly clear.", "start": 3286.755, "stop": 3291.564, "duration": 4.81, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "in", "our", "view", "be", "the", "teaching", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "case", "and", "it", "be", "perfectly", "clear"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "I thought that it reached that little fine pinpoint in the brief.", "start": 3291.564, "stop": 3295.803, "duration": 4.24, "cleanText": [["i", "think", "that", "it", "reach", "that", "little", "fine", "pinpoint", "in", "the", "brief"]]}, {"text": "It didn't even get to the possibility that they might even end up with.", "start": 3295.803, "stop": 3299.479, "duration": 3.68, "cleanText": [["it", "do", "not", "even", "get", "to", "the", "possibility", "that", "they", "might", "even", "end", "up", "with"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, Your Honor it didn't reached that, but of course, it recognize that it could happen.", "start": 3299.479, "stop": 3302.777, "duration": 3.3, "cleanText": [["well", "your", "honor", "it", "do", "not", "reach", "that", "but", "of", "course", "it", "recognize", "that", "it", "could", "happen"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "But it didn't get to the prob -- possibility that they would register it, did it?", "start": 3302.777, "stop": 3307.938, "duration": 5.16, "cleanText": [["but", "it", "do", "not", "get", "to", "the", "prob", "possibility", "that", "they", "would", "register", "it", "do", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Well, it -- Your Honor it did not consider the Fifth Amendment questions on whether they --", "start": 3307.938, "stop": 3312.905, "duration": 4.97, "cleanText": [["well", "it", "your", "honor", "it", "do", "not", "consider", "the", "fifth", "amendment", "question", "on", "whether", "they"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "They said -- said they might not register.", "start": 3312.905, "stop": 3314.528, "duration": 1.62, "cleanText": [["they", "say", "say", "they", "might", "not", "register"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 3314.528, "stop": 3315.174, "duration": 0.65, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "Therefore, you don't have to reach any of these other things.", "start": 3315.174, "stop": 3317.33, "duration": 2.16, "cleanText": [["therefore", "you", "do", "not", "have", "to", "reach", "any", "of", "these", "other", "thing"]]}, {"text": "But how do you decided for us now to say we shouldn't consider them now.T", "start": 3317.33, "stop": 3322.573, "duration": 5.24, "cleanText": [["but", "how", "do", "you", "decide", "for", "us", "now", "to", "say", "we", "should", "not", "consider", "them", "nowt"]]}, {"text": "hey've got to register now, isn't it?", "start": 3322.573, "stop": 3324.138, "duration": 1.57, "cleanText": [["hey", "ve", "get", "to", "register", "now", "be", "not", "it"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Oh no, they -- they're in the same position as the Communist Party was when it came to this -- when it came to this Court in the Communist Party case.", "start": 3324.138, "stop": 3330.815, "duration": 6.68, "cleanText": [["oh", "no", "they", "they", "be", "in", "the", "same", "position", "as", "the", "communist", "party", "be", "when", "it", "come", "to", "this", "when", "it", "come", "to", "this", "court", "in", "the", "communist", "party", "case"]]}, {"text": "They're in exactly the same position.", "start": 3330.815, "stop": 3332.618, "duration": 1.8, "cleanText": [["they", "be", "in", "exactly", "the", "same", "position"]]}, {"text": "There's an outstanding order that they register, that was exactly the position of the Communist Party when it came to this Court.", "start": 3332.618, "stop": 3340.281, "duration": 7.66, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "an", "outstanding", "order", "that", "they", "register", "that", "be", "exactly", "the", "position", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "when", "it", "come", "to", "this", "court"]]}, {"text": "There's no difference at all in the posture of the two cases.", "start": 3340.281, "stop": 3347.433, "duration": 7.15, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "no", "difference", "at", "all", "in", "the", "posture", "of", "the", "two", "case"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "How many are included in this order?", "start": 3347.433, "stop": 3349.567, "duration": 2.13, "cleanText": [["how", "many", "be", "include", "in", "this", "order"]]}, {"text": "Just one?", "start": 3349.567, "stop": 3350.488, "duration": 0.92, "cleanText": [["just", "one"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "How many organizations?", "start": 3350.488, "stop": 3351.517, "duration": 1.03, "cleanText": [["how", "many", "organization"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes.", "start": 3351.517, "stop": 3351.963, "duration": 0.45, "cleanText": [["yes"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Yes Your Honor.", "start": 3351.963, "stop": 3353.543, "duration": 1.58, "cleanText": [["yes", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "There are -- then of course, the next case involves an additional --", "start": 3353.543, "stop": 3356.316, "duration": 2.77, "cleanText": [["there", "be", "then", "of", "course", "the", "next", "case", "involve", "an", "additional"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "This particular order just one?", "start": 3356.316, "stop": 3357.995, "duration": 1.68, "cleanText": [["this", "particular", "order", "just", "one"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Pardon me?", "start": 3357.995, "stop": 3359.8, "duration": 1.81, "cleanText": [["pardon", "me"]]}, {"text": "Yes, it's -- there's just one included in this.", "start": 3359.8, "stop": 3362.531, "duration": 2.73, "cleanText": [["yes", "it", "be", "there", "be", "just", "one", "include", "in", "this"]]}, {"text": "Mr. Justice Goldberg.", "start": 3362.531, "stop": 3363.256, "duration": 0.72, "cleanText": [["mr", "justice", "goldberg"]]}, {"text": "I'd like to return -- return to -- return to your question about what the aid component of the Act really means.", "start": 3363.256, "stop": 3369.843, "duration": 6.59, "cleanText": [["I", "would", "like", "to", "return", "return", "to", "return", "to", "your", "question", "about", "what", "the", "aid", "component", "of", "the", "act", "really", "mean"]]}, {"text": "Now, first of all, looking just at the aid component itself, all it says is that the Government must show that organization has the purpose of giving aid.", "start": 3369.843, "stop": 3381.761, "duration": 11.92, "cleanText": [["now", "first", "of", "all", "look", "just", "at", "the", "aid", "component", "itself", "all", "it", "say", "be", "that", "the", "government", "must", "show", "that", "organization", "have", "the", "purpose", "of", "give", "aid"]]}, {"text": "It does not say that there has to be any particular kind of aid.", "start": 3381.761, "stop": 3384.929, "duration": 3.17, "cleanText": [["it", "do", "not", "say", "that", "there", "have", "to", "be", "any", "particular", "kind", "of", "aid"]]}, {"text": "On its face, it would seem to include any kind of aid which would in -- and certainly nobody could deny, I would think, that defending party members aids the Communist Party.", "start": 3384.929, "stop": 3398.133, "duration": 13.2, "cleanText": [["on", "its", "face", "it", "would", "seem", "to", "include", "any", "kind", "of", "aid", "which", "would", "in", "and", "certainly", "nobody", "could", "deny", "i", "would", "think", "that", "defend", "party", "member", "aid", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Then in addition, Section 2 (7) describes what Communist-fronts are like.", "start": 3398.133, "stop": 3405.557, "duration": 7.42, "cleanText": [["then", "in", "addition", "section", "describe", "what", "communist", "front", "be", "like"]]}, {"text": "And this finding --", "start": 3405.557, "stop": 3406.393, "duration": 0.84, "cleanText": [["and", "this", "finding"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "I don't quite understand that, you said, nobody can deny what?", "start": 3406.393, "stop": 3410.082, "duration": 3.69, "cleanText": [["i", "do", "not", "quite", "understand", "that", "you", "say", "nobody", "can", "deny", "what"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "The defending -- defending a Communist Party member aids the Communist Party.", "start": 3410.082, "stop": 3414.607, "duration": 4.53, "cleanText": [["the", "defend", "defend", "a", "communist", "party", "member", "aids", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "It may do many other things, Your Honor.", "start": 3414.607, "stop": 3416.831, "duration": 2.22, "cleanText": [["it", "may", "do", "many", "other", "thing", "your", "honor"]]}, {"text": "It may do many other things that are very laudable but it does do that one thing.", "start": 3416.831, "stop": 3421.061, "duration": 4.23, "cleanText": [["it", "may", "do", "many", "other", "thing", "that", "be", "very", "laudable", "but", "it", "do", "do", "that", "one", "thing"]]}, {"text": "I'm not suggesting it's a bad thing to do --", "start": 3421.061, "stop": 3423.257, "duration": 2.2, "cleanText": [["I", "be", "not", "suggest", "it", "be", "a", "bad", "thing", "to", "do"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "(Inaudible)", "start": 3423.257, "stop": 3424.105, "duration": 0.85, "cleanText": [["inaudible"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Pardon me?", "start": 3424.105, "stop": 3424.648, "duration": 0.54, "cleanText": [["pardon", "me"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Hugo L. Black", "textObjs": [{"text": "Defend them where?", "start": 3424.648, "stop": 3426.169, "duration": 1.52, "cleanText": [["defend", "them", "where"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "Defend them in the courts or before the Immigration and Naturalization Service.", "start": 3426.169, "stop": 3430.45, "duration": 4.28, "cleanText": [["defend", "them", "in", "the", "court", "or", "before", "the", "immigration", "and", "naturalization", "service"]]}, {"text": "I -- I'm not suggesting that this is a bad thing for a person to do.", "start": 3430.45, "stop": 3435.33, "duration": 4.88, "cleanText": [["i", "I", "be", "not", "suggest", "that", "this", "be", "a", "bad", "thing", "for", "a", "person", "to", "do"]]}, {"text": "What I'm saying is that it does amokong other things aid the Communist Party.", "start": 3435.33, "stop": 3440.232, "duration": 4.9, "cleanText": [["what", "I", "be", "say", "be", "that", "it", "do", "amokong", "other", "thing", "aid", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "Every additional Communist Party member who stays in the Unites States presumably helps the Communist Party.", "start": 3440.232, "stop": 3445.926, "duration": 5.69, "cleanText": [["every", "additional", "communist", "party", "member", "who", "stay", "in", "the", "unites", "state", "presumably", "help", "the", "communist", "party"]]}, {"text": "At least, I think it's fair to say this record shows that the Communist Party thinks so.", "start": 3445.926, "stop": 3450.678, "duration": 4.75, "cleanText": [["at", "least", "i", "think", "it", "be", "fair", "to", "say", "this", "record", "show", "that", "the", "communist", "party", "think", "so"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "It's been argued that the other way and then one of the -- one of the big selling points of the Communist Party is that we have a terrible system of justice here and it's a tribalistic nation and maybe if they get the very just result in their lawsuit they will be disenchanted with Communism.", "start": 3450.678, "stop": 3467.765, "duration": 17.09, "cleanText": [["it", "be", "be", "argue", "that", "the", "other", "way", "and", "then", "one", "of", "the", "one", "of", "the", "big", "selling", "point", "of", "the", "communist", "party", "be", "that", "we", "have", "a", "terrible", "system", "of", "justice", "here", "and", "it", "be", "a", "tribalistic", "nation", "and", "maybe", "if", "they", "get", "the", "very", "just", "result", "in", "their", "lawsuit", "they", "will", "be", "disenchant", "with", "communism"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "That's right.", "start": 3467.765, "stop": 3467.99, "duration": 0.22, "cleanText": [["that", "be", "right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "And Communists.", "start": 3467.99, "stop": 3468.815, "duration": 0.83, "cleanText": [["and", "communist"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "I don't think Your Honor that this Court should really make the decision --", "start": 3468.815, "stop": 3471.786, "duration": 2.97, "cleanText": [["i", "do", "not", "think", "your", "honor", "that", "this", "court", "should", "really", "make", "the", "decision"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "No.", "start": 3471.786, "stop": 3472.028, "duration": 0.24, "cleanText": [["no"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- between -- which is the ultimate thing that aids democracy --", "start": 3472.028, "stop": 3477.006, "duration": 4.98, "cleanText": [["between", "which", "be", "the", "ultimate", "thing", "that", "aid", "democracy"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Potter Stewart", "textObjs": [{"text": "Right.", "start": 3477.006, "stop": 3477.157, "duration": 0.15, "cleanText": [["right"]]}]}, {"speakerName": "Bruce J. Terris", "textObjs": [{"text": "-- more or the Communist Party more.", "start": 3477.157, "stop": 3479.399, "duration": 2.24, "cleanText": [["more", "or", "the", "communist", "party", "more"]]}, {"text": "I understand that there's a -- that one could argue very persuasively that providing a good defense through those administrative and judicial review that this really helps democracy.", "start": 3479.399, "stop": 3492.79, "duration": 13.39, "cleanText": [["i", "understand", "that", "there", "be", "a", "that", "one", "could", "argue", "very", "persuasively", "that", "provide", "a", "good", "defense", "through", "those", "administrative", "and", "judicial", "review", "that", "this", "really", "help", "democracy"]]}, {"text": "But the point, the point that I'm making is that I don't think -- I think for the purpose of the statute that this was aiding the Communist Party, more members they hope will be in this country.", "start": 3492.79, "stop": 3508.621, "duration": 15.83, "cleanText": [["but", "the", "point", "the", "point", "that", "I", "be", "make", "be", "that", "i", "do", "not", "think", "i", "think", "for", "the", "purpose", "of", "the", "statute", "that", "this", "be", "aid", "the", "communist", "party", "more", "member", "they", "hope", "will", "be", "in", "this", "country"]]}]}]}], "decidedBy": "Warren Court", "arguedOn": "Dec  8 - 9, 1964", "petitioner": "American Committee for Protection of Foreign Born", "respondent": "Subversive Activities Control Board", "docket": "44", "citation": "380US503(1965)", "justiaLink": "https://supreme.justia.com/cases/federal/us/380/503", "lowerCourt": "United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit", "grantedOn": "", "decidedOn": "Apr 26, 1965"}